  <para style="h">U-Eksodasi</para>
  <para style="toc1">U-Eksodasi</para>
  <para style="toc2">U-Eksodasi</para>
  <para style="toc3">Eks</para>
  <para style="mt1">U-Eksodasi</para>
  <para style="imt">Isingeniso</para>
  <para style="imt1">Isingeniso</para>
  <para style="im">Amabhuku la, u-Eksodasi, uLevi lamaNani aqhubeka ngodaba lwendlela uNkulunkulu abumba ngayo isizwe sako-Israyeli ukuze sibelomlandu okhethekileyo emacebeni akhe omhlaba wonke. Abako-Israyeli sebethunjiwe eGibhithe, uNkulunkulu weza kubo wenza izimanga ezinkulu zokubakhulula ngoMosi. ENtabeni yaseSinayi uNkulunkulu wethula imilayo yakhe kuMosi kubalisa lemiThetho eliTshumi njalo waphawula isivumelwano sakhe lesizwana esincane. Abako-Israyeli bakha “ithabanikeli” kumbe “ithente lokuhlangana” ukuze uNkulunkulu ahlale phakathi kwabo. Emva kwalokho abantu badabula enkangala besiya elizweni laseKhenani.</para>
  <para style="ip">Imingcele ephakathi kwebhuku lika-Eksodasi, uLevi laManani kayivezwanga obala. Indlela emiswe ngayo emabhukwini wonke iveza ubudlelwano bezindawo ezithile abako-Israyeli abamisa khona ohanjweni lwabo. Kuvezwa indawo yinye ngayinye kanye lezehlakalo zayo ziyachazwa. Indawo emqoka yiNtaba yaseSinayi; ingxenye yesibili ka-Eksodasi, uLevi wonke kanye lekuqaliseni kwebhuku laManani kuchazwa okwenzakala lapho. ULevi kakhulukazi uqukethe imithetho lezimiso <char style="nd">uThixo</char> azipha abako-Israyeli. Ibhuku laManani libika indlela abantu ababeqoqwe ngayo emaviyweni ezimpi lokuya ezweni lesithembiso.</para>
  <para style="ip">Ugwalo lwaManani luthatha indaba ezike zakhulunywa kuLevi lo-Eksodasi njalo luphindaphinda umugca obumba uGenesisi othi <char style="qt">Lo ngumlando wemuli ka-Aroni loMosi</char> (AmaNani 3.1). Ngokugcweleyo umugca lo siwathola okwetshumi lambili njengezizwe ezilitshumi lambili ziqoqwa zisiba yisizwe esisodwa. Emaphethelweni ogwalo lwaManani umphrofethi uBhalamu uthi kwabako-Israyeli <char style="qt">Sengathi labo abalibusisayo bangabusiswa kuthi labo abaliqalekisayo baqalekiswe.</char> Lokhu kusikhumbuza isithembiso sikaNkulunkulu ku-Abhrahama ebhukwini likaGenesisi <char style="qt">Ngizababusisa labo abakubusisayo njalo ngimqalekise lowo okuqalekisayo.</char> Lamazwi aveza ukuthi amabhuku wonke la akhuluma udaba lunye lokuqala komsebenzi kaNkulunkulu wokuhlenga umhlaba.</para>
  <para style="ie"/>
  <chapter number="1" style="c" sid="EXO 1"/>
  <para style="s1">Ukuncindezelwa Kwabako-Israyeli</para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="EXO 1:1"/>La ngamabizo amadodana ka-Israyeli aya eGibhithe loJakhobe, munye ngamunye lemuli yakhe:<verse eid="EXO 1:1"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="EXO 1:2"/>uRubheni, uSimiyoni, uLevi loJuda;<verse eid="EXO 1:2"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="EXO 1:3"/>u-Isakhari, uZebhuluni loBhenjamini,<verse eid="EXO 1:3"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="EXO 1:4"/>uDani loNafithali;</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="EXO 1:4">uGadi lo-Asheri.<verse eid="EXO 1:4"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="EXO 1:5"/>Inzalo yonke kaJakhobe yayingamatshumi ayisikhombisa. UJosefa wayevele eseseGibhithe.<verse eid="EXO 1:5"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="EXO 1:6"/>Kwathi uJosefa labo bonke abafowabo kanye lasosonke lesosizukulwane sebefile, <verse eid="EXO 1:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="EXO 1:7"/>abako-Israyeli bazalana banda kakhulu, okokuthi ilizwe lonke lagcwala ngabo.<verse eid="EXO 1:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="EXO 1:8"/>Kwasekusiba lenye inkosi eyayingazi lutho ngoJosefa, yaba ngumbusi eGibhithe. <verse eid="EXO 1:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="EXO 1:9"/>Yathi ebantwini bayo, “Khangelani, abantu bako-Israyeli sebebanengi kakhulu kulathi. <verse eid="EXO 1:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="EXO 1:10"/>Asiboneni amacebo esingawenza ngabo funa bande kakhulu kuthi lapho kuqhamuka impi, babambane lezitha zethu, balwe lathi, besebesuka elizweni.”<verse eid="EXO 1:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="EXO 1:11"/>Ngakho babeka izinduna zezigqili ukuthi zibasebenzise kanzima, bakha iPhithomi leRamesesi aba ngamadolobho eziphala zikaFaro. <verse eid="EXO 1:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="EXO 1:12"/>Kodwa kwathi ngokuhlutshwa kwabo ngamandla, labo banda kakhulu basabalala; okwenza amaGibhithe abesaba abako-Israyeli <verse eid="EXO 1:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="EXO 1:13"/>asebasebenzisa ngochuku. <verse eid="EXO 1:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="EXO 1:14"/>Enza impilo yabo yaba nzima kakhulu betshaya izitina lokuvoxa udaka besenza leminye yonke imisebenzi yemasimini. Kuyo yonke imisebenzi enzima amaGibhithe abasebenzisa ngochuku.<verse eid="EXO 1:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="EXO 1:15"/>Inkosi yaseGibhithe yathi kubabelethisi bamaHebheru okwakuthiwa nguShifira loPhuwa, <verse eid="EXO 1:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="EXO 1:16"/>“Nxa libelethisa abafazi bamaHebheru, lingabona kuzelwe umfana kufanele limbulale; kodwa nxa kuyinkazana, liyiyekele iphile.” <verse eid="EXO 1:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="EXO 1:17"/>Kodwa ababelethisi babemesaba uNkulunkulu, ngakho abakwenzanga lokho ababekutshelwe yinkosi yaseGibhithe. <verse eid="EXO 1:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="EXO 1:18"/>Sekube njalo, inkosi yaseGibhithe yababiza ababelethisi yathi kubo, “Kungani lenze lokhu? Kungani liyekele abafana baphila?”<verse eid="EXO 1:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="EXO 1:19"/>Ababelethisi bamphendula uFaro bathi, “Abafazi bamaHebheru abafani labafazi bamaGibhithe; balamandla baphanga babelethe ababelethisi bengakafiki.”<verse eid="EXO 1:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="EXO 1:20"/>Ngakho uNkulunkulu waba lomusa kubo ababelethisi, abantu banda baba banengi kakhulu. <verse eid="EXO 1:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="EXO 1:21"/>Njalo njengoba ababelethisi bamesaba uNkulunkulu, wabapha ezabo izimuli.<verse eid="EXO 1:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="EXO 1:22"/>UFaro wasesipha abantu bakhe bonke umlayo othi: “Wonke umfana womHebheru ozalwayo kufanele aphoselwe emfuleni uNayili, kodwa wonke amankazana liwayekele aphile.”<verse eid="EXO 1:22"/></para>
  <chapter eid="EXO 1"/>
  <chapter number="2" style="c" sid="EXO 2"/>
  <para style="s1">Ukuzalwa KukaMosi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="EXO 2:1"/>Kwasekusithi eyinye indoda esizweni sakoLevi yathatha owesifazane ongumLevi, <verse eid="EXO 2:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="EXO 2:2"/>wazithwala wabeletha indodana. Wabona ukuthi umntwana wayemuhle kakhulu, wasemfihla okwezinyanga ezintathu. <verse eid="EXO 2:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="EXO 2:3"/>Kodwa kwathi lapho sekusehlula ukuthi amfihle, wenza isitsha semizi, wasibhada ngodaka lengcino. Wafaka umntwana phakathi kwaso wayasibeka okhunjini lomfula uNayili phakathi kwemihlanga. <verse eid="EXO 2:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="EXO 2:4"/>Udadewabo wema bucwala ukuba abone okwenzakala kuye.<verse eid="EXO 2:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="EXO 2:5"/>Indodakazi kaFaro yehlela emfuleni ukuyageza, amantombazana ayikhangelayo ayehamba okhunjini lomfula. Yasisibona isitsha phakathi kwemihlanga yathuma incekukazi yayo ukuyasithatha. <verse eid="EXO 2:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="EXO 2:6"/>Yasivula yambona umntwana. Wayekhala, yasimzwela usizi yathi, “Lo ngomunye wabantwana bamaHebheru.”<verse eid="EXO 2:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="EXO 2:7"/>Udadewabo wasesithi endodakazini kaFaro, “Ngingayakudingela omunye wabesifazane bamaHebheru ukuthi akondlele umntwana na?”<verse eid="EXO 2:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="EXO 2:8"/>Yasisithi, “Yebo, hamba.” Intombazana yasuka yayabiza unina womntwana. <verse eid="EXO 2:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="EXO 2:9"/>Indodakazi kaFaro yathi kuye, “Mthathe lumntwana ungondlele yena, ngizakupha isondlo.” Ngakho owesifazane wamthatha umntwana wamondla. <verse eid="EXO 2:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="EXO 2:10"/>Esekhulile umntwana, wamthatha wamusa endodakazini kaFaro wasesiba ngumntanayo. Yasimutha ibizo yathi nguMosi ngoba yathi, “Ngamkhupha emanzini.”<verse eid="EXO 2:10"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UMosi Ubalekela EMidiyani</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="EXO 2:11"/>Ngelinye ilanga, uMosi esekhulile, waya lapho okwakusebenzela khona abantu bakibo, wabona ukuthi babethwele nzima kanjani. Wabona umGibhithe etshaya umHebheru, omunye wabantu bakibo. <verse eid="EXO 2:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="EXO 2:12"/>Wathi thala ngapha langapha wabona kungelamuntu, wasebulala umGibhithe wamfihla etshebetshebeni. <verse eid="EXO 2:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="EXO 2:13"/>Ngelanga elilandelayo waphuma njalo wabona amaHebheru amabili esilwa. Wasebuza lo owayephambanisile wathi, “Kungani utshaya owakini ongumHebheru na?”<verse eid="EXO 2:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="EXO 2:14"/>Indoda leyo yathi, “Ngubani okwenze waba ngumbusi lomahluleli wethu? Usucabanga ukungibulala na njengoba ubulele umGibhithe?” Ngalokho uMosi wesaba wacabanga ukuthi, “Engxenye engikwenzileyo sekusazakala.”<verse eid="EXO 2:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="EXO 2:15"/>Kwathi uFaro ekuzwa lokho, wazama ukubulala uMosi, kodwa uMosi wabalekela eMidiyani, lapho afika khona wahlala phansi eduze komthombo. <verse eid="EXO 2:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="EXO 2:16"/>Umphristi waseMidiyani wayelamadodakazi ayisikhombisa, afika ezokukha amanzi lokukhelela imikolo ukuze anathise izimvu zikayise. <verse eid="EXO 2:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="EXO 2:17"/>Kwafika abelusi abathile bawaxotsha, kodwa uMosi wasukuma wawalamulela wanathisa izimvu zawo.<verse eid="EXO 2:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="EXO 2:18"/>Kwathi izintombi sezibuyele kuyise eRuweli wazibuza esithi, “Kungani lamhla liphangisile ukuphenduka?”<verse eid="EXO 2:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="EXO 2:19"/>Zaphendula zathi, “KulomGibhithe osilamulele kubelusi. Uze wasikhelela amanzi wanathisa lezimvu zethu.”<verse eid="EXO 2:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="EXO 2:20"/>Wawabuza amadodakazi akhe wathi, “Ungaphi? Limtshiyeleni? Mbizeni ukuze azothola okokudla.”<verse eid="EXO 2:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="EXO 2:21"/>UMosi wavuma ukuzehlala lale indoda, eyamnika indodakazi yayo uZiphora ukuthi abe ngumkakhe. <verse eid="EXO 2:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="EXO 2:22"/>UZiphora wazala indodana, uMosi wayitha ibizo wathi nguGeshomu ngoba esithi, “Sengibe ngumuntu wezizweni endaweni yabezizweni.”<verse eid="EXO 2:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="EXO 2:23"/>Emva kwesikhathi eside, inkosi yaseGibhithe yafa. Abako-Israyeli bakhala babubula ebugqilini babo, kwasekusithi ukukhala kwabo becela usizo ngenxa yobugqili ababekubo kwafinyelela kuNkulunkulu. <verse eid="EXO 2:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="EXO 2:24"/>UNkulunkulu wakuzwa ukububula kwabo wasekhumbula isivumelwano asenza lo-Abhrahama, lo-Isaka loJakhobe. <verse eid="EXO 2:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="EXO 2:25"/>Ngakho uNkulunkulu wakhangela abako-Israyeli, wakhathazeka ngabo.<verse eid="EXO 2:25"/></para>
  <chapter eid="EXO 2"/>
  <chapter number="3" style="c" sid="EXO 3"/>
  <para style="s1">UMosi Lesixuku Esivutha Umlilo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="EXO 3:1"/>Kwathi uMosi eselusa izimvu zikayisezala uJethro, umphristi waseMidiyani, waseqhuba izimvu zaya kude ohlangothini lwenkangala wasefika eHorebhi, intaba kaNkulunkulu. <verse eid="EXO 3:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="EXO 3:2"/>Lapho-ke ingilosi <char style="nd">kaThixo</char> yabonakala kuye iphakathi kwamalangabi omlilo esixukwini. UMosi wabona ukuthi loba isixuku sasibhebha kasizange sitshe. <verse eid="EXO 3:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="EXO 3:3"/>Ngakho uMosi wacabanga esithi, “Ngizasondela ngiyebona isimanga lesi ukuba kungani isixuku singatshi silothe.”<verse eid="EXO 3:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="EXO 3:4"/>Kwathi <char style="nd">uThixo</char> ebona ukuthi usesondele ukuba ayekhangela, uNkulunkulu wasememeza ngelizwi elaliphuma kulesosixuku wathi, “Mosi! Mosi!”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="EXO 3:4">UMosi wathi, “Ngilapha.”<verse eid="EXO 3:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="EXO 3:5"/>UNkulunkulu wathi, “Ungasondeli. Khupha amanyathela akho, ngoba indawo omi kuyo ingumhlabathi ongcwele.” <verse eid="EXO 3:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="EXO 3:6"/>Wasesithi njalo, “NginguNkulunkulu kayihlo, uNkulunkulu ka-Abhrahama, uNkulunkulu ka-Isaka loNkulunkulu kaJakhobe.” Ngalokhu, uMosi wafihla ubuso bakhe ngoba wayesesaba ukukhangela uNkulunkulu.<verse eid="EXO 3:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="EXO 3:7"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wasesithi, “Impela ngilubonile usizi lwabantu bami eGibhithe. Ngibazwile bekhala ngenxa yezinduna zezigqili ezibancindezelayo, njalo ngiyakhathazeka ngokuhlupheka kwabo. <verse eid="EXO 3:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="EXO 3:8"/>Ngakho ngehlile ukuzabakhulula ezandleni zamaGibhithe ngibakhuphe kulelolizwe ngibase elizweni elilendawo enengi, ilizwe eligeleza uchago loluju, endaweni yamaKhenani, amaHithi, ama-Amori, amaPherizi, amaHivi lamaJebusi. <verse eid="EXO 3:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="EXO 3:9"/>Ukukhala kwabako-Israyeli sekufikile kimi, njalo sengibonile lendlela amaGibhithe ababahlukuluza ngayo. <verse eid="EXO 3:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="EXO 3:10"/>Ngakho suka uhambe. Ngikuthuma kuFaro ukuthi uyekhupha abantu bami abako-Israyeli elizweni laseGibhithe.”<verse eid="EXO 3:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="EXO 3:11"/>Kodwa uMosi wathi kuNkulunkulu, “Kambe ngingubani ukuba ngiye kuFaro ukuyakhupha abako-Israyeli elizweni laseGibhithe na?”<verse eid="EXO 3:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="EXO 3:12"/>UNkulunkulu wasesithi, “Ngizakuba lawe. Lesi sizakuba yisibonakaliso sokuthi yimi engikuthumileyo: Nxa usubakhuphile abantu eGibhithe, lizakhonza uNkulunkulu kuyonale intaba.”<verse eid="EXO 3:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="EXO 3:13"/>UMosi wathi kuNkulunkulu, “Aluba ngifika kwabako-Israyeli ngithi kubo, ‘UNkulunkulu waboyihlo ungithumile kini,’ besebengibuza bathi, ‘Ungubani ibizo lakhe?’ Ngizakuthini kubo?”<verse eid="EXO 3:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="EXO 3:14"/>UNkulunkulu wathi kuMosi, “<char style="nd">Nginguye Onguye</char>. Lokhu yikho ozakutsho kwabako-Israyeli ukuthi, ‘<char style="nd">Unguye</char> ungithumile kini.’ ”<verse eid="EXO 3:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="EXO 3:15"/>UNkulunkulu wabuye wathi kuMosi, “Tshono kwabako-Israyeli uthi, ‘<char style="nd">uThixo</char>, uNkulunkulu waboyihlo, uNkulunkulu ka-Abhrahama, uNkulunkulu ka-Isaka, loNkulunkulu kaJakhobe ungithumile kini.’</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="EXO 3:15">Leli libizo lami laphakade,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="EXO 3:15">ibizo engizakhunjulwa ngalo kusukela</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="EXO 3:15">kusizukulwane kusiya kwesinye isizukulwane.<verse eid="EXO 3:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="EXO 3:16"/>Hamba uyebuthanisa abadala bako-Israyeli uthi kubo, ‘<char style="nd">uThixo</char>, uNkulunkulu waboyihlo, uNkulunkulu ka-Abhrahama, ka-Isaka loJakhobe, ubonakele kimi wathi: Bengilikhangele njalo ngikubonile okwenziwe kini eGibhithe. <verse eid="EXO 3:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="EXO 3:17"/>Futhi ngithembisile ukulikhupha osizini lwenu elikulo eGibhithe ngilise elizweni lamaKhenani, amaHithi, ama-Amori, amaPherizi, amaHivi lamaJebusi, ilizwe eligeleza uchago loluju.’<verse eid="EXO 3:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="EXO 3:18"/>Abadala bako-Israyeli bazakulalela. Kuzakuthi wena kanye labadala liye enkosini yaseGibhithe lithi kuyo, ‘<char style="nd">uThixo</char>, uNkulunkulu wamaHebheru uhlangane lathi. Sivumele sithathe uhambo lwezinsuku ezintathu siye enkangala ukuyanikela imihlatshelo <char style="nd">kuThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wethu.’ <verse eid="EXO 3:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="EXO 3:19"/>Kodwa ngiyakwazi ukuthi inkosi yaseGibhithe ayiyikulivumela ukuthi lihambe ngaphandle kokuba incindezelwe yisandla esilamandla. <verse eid="EXO 3:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="EXO 3:20"/>Ngakho ngizakwelula isandla sami ngiwatshaye amaGibhithe ngazozonke izimanga engizazenza phakathi kwawo. Ngemva kwalokho, izalivumela lihambe.<verse eid="EXO 3:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="EXO 3:21"/>Njalo ngizakwenza amaGibhithe abe lomusa kulababantu, ukuze kuthi mhla lisuka lingahambi lingaphethe lutho. <verse eid="EXO 3:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="EXO 3:22"/>Wonke owesifazane kacele kumakhelwane wakhe lakuye wonke owesifazane ohlala endlini yakhe izinto eziligugu ezenziwe ngesiliva legolide kanye lezigqoko ezizagqokwa ngamadodana lamadodakazi enu. Ngaleyondlela lizawemuka impahla amaGibhithe.”<verse eid="EXO 3:22"/></para>
  <chapter eid="EXO 3"/>
  <chapter number="4" style="c" sid="EXO 4"/>
  <para style="s1">Izibonakaliso ZikaMosi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="EXO 4:1"/>UMosi waphendula wathi, “Pho bangayekela ukungikholwa loba ukulalela engikutshoyo bathi, ‘<char style="nd">uThixo</char> kazange abonakale kuwe’?”<verse eid="EXO 4:1"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="EXO 4:2"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wathi kuye, “Kuyini lokho okusesandleni sakho?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="EXO 4:2">Waphendula wathi, “Yintonga.”<verse eid="EXO 4:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="EXO 4:3"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wathi, “Iphosele phansi emhlabathini.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="EXO 4:3">UMosi wayiphosa phansi yasiphenduka yaba yinyoka, wayibalekela. <verse eid="EXO 4:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="EXO 4:4"/><char style="nd">UThixo</char> wasesithi kuye, “Yelula isandla sakho uyibambe ngomsila.” UMosi welula isandla wayibamba inyoka yasiphenduka yaba yintonga esandleni sakhe. <verse eid="EXO 4:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="EXO 4:5"/><char style="nd">UThixo</char> wathi, “Lokhu yikwenzela ukuthi bakholwe ukuthi <char style="nd">uThixo</char>, uNkulunkulu waboyise, uNkulunkulu ka-Abhrahama, uNkulunkulu ka-Isaka loNkulunkulu kaJakhobe ubonakele kuwe.”<verse eid="EXO 4:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="EXO 4:6"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wabuye wathi, “Faka isandla sakho phakathi kwejazi lakho.” UMosi wasefaka isandla sakhe ejazini lakhe, kwathi lapho esesikhupha, sasesimhlophe njengongqwaqwane sesilobulephero.<verse eid="EXO 4:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="EXO 4:7"/>Wathi njalo, “Sibuyisele isandla sakho ejazini lakho.” UMosi wasifaka isandla sakhe ejazini lakhe, wathi esesikhupha sasesibuyele esimeni saso, sesifanana lejwabu lakhe.<verse eid="EXO 4:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="EXO 4:8"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wasesithi, “Nxa bengayikukholwa loba bengananzi izibonakaliso zokuqala, mhlawumbe bazakholwa ezesibili. <verse eid="EXO 4:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="EXO 4:9"/>Kodwa nxa bengakholwa izibonakaliso lezi ezimbili loba bengakulaleli, uzathatha amanzi emfuleni uNayili uwathele emhlabathini owomileyo. Amanzi ozawathatha emfuleni azaphenduka abe ligazi emhlabathini owomileyo.”<verse eid="EXO 4:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="EXO 4:10"/>UMosi wasesithi <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>, “Oh <char style="nd">Thixo</char>, ngixolele, angizange ngibe yisikhulumi kusukela emuva kuze kube lakhathesi ukhuluma lenceku yakho. Ngiyagagasa njalo ngilamalimi.”<verse eid="EXO 4:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="EXO 4:11"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wathi kuye, “Ngubani owapha umuntu umlomo? Ngubani omenza abe yisacuthe loba abe yisimungulu? Ngubani omenza abone loba abe yisiphofu? Akusimi <char style="nd">uThixo</char> na? <verse eid="EXO 4:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="EXO 4:12"/>Ngakho hamba, ngizakusiza ukuthi ukhulume njalo ngikufundise lokuthi uthini.”<verse eid="EXO 4:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="EXO 4:13"/>Kodwa uMosi wathi, “Oh Thixo, ngicela uthume omunye ukuthi ayekwenza lokhu.”<verse eid="EXO 4:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="EXO 4:14"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wathukuthela, ulaka lwakhe lwavutha kuMosi, wathi, “Umfowenu u-Aroni, ongumLevi ke? Ngiyazi ukuthi uyenelisa ukukhuluma kuhle. Uvele usendleleni ukuzahlangana lawe, njalo inhliziyo yakhe izathokoza ukukubona. <verse eid="EXO 4:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="EXO 4:15"/>Uzakhuluma laye ufake amazwi emlonyeni wakhe. Ngizaliphathisa lobabili ukuthi likhulume njalo ngizalifundisa ukuthi lenzeni. <verse eid="EXO 4:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="EXO 4:16"/>Yena uzakukhulumela ebantwini, njalo kuzakuba sengani nguye ongumlomo wakho njalo kube angani wena unguNkulunkulu kuye. <verse eid="EXO 4:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="EXO 4:17"/>Kodwa phatha intonga le esandleni sakho ukuze wenze izimangaliso ngayo.”<verse eid="EXO 4:17"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UMosi Ubuyela EGibhithe</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="EXO 4:18"/>UMosi wasebuyela kuyisezala uJethro wathi kuye, “Bengicela ukubuyela ebantwini bakithi eGibhithe ukuthi ngiyebona kumbe balokhu besaphilile.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="EXO 4:18">UJethro wathi kuye, “Hamba kuhle.”<verse eid="EXO 4:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="EXO 4:19"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wayethe kuMosi eMidiyani, “Buyela eGibhithe, ngoba bonke abantu ababefuna ukukubulala sebafa.” <verse eid="EXO 4:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="EXO 4:20"/>Ngakho uMosi wathatha umkakhe kanye lamadodana akhe, wabakhweza kubabhemi waqala uhambo lokubuyela eGibhithe. Wathatha intonga kaNkulunkulu wayiphatha ngesandla.<verse eid="EXO 4:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="EXO 4:21"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wathi kuMosi, “Ekubuyeleni kwakho eGibhithe, bona ukuthi uyazenza zonke izimangaliso engikuphe amandla okuba uzenze phambi kukaFaro. Kodwa ngizakwenza inhliziyo yakhe ibe lukhuni ukuba angabavumeli abantu ukuthi basuke. <verse eid="EXO 4:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="EXO 4:22"/>Uzakuthi kuFaro, ‘<char style="nd">uThixo</char> uthi u-Israyeli yindodana yami elizibulo, <verse eid="EXO 4:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="EXO 4:23"/>njalo ngakutshela ngathi, “Vumela indodana yami ihambe, ukuze iyengikhonza.” Kodwa wena wala ukuyivumela ukuba ihambe; ngakho ngizabulala indodana yakho elizibulo.’ ”<verse eid="EXO 4:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="EXO 4:24"/>Kwathi besesendleleni, endlini yezihambi, <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wahlangana loMosi wafuna ukumbulala. <verse eid="EXO 4:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="EXO 4:25"/>Kodwa uZiphora wayisoka indodana yakhe, wathatha isikhumba sakhona wasethinta inyawo zikaMosi ngaso. Wathi, “Impela wena ungumyeni wegazi.” <verse eid="EXO 4:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="EXO 4:26"/>Ngakho <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wamyekela. (Ngalesosikhathi uZiphora wathi “umyeni wegazi,” esitsho ukusoka.)<verse eid="EXO 4:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="EXO 4:27"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wathi ku-Aroni, “Hamba uye enkangala uhlangabezane loMosi.” Ngakho wasuka wayahlangana loMosi entabeni <char style="nd">kaThixo</char> wamanga. <verse eid="EXO 4:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="EXO 4:28"/>UMosi wamtshela u-Aroni konke <char style="nd">uThixo</char> ayemthume ukuthi akutsho, njalo langazo zonke izibonakaliso ezimangalisayo ayemlaye ukuba azenze.<verse eid="EXO 4:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="EXO 4:29"/>UMosi lo-Aroni bahamba bafika baqoqa bonke abadala bako-Israyeli, <verse eid="EXO 4:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="EXO 4:30"/>u-Aroni wasebatshela konke <char style="nd">uThixo</char> ayekutshele uMosi. Wenza lezibonakaliso phambi kwabantu, <verse eid="EXO 4:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="EXO 4:31"/>bakholwa. Kwathi besizwa ukuthi <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uyabakhathalela, njalo wayelubonile usizi lwabo, bakhothama phansi bamkhonza.<verse eid="EXO 4:31"/></para>
  <chapter eid="EXO 4"/>
  <chapter number="5" style="c" sid="EXO 5"/>
  <para style="s1">Izitina Kungelatshani</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="EXO 5:1"/>Emva kwalokho uMosi lo-Aroni baya kuFaro. Bathi kuye, “Sikulethele ilizwi elivela <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>, uNkulunkulu wabantu bako-Israyeli. Uthi, ‘Vumela abantu bami bahambe, ukuze bangenzele umkhosi enkangala.’ ”<verse eid="EXO 5:1"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="EXO 5:2"/>UFaro wathi, “Ungubani <char style="nd">uThixo</char> okufanele ngimlalele ngivumele abako-Israyeli ukuba bahambe na? Mina kangimazi <char style="nd">uThixo</char>, njalo kangiyikubavumela abako-Israyeli ukuba bahambe.”<verse eid="EXO 5:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="EXO 5:3"/>Ngakho-ke bona bathi, “UNkulunkulu wamaHebheru ubonakele kithi. Kumele sithathe uhambo lwamalanga amathathu siye enkangala ukuze siyenikela iminikelo <char style="nd">kuThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wethu, funa asibulale ngemikhuhlane loba ngenkemba.”<verse eid="EXO 5:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="EXO 5:4"/>Kodwa inkosi yaseGibhithe yathi, “Mosi lo-Aroni, kungani lisusa abantu emsebenzini wabo? Buyelani emisebenzini yenu.” <verse eid="EXO 5:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="EXO 5:5"/>UFaro wasesithi, “Khangelani abantu sebebanengi elizweni, kodwa lina liyabamisa ukusebenza.”<verse eid="EXO 5:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="EXO 5:6"/>Ngalelolanga uFaro wathumela lelilizwi ezinduneni zezigqili ezazisebenzisa abantu wathi: <verse eid="EXO 5:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="EXO 5:7"/>“Lingabe lisabapha abantu utshani bokwenza izitina. Yekelani bayezidingela utshani babo kodwa lingehlisi inani lezitina okumele bazenze. <verse eid="EXO 5:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="EXO 5:8"/>Kumele ukuthi batshaye inani abebelitshaya. Bangamavila, yikho besuka bakhale besithi, ‘Kasihambeni siyenikela kuNkulunkulu wethu.’ <verse eid="EXO 5:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="EXO 5:9"/>Yenzani umsebenzi ubenzima kwabesilisa ukuze baqhubekele phambili ngomsebenzi batshiyane lokulalela amanga.”<verse eid="EXO 5:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="EXO 5:10"/>Izinduna zezigqili kanye labaphathi baphuma bayatshela abantu bathi, “Nanku esikulaywe nguFaro, uthi, ‘Kangisoze ngilinike utshani futhi. <verse eid="EXO 5:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="EXO 5:11"/>Hambani liyesika utshani lapho elingabuthola khona. Kodwa umsebenzi wenu kawusoze uphungulwe lakancinyane.’ ” <verse eid="EXO 5:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="EXO 5:12"/>Ngakho abantu bahlakazeka kulolonke elaseGibhithe, besika imihlanga ukuze bayisebenzise esikhundleni sotshani. <verse eid="EXO 5:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="EXO 5:13"/>Izinduna zezigqili zaqhubeka zibakhahlameza zisithi, “Qedani imisebenzi yansuku zonke njengalokho elalikwenza lisazuza utshani.” <verse eid="EXO 5:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="EXO 5:14"/>Abaphathi bezisebenzi bako-Israyeli ababekhethwe yizinduna zezigqili zikaFaro batshaywa bebuzwa ukuthi, “Kungani inani lezolo lelanamuhla lingenelanga njengakuqala?”<verse eid="EXO 5:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="EXO 5:15"/>Ngakho abaphathi bezisebenzi bako-Israyeli baya kuFaro bamncenga besithi, “Kungani uphatha izisebenzi zakho ngale indlela? <verse eid="EXO 5:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="EXO 5:16"/>Izisebenzi zakho kazinikwa utshani, kodwa sitshelwa ukuthi, ‘Tshayani izitina!’ Izisebenzi zakho ziyatshaywa, kodwa umlandu ngowabantu bakho.”<verse eid="EXO 5:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="EXO 5:17"/>UFaro wathi, “Mavila, yikho eliyikho, mavila! Yikho lihlala lisithi, ‘Siyekele siyenikela <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>.’ <verse eid="EXO 5:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="EXO 5:18"/>Buyelani emsebenzini. Akulatshani elizabuphiwa. Kodwa kumele lenze izitina ezifika inani ebelivele lilenza.”<verse eid="EXO 5:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="EXO 5:19"/>Abaphathi bezisebenzi bako-Israyeli bananzelela ukuthi babesebunzimeni obukhulu baze batshelwe ukuthi, “Kakumelanga lehlise inani lezitina okumele lilenze nsuku zonke.” <verse eid="EXO 5:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="EXO 5:20"/>Sebesukile kuFaro, bafica uMosi lo-Aroni bebalindele. <verse eid="EXO 5:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="EXO 5:21"/>Basebesithi, “<char style="nd">uThixo</char> kalikhangele alahlulele. Selenze ukuthi senyanyeke kuFaro lakuziphathamandla zakhe, lafaka inkemba ezandleni zabo ukuba basibulale.”<verse eid="EXO 5:21"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UNkulunkulu Uthembisa Ukukhululwa Kwabako-Israyeli</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="EXO 5:22"/>UMosi wabuyela <char style="nd">kuThixo</char> wathi kuye, “<char style="nd">Thixo</char>, kungani ulethe uhlupho ebantwini laba? Yiso yini isizatho sokungithuma. <verse eid="EXO 5:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="EXO 5:23"/>Selokhu ngaya kuFaro ukuyakhuluma ngebizo lakho, uselethe uhlupho ebantwini laba, njalo kawubahlenganga abantu bakho lakancane.”<verse eid="EXO 5:23"/></para>
  <chapter eid="EXO 5"/>
  <chapter number="6" style="c" sid="EXO 6"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="EXO 6:1"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wasesithi kuMosi, “Uzabona esengizakwenza kuFaro khathesi. Ngenxa yamandla esandla sami uzabavumela bahambe, ngenxa yamandla esandla sami uzabaxotsha elizweni lakhe.”<verse eid="EXO 6:1"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="EXO 6:2"/>UNkulunkulu waphinda wathi kuMosi, “<char style="nd">NginguThixo</char>. <verse eid="EXO 6:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="EXO 6:3"/>Ngazibonakalisa ku-Abhrahama, ku-Isaka lakuJakhobe njengoNkulunkulu uSomandla, kodwa ngegama lami elithi <char style="nd">Thixo</char> kangizange ngizibonakalise kubo. <verse eid="EXO 6:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="EXO 6:4"/>Ngaphinda ngenza isivumelwano labo ukuze ngibanike ilizwe leKhenani lapho ababehlala khona njengabezizweni. <verse eid="EXO 6:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="EXO 6:5"/>Phezu kwalokho, sengikuzwile ukububula kwabantu bako-Israyeli besebugqilini ngaphansi kwamaGibhithe, njalo sengikhumbule isivumelwano sami.<verse eid="EXO 6:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="EXO 6:6"/>Ngakho tshela abako-Israyeli ukuthi <char style="nd">nginguThixo</char>, njalo ngizalikhulula embusweni wamaGibhithe onzima, ngizalikhulula ukuze lingabi yizigqili zabo, njalo ngizalikhulula ngesandla eseluliweyo langezimangaliso. <verse eid="EXO 6:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="EXO 6:7"/>Ngizalemukela njengabantu bami njalo ngizakuba nguNkulunkulu wenu. Ngalokho lizakwazi ukuthi <char style="nd">nginguThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wenu owalikhupha embusweni olukhuni wamaGibhithe. Ngizalikhulula ukuze lingabi yizigqili zabo. <verse eid="EXO 6:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="EXO 6:8"/>Njalo ngizaliletha elizweni engafunga ngesandla sami esiphakemeyo ukulinika u-Abhrahama, u-Isaka loJakhobe. Ngizalinika lona ukuze libe ngelenu. Mina <char style="nd">nginguThixo</char>.”<verse eid="EXO 6:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="EXO 6:9"/>UMosi wabika lokhu kwabako-Israyeli, kodwa kabazange bamlalele ngenxa yokudangala kwabo ebugqilini obulochuku.<verse eid="EXO 6:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="EXO 6:10"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wasesithi kuMosi, <verse eid="EXO 6:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="EXO 6:11"/>“Hamba uyetshela uFaro inkosi yaseGibhithe ukuthi avumele abako-Israyeli baphume elizweni lakhe.”<verse eid="EXO 6:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="EXO 6:12"/>Kodwa uMosi wathi <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>, “Nxa abako-Israyeli bengangilaleli, kuyini okungenza ukuthi uFaro angilalele, njengoba ngikhuluma ngigagasa?”<verse eid="EXO 6:12"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Umbhalo Wendlu Yakwabo KaMosi Lo-Aroni</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="EXO 6:13"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wakhuluma loMosi lo-Aroni mayelana labako-Israyeli loFaro inkosi yaseGibhithe wabalaya ukuthi bavumele abantu bako-Israyeli ukuthi baphume eGibhithe.<verse eid="EXO 6:13"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="EXO 6:14"/>Laba babezinhloko zezindlu zaboyise:</para>
  <para style="b" vid="EXO 6:14"/>
  <para style="li1" vid="EXO 6:14">Amadodana kaRubheni, izibulo lika-Israyeli ayeyila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="EXO 6:14">uHanokhi, uPhalu, uHezironi, loKhami.</para>
  <para style="li4" vid="EXO 6:14">Laba babengabosendo lukaRubheni.<verse eid="EXO 6:14"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="EXO 6:15"/>Amadodana kaSimiyoni ayeyila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="EXO 6:15">uJemuyeli, uJamini, u-Ohadi, uJakhini, uZohari, loShawuli olonina oweyengumKhenani.</para>
  <para style="li4" vid="EXO 6:15">Laba babengabosendo lukaSimiyoni.<verse eid="EXO 6:15"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="EXO 6:16"/>La ngamabizo amadodana kaLevi ngokwemibhalo yabo:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="EXO 6:16">uGeshoni, uKhohathi loMerari.</para>
  <para style="li4" vid="EXO 6:16">ULevi waphila iminyaka elikhulu elilamatshumi amathathu lesikhombisa (137).<verse eid="EXO 6:16"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="EXO 6:17"/>Amadodana kaGeshoni ngezizukulwana zawo ayeyila:</para>
  <para style="li3" vid="EXO 6:17">uLibhini, uShimeyi, lemuli zabo.<verse eid="EXO 6:17"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="EXO 6:18"/>Amadodana kaKhohathi ayeyila:</para>
  <para style="li3" vid="EXO 6:18">u-Amramu, u-Izihari, uHebhroni lo-Uziyeli.</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="EXO 6:18">UKhohathi waphila iminyaka elikhulu elilamatshumi amathathu lantathu (133).<verse eid="EXO 6:18"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="EXO 6:19"/>Amadodana kaMerari ayeyila:</para>
  <para style="li3" vid="EXO 6:19">uMahili loMushi.</para>
  <para style="li4" vid="EXO 6:19">Laba babengabosendo lukaLevi, ngokwemibhalo yabo.<verse eid="EXO 6:19"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="EXO 6:20"/>U-Amramu wathatha uJokhebhedi owayengudadewabo kayise. Wamzalela u-Aroni loMosi.</para>
  <para style="li4" vid="EXO 6:20">U-Amramu waphila iminyaka elikhulu elilamatshumi amathathu lesikhombisa (137).<verse eid="EXO 6:20"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="EXO 6:21"/>Amadodana ka-Izihari ayeyila;</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="EXO 6:21">uKhora, uNefegi loZikhiri.<verse eid="EXO 6:21"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="EXO 6:22"/>Amadodana ka-Uziyeli ayeyila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="EXO 6:22">uMishayeli, u-Elizafani loSithiri.<verse eid="EXO 6:22"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="EXO 6:23"/>U-Aroni wathatha u-Elishebha indodakazi ka-Aminadabi. U-Elishebha wayengudadewabo kaNahashoni. Wamzalela uNadabi, u-Abhihu, u-Eliyazari lo-Ithamari.<verse eid="EXO 6:23"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="EXO 6:24"/>Amadodana kaKhora ayeyila;</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="EXO 6:24">u-Asiri, u-Elikhana lo-Abhiyasafi.</para>
  <para style="li4" vid="EXO 6:24">Laba babengabosendo lukaKhora.<verse eid="EXO 6:24"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="EXO 6:25"/>U-Eliyazari indodana ka-Aroni wathatha omunye wamadodakazi kaPhuthiyeli. Wamzalela uFinehasi.</para>
  <para style="b" vid="EXO 6:25"/>
  <para style="li4" vid="EXO 6:25">Laba-ke yibo ababengabakhokheli bezimuli zakoLevi, ngendlu yinye ngayinye.<verse eid="EXO 6:25"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="EXO 6:26"/>Yibo labo o-Aroni loMosi <char style="nd">uThixo</char> athi kubo, “Khokhelani abantu bami bako-Israyeli libakhuphe elizweni laseGibhithe ngamakhulu abo.” <verse eid="EXO 6:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="EXO 6:27"/>Yibo laba abaya kuFaro inkosi yaseGibhithe mayelana lokukhupha abantu bako-Israyeli eGibhithe. Kwakuyibo oMosi lo-Aroni.<verse eid="EXO 6:27"/></para>
  <para style="s1">U-Aroni Ukhulumela UMosi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="EXO 6:28"/>Ngesikhathi <char style="nd">uThixo</char> ekhuluma loMosi eGibhithe, <verse eid="EXO 6:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="EXO 6:29"/>wathi kuye, “<char style="nd">NginguThixo</char>. Tshela uFaro inkosi yaseGibhithe yonke into engikutshela yona.”<verse eid="EXO 6:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="EXO 6:30"/>Kodwa uMosi wathi <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>, “Njengoba ngikhuluma ngigagasa, kambe kuyini okungenza ukuthi uFaro azihluphe ngokungilalela?”<verse eid="EXO 6:30"/></para>
  <chapter eid="EXO 6"/>
  <chapter number="7" style="c" sid="EXO 7"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="EXO 7:1"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wasesithi kuMosi, “Khangela, sengikwenze wafana loNkulunkulu kuFaro, njalo umfowenu u-Aroni uzakuba ngumphrofethi wakho. <verse eid="EXO 7:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="EXO 7:2"/>Uzakhuluma konke engizakulaya khona njalo umfowenu u-Aroni uzatshela uFaro ukuthi avumele abako-Israyeli ukuba basuke elizweni lakhe. <verse eid="EXO 7:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="EXO 7:3"/>Kodwa ngizakwenza inhliziyo kaFaro ibe lukhuni, njalo lanxa ngizakwandisa izimangaliso zami elizweni laseGibhithe, <verse eid="EXO 7:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="EXO 7:4"/>kasoze alilalele. Sekunjalo ngizakwelula isandla sami phezu kweGibhithe, njalo ngezenzo zami zokwahlulela ezilamandla, ngizakwahlukanisa abantu. <verse eid="EXO 7:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="EXO 7:5"/>Njalo abantu baseGibhithe bazakwazi ukuthi ngempela mina <char style="nd">nginguThixo</char> lapho sengiselula isandla sami phezu kweGibhithe, besengikhupha abako-Israyeli kulelolizwe.”<verse eid="EXO 7:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="EXO 7:6"/>UMosi lo-Aroni benza njengokulaywa kwabo <char style="nd">nguThixo</char>. <verse eid="EXO 7:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="EXO 7:7"/>UMosi wayeleminyaka engamatshumi ayisificaminwembili ubudala, u-Aroni wayeleminyaka engamatshumi ayisificaminwembili lantathu ngesikhathi bekhuluma loFaro.<verse eid="EXO 7:7"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Intonga Ka-Aroni Iba Yinyoka</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="EXO 7:8"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wathi kuMosi lo-Aroni, <verse eid="EXO 7:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="EXO 7:9"/>“Nxa uFaro angathi kini limenzele isimangaliso, wena uzakuthi ku-Aroni, ‘Thatha intonga yakho uyiphose phambi kukaFaro,’ izaphenduka ibe yinyoka.”<verse eid="EXO 7:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="EXO 7:10"/>Ngakho uMosi lo-Aroni baya kuFaro. Bafika benza njengokulaywa kwabo <char style="nd">nguThixo</char>. U-Aroni waphosa intonga yakhe phansi phambi kukaFaro lezikhulu zakhe, yaphenduka yaba yinyoka. <verse eid="EXO 7:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="EXO 7:11"/>UFaro wasebiza izanuse lezinyanga zaseGibhithe. Lazo zenza izimanga ngendlela efanayo. <verse eid="EXO 7:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="EXO 7:12"/>Bonke baphosela intonga zabo phansi zaphenduka zaba zinyoka. Kodwa inyoka ka-Aroni yaziginya zonke izinyoka. <verse eid="EXO 7:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="EXO 7:13"/>Kodwa-ke, lanxa kwabanjalo, inhliziyo kaFaro yala ilokhu ilukhuni; njengoba <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wayetshilo.<verse eid="EXO 7:13"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Uhlupho Lwegazi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="EXO 7:14"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wasesithi kuMosi, “Inhliziyo kaFaro ilukhuni; uyala ukuthi abantu bahambe. <verse eid="EXO 7:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="EXO 7:15"/>Yana kuFaro ekuseni, ngesikhathi esehlela emfuleni. Ubokuma okhunjini lomfula uNayili, umhlangabeze uphethe intonga eyaphenduka yaba yinyoka. <verse eid="EXO 7:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="EXO 7:16"/>Ubokuthi kuye, ‘<char style="nd">uThixo</char>, uNkulunkulu wamaHebheru ungithumile njalo kuwe ukuba ngizekutshela ukuthi: Vumela abantu bami ukuthi bahambe, ukuze bayengikhonza enkangala. Kodwa kuze kube khathesi kawukalaleli. <verse eid="EXO 7:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="EXO 7:17"/><char style="nd">UThixo</char> uthi, Ngalokhu uzakwazi ukuthi <char style="nd">nginguThixo</char>: Ngentonga esesandleni sami ngizatshaya amanzi kaNayili njalo azaphenduka abe ligazi. <verse eid="EXO 7:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="EXO 7:18"/>Inhlanzi kuNayili zizakufa, amanzi omfula azanuka athi phu, ngakho abantu baseGibhithe abangeke babe besawanatha.’ ”<verse eid="EXO 7:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="EXO 7:19"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wasesithi kuMosi, “Tshela u-Aroni uthi ‘thatha intonga yakho welulele isandla sakho phezu kwamanzi eGibhithe, lakuyo yonke imifula yakhona lemisele yamanzi, amaxhaphozi, lamachibi, wonke amanzi alapho azaphenduka abe ligazi.’ Igazi lizagcwala eGibhithe lasezinkonxeni zezigodo lasezitsheni zamatshe.”<verse eid="EXO 7:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="EXO 7:20"/>UMosi lo-Aroni benza njengokulaywa kwabo <char style="nd">nguThixo</char>. Waphakamisa intonga yakhe phambi kukaFaro lezikhulu zakhe watshaya amanzi kaNayili aphenduka aba ligazi. <verse eid="EXO 7:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="EXO 7:21"/>Inhlanzi zikaNayili zafa. Umfula wanuka kubi okokuthi abaseGibhithe babengeke bawanathe amanzi akhona. Igazi laseligcwele indawo yonke.<verse eid="EXO 7:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="EXO 7:22"/>Kodwa izanuse zaseGibhithe lazo ngemilingo yazo zenza izimanga ezifananayo. Ngalokho inhliziyo kaFaro yala ilokhu ilukhuni. Kabalalelanga oMosi lo-Aroni njengoba <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wayevele etshilo. <verse eid="EXO 7:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="EXO 7:23"/>UFaro wabuyela esigodlweni sakhe engakunaki lokho. <verse eid="EXO 7:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="EXO 7:24"/>Sekunjalo abaseGibhithe bemba imithombo okhunjini lomfula uNayili ukuba bathole amanzi okunatha, ngoba babengeke babe besawanatha awomfula.<verse eid="EXO 7:24"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Uhlupho Lwamaxoxo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="EXO 7:25"/>Kwedlula insuku eziyisikhombisa ngemva kokuba <char style="nd">uThixo</char> enze amanzi kaNayili aba ligazi.<verse eid="EXO 7:25"/></para>
  <chapter eid="EXO 7"/>
  <chapter number="8" style="c" sid="EXO 8"/>
  <para style="nb">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="EXO 8:1"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wathi kuMosi, “Buyela njalo kuFaro uthi kuye, ‘<char style="nd">UThixo</char> uthi, Vumela abantu bami bahambe bayengikhonza. <verse eid="EXO 8:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="EXO 8:2"/>Ungala ngizathumela uhlupho lwamaxoxo elizweni lakho. <verse eid="EXO 8:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="EXO 8:3"/>Umfula uNayili uzagcwala amaxoxo. Azangena esigodlweni sakho lasendlini yakho yokulala, lasembhedeni wakho; angene lezindlini zezikhulu zakho lezabantu bakho. Azagcwala ezindaweni zenu zokuphekela, lasemiganwini yenu yokuvubela izinkwa. <verse eid="EXO 8:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="EXO 8:4"/>Amaxoxo la azakuba phezu kwakho laphezu kwabantu bakho kanye lezikhulu zakho.’ ”<verse eid="EXO 8:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="EXO 8:5"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wasesithi kuMosi, “Tshela u-Aroni akhombele intonga emifuleni, lasezifudlaneni lasezizibeni zonke zaseGibhithe ukuze kube lamaxoxo ezindaweni zonke zelizwe.”<verse eid="EXO 8:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="EXO 8:6"/>U-Aroni welulela isandla sakhe emanzini eGibhithe, amaxoxo agcwala ilizwe lonke. <verse eid="EXO 8:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="EXO 8:7"/>Kodwa-ke izanuse lazo zenzanjalo ngemilingo yazo yensitha, zenza kwaba lamaxoxo elizweni lonke leGibhithe.<verse eid="EXO 8:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="EXO 8:8"/>UFaro wabiza uMosi lo-Aroni wathi kubo, “Ncengani <char style="nd">uThixo</char> asuse amaxoxo kimi lebantwini bami, lami ngizavumela abantu bakhe ukuba bahambe bayenikela imihlatshelo <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>.”<verse eid="EXO 8:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="EXO 8:9"/>UMosi wathi, kuFaro “Ngikutshiya kuwe ukuba ubeke isikhathi sokuthi ngikukhulekele wena lezikhulu zakho labantu bakho ukuze lina lezindlu zenu lilanyulelwe emaxoxweni, ngaphandle kwalawo azasala kuNayili.”<verse eid="EXO 8:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="EXO 8:10"/>UFaro wathi, “Kwenze kusasa.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="EXO 8:10">UMosi wasesithi, “Kuzakuba njengokutsho kwakho ukuze ukwazi ukuthi kakho omunye <char style="nd">onjengoThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wethu. <verse eid="EXO 8:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="EXO 8:11"/>Amaxoxo azasuka kini lezindlini zenu lezezikhulu labantu benu abesesala emfuleni uNayili kuphela.”<verse eid="EXO 8:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="EXO 8:12"/>UMosi lo-Aroni basuka kuFaro. UMosi wakhala <char style="nd">kuThixo</char> ukuba asuse amaxoxo ayewathumele kuFaro. <verse eid="EXO 8:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="EXO 8:13"/><char style="nd">UThixo</char> wenza lokho uMosi ayekucelile. Amaxoxo afa ezindlini lemagumeni lemasimini. <verse eid="EXO 8:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="EXO 8:14"/>Bawabuthelela aba zinqwabanqwaba; ilizwe lonke lanuka phu ngamaxoxo. <verse eid="EXO 8:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="EXO 8:15"/>Kodwa uFaro ebona ukuthi udubo soluphungukile womisa inhliziyo yakhe wala ukulalela uMosi lo-Aroni njengokwakuvele kukhulunywe <char style="nd">nguThixo</char>.<verse eid="EXO 8:15"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Uhlupho Lwentwala</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="EXO 8:16"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wasesithi kuMosi, “Tshela u-Aroni uthi, ‘Phakamisa intonga yakho utshaye uthuli lomhlabathi,’ uthuli luzaphenduka lube zintwala elizweni lonke laseGibhithe.” <verse eid="EXO 8:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="EXO 8:17"/>Benza njengokulaywa kwabo, kwathi u-Aroni eselule isandla sakhe ephethe intonga watshaya uthuli, intwala zahlasela abantu lezifuyo zabo. Uthuli lonke eGibhithe lwaphenduka lwaba zintwala. <verse eid="EXO 8:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="EXO 8:18"/>Izanuse lazo zazama ukwenza intwala ngemilingo yazo, kodwa zehluleka.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="EXO 8:18">Njengoba intwala zazisebantwini lezinyamazaneni, <verse eid="EXO 8:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="EXO 8:19"/>izanuse zathi kuFaro, “Lokhu kungumunwe kaNkulunkulu.” Kodwa inhliziyo kaFaro yayilukhuni, kabalalelanga njengoba <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wayevele etshilo.<verse eid="EXO 8:19"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Uhlupho Lwempukane</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="EXO 8:20"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wasesithi kuMosi, “Kusasa ubovuka ekuseni kakhulu uhlangabeze uFaro lapho esiya emanzini. Ubokuthi kuye, ‘Vumela abantu bami bahambe bayengikhonza. <verse eid="EXO 8:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="EXO 8:21"/>Ungala, ngizathumela umtshitshi wempukane kuwe, ebantwini bakho lezindlini zenu. Izindlu zabantu baseGibhithe zizagcwala impukane lomhlabathi ugcwale zona.<verse eid="EXO 8:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="EXO 8:22"/>Kodwa ngalolosuku akuyikuba njalo eGosheni lapho okuhlala khona abantu bami. Akuyikuba lemitshitshi yempukane khona. Ngakho uzakwazi ukuthi mina <char style="nd">nginguThixo</char> womhlaba wonke. <verse eid="EXO 8:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="EXO 8:23"/>Ngizakwenza kube lomahluko phakathi kwabantu bami labantu bakho. Lesisimangaliso sizakwenzakala kusasa.’ ”<verse eid="EXO 8:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="EXO 8:24"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wenza njengoba wayetshilo. Umtshitshi wempukane ezinengi okwesabeka kakhulukazi zagcwala esigodlweni sikaFaro lasezindlini zezikhulu zakhe, lakulo lonke ilizwe laseGibhithe; zalitshabalalisa.<verse eid="EXO 8:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="EXO 8:25"/>UFaro wabiza uMosi lo-Aroni. Wathi kubo, “Hambani liyehlabela uNkulunkulu wenu likhonapha kulelilizwe.”<verse eid="EXO 8:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="EXO 8:26"/>UMosi waphendula wathi, “Lokho akulunganga. Imihlatshelo yethu esinikela ngayo <char style="nd">kuThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wethu iyanengeka ebantwini beGibhithe. Singanikela ngeminikelo abayizondayo kambe kabayikusitshaya ngamatshe na? <verse eid="EXO 8:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="EXO 8:27"/>Kumele sithathe uhambo lwezizinsuku ezintathu siye enkangala siyemhlabela khonale <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wethu njengokusilaya kwakhe.”<verse eid="EXO 8:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="EXO 8:28"/>UFaro wathi, “Ngizalivumela lihambe liyenikela imihlatshelo <char style="nd">kuThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wenu enkangala, kodwa lingayi khatshana. Khathesi ngikhulekelani.”<verse eid="EXO 8:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="EXO 8:29"/>UMosi waphendula wathi, “Ngizakuthi ngisanda kusuka ngikhuleke <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>, njalo kusasa umtshitshi wempukane uzasuka kuFaro, ezikhulwini zakhe lebantwini bakhe. Kodwa uFaro kangasikhohlisi futhi asuke angasavumeli abantu ukuba bahambe bayenikela imihlatshelo <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>.”<verse eid="EXO 8:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="EXO 8:30"/>Emva kwalokho uMosi wasuka kuFaro wasekhuleka <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>. <verse eid="EXO 8:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="EXO 8:31"/><char style="nd">UThixo</char> wenza lokho okwakucelwe nguMosi, umtshitshi wempukane wanyamalala kuFaro lezikhulu zakhe labantu bakhe, akwaze kwasala leyodwa. <verse eid="EXO 8:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="EXO 8:32"/>Kodwa langalesosikhathi uFaro wenza inhliziyo yakhe yaba lukhuni kazabavumela abako-Israyeli ukuba bahambe.<verse eid="EXO 8:32"/></para>
  <chapter eid="EXO 8"/>
  <chapter number="9" style="c" sid="EXO 9"/>
  <para style="s1">Uhlupho Ezifuyweni</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="EXO 9:1"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wasesithi kuMosi, “Yana kuFaro uthi kuye, ‘Nanku okutshiwo <char style="nd">nguThixo</char>, uNkulunkulu wamaHebheru, ukuthi, “Yekela abantu bami bahambe, ukuze bayengikhonza.” <verse eid="EXO 9:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="EXO 9:2"/>Ungabalela ukuthi bahambe ube ulokhu ubabambile <verse eid="EXO 9:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="EXO 9:3"/><char style="nd">uThixo</char> uzakwehlisela isifo esibi ezifuyweni zakho emadlelweni, amabhiza enu, obabhemi, amakamela, inkomo, izimvu lembuzi. <verse eid="EXO 9:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="EXO 9:4"/>Kodwa <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uzakwenza umahluko phakathi kwezifuyo zabako-Israyeli lezamaGibhithe ukuze kungafi lasinye isifuyo sabako-Israyeli.’ ”<verse eid="EXO 9:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="EXO 9:5"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wamisa isikhathi esithile wathi, “<char style="nd">uThixo</char> uzakwenza lokhu kusasa elizweni leli.” <verse eid="EXO 9:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="EXO 9:6"/>Lakanye ngelanga elilandelayo <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wakwenza, zonke izifuyo zamaGibhithe zafa, kodwa akufanga ngitsho lasinye isifuyo sabako-Israyeli. <verse eid="EXO 9:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="EXO 9:7"/>UFaro wathuma amadoda ukuyahlola umonakalo afumana ukuthi kwakungafanga sifuyo lasinye sabako-Israyeli. Kodwa inhliziyo yakhe yala ilokhu ilukhuni, wabalela abantu ukuthi bahambe.<verse eid="EXO 9:7"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Uhlupho Lwamathumba</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="EXO 9:8"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wasesithi kuMosi lo-Aroni, “Thathani umlotha omlutshwana eziko lifike kuFaro uMosi awuhazele emoyeni phambi kwakhe. <verse eid="EXO 9:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="EXO 9:9"/>Uzakuba luthuli phezu kwelizwe lonke laseGibhithe, lapho-ke kuzaphihlika amathumba amabi ebantwini lasezinyamazaneni kulolonke ilizwe.”<verse eid="EXO 9:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="EXO 9:10"/>Ngakho bathatha umlotha eziko baya kuFaro. UMosi wawuhazela emoyeni, abantu bonke lezinyamazana zonke kwamilwa ngamathumba aphihlikayo. <verse eid="EXO 9:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="EXO 9:11"/>Izangoma zehluleka ukumisana loMosi ngenxa yamathumba ayezibulala kanye lamaGibhithe wonke. <verse eid="EXO 9:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="EXO 9:12"/>Kodwa <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wenza yaba lukhuni inhliziyo kaFaro wala ukulalela uMosi lo-Aroni njengoba <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wayevele etshilo kuMosi.<verse eid="EXO 9:12"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Uhlupho Lwesiqhotho</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="EXO 9:13"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wasesithi kuMosi, “Vuka ekuseni kakhulu uye kuFaro, uthi kuye, ‘Nanku okutshiwo <char style="nd">nguThixo</char>, uNkulunkulu wamaHebheru, uthi, yekela abantu bami bahambe ukuze bayengikhonza. <verse eid="EXO 9:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="EXO 9:14"/>Kungenjalo kulesisikhathi ngizakwehlisa ubunzima bezinhlupho zami obulesihluku phezu kwakho, phezu kwezinceku zakho labantu bakho ukuze lazi ukuthi kakho omunye onjengami emhlabeni wonke. <verse eid="EXO 9:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="EXO 9:15"/>Kunje nje ngabe sengiselulile isandla sami ngakutshaya kanye labantu bakho ngesifo ebesizakucitsha emhlabeni. <verse eid="EXO 9:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="EXO 9:16"/>Kodwa ngikuphephisile ngayonale injongo yokuthi ngikubonise amandla ami, lokuthi ibizo lami lifakazwe kuwo wonke umhlaba. <verse eid="EXO 9:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="EXO 9:17"/>Ulokhu utshingela abantu bami ubalela ukuthi bahambe. <verse eid="EXO 9:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="EXO 9:18"/>Ngalokho-ke ngalesisikhathi kusasa ngizakwehlisa isiqhotho esingakaze sehlele eGibhithe lilokhu lababala laba khona ilizwe leli. <verse eid="EXO 9:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="EXO 9:19"/>Wohle nje uthumezele ilizwi lokuthi izifuyo zakho lakho konke olakho emadlelweni kubuyiswe kuvalelwe esibayeni esivikelweyo ngoba isiqhotho leso sizatshaya umuntu wonke lesifuyo sonke esingabuthwanga nxa silokhu sisegangeni, konke kuzakufa.’ ”<verse eid="EXO 9:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="EXO 9:20"/>Lezozikhulu zikaFaro ezalesabayo ilizwi <char style="nd">likaThixo</char> zaphanga zangenisa izigqili zazo lezifuyo ngaphakathi. <verse eid="EXO 9:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="EXO 9:21"/>Labo abangalinanzanga ilizwi <char style="nd">likaThixo</char> izigqili zabo lezifuyo zabo bakuyekela kusegangeni.<verse eid="EXO 9:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="EXO 9:22"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wasesithi kuMosi, “Yelula isandla sakho siye phezulu ukuze kune isiqhotho kulolonke iGibhithe, phezu kwabantu lezinyamazana laphezu kwakho konke okukhulayo emasimini aseGibhithe.” <verse eid="EXO 9:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="EXO 9:23"/>UMosi wonela ukukhomba ngentonga yakhe phezulu, <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wehlisa umdumo lesiqhotho, umbane wabaneka phansi emhlabathini. Ngakho <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wanisa isiqhotho elizweni laseGibhithe. <verse eid="EXO 9:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="EXO 9:24"/>Isiqhotho satshaya umbane wabaneka yonke indawo. Sasingakaze sibe khona isiphepho esinjalo sekulokhu isizwe saseGibhithe saba khona. <verse eid="EXO 9:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="EXO 9:25"/>Isiqhotho satshaya saqothula yonke into egangeni, abantu lezinyamazana; sabhuqa konke okukhulayo emasimini, saphundla izihlahla zonke eGibhithe. <verse eid="EXO 9:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="EXO 9:26"/>Indawo eyasilayo yiGosheni lapho okwakulabako-Israyeli khona.<verse eid="EXO 9:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="EXO 9:27"/>UFaro wasebiza uMosi lo-Aroni. Wathi kubo, “Okwamanje ngenze isono. <char style="nd">UThixo</char> ulungile, kukanti mina labantu bami siyizoni. <verse eid="EXO 9:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="EXO 9:28"/>Khulekani <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>, ngoba ukukhwaza kwezulu lesiqhotho sekwanele. Ngizaliyekela lihambe; akusadingeki ukuthi lihlale.”<verse eid="EXO 9:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="EXO 9:29"/>UMosi waphendula wathi. “Nxa sengiphumile edolobheni ngizavula izandla zami ngikhuleke <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>. Ukuduma kuzakhawula kungabe kusaba lesiqhotho, ukuze wazi ukuthi umhlaba <char style="nd">ngokaThixo</char>. <verse eid="EXO 9:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="EXO 9:30"/>Kodwa ngiyazi ukuthi wena lezikhulu zakho lilokhu lingamesabi <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uNkulunkulu.”<verse eid="EXO 9:30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="EXO 9:31"/>(Amabele lebhali kwabhuqwa nya ngoba amabele ayeselezikhwebu lophoko selumumethe. <verse eid="EXO 9:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="EXO 9:32"/>Ingqoloyi lenyawuthi khona kakuthintwanga ngoba kuvuthwa muva.)<verse eid="EXO 9:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="EXO 9:33"/>UMosi wasesuka kuFaro waphuma edolobheni. Welulela izandla zakhe <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>; ukuduma kwezulu lesiqhotho kwakhawula, izulu alabe lisana emhlabeni. <verse eid="EXO 9:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="EXO 9:34"/>Kwathi uFaro ebona ukuthi izulu lesiqhotho lokukhwaza kwezulu kwasekukhawule waphinda wenza isono: Yena lezikhulu zakhe benza inhliziyo zabo zaba lukhuni. <verse eid="EXO 9:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="EXO 9:35"/>Ngakho inhliziyo kaFaro yaba lukhuni akaze avumela abako-Israyeli ukuthi bahambe njengoba <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wayetshilo ngoMosi.<verse eid="EXO 9:35"/></para>
  <chapter eid="EXO 9"/>
  <chapter number="10" style="c" sid="EXO 10"/>
  <para style="s1">Uhlupho Lwentethe</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="EXO 10:1"/>Ngakho <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wasesithi kuMosi, “Hamba kuFaro, ngoba sengiyenze yaba lukhuni inhliziyo yakhe lezinhliziyo zezikhulu zakhe ukuze ngenze izimanga zami kubo <verse eid="EXO 10:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="EXO 10:2"/>ukuze lilandisele abantwabenu labazukulu benu ukuthi ngabahlukuluza njani abeGibhithe lokuthi ngabenzela izimanga, khona lizakwazi ukuthi mina <char style="nd">nginguThixo</char>.”<verse eid="EXO 10:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="EXO 10:3"/>Ngakho oMosi lo-Aroni baya kuFaro bathi kuye, “Nanku okutshiwo <char style="nd">nguThixo</char>, uNkulunkulu wamaHebheru: ‘Uzakwala kuze kube nini ukuzithoba phambi kwami? Yekela abantu bami bahambe ukuze bayengikhonza. <verse eid="EXO 10:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="EXO 10:4"/>Nxa usala ukuthi bahambe ngizaletha intethe elizweni lakho kusasa. <verse eid="EXO 10:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="EXO 10:5"/>Zizakwembesa wonke umhlabathi usale ungasabonakali. Zizakudla ziphundle du lalokho okuncinyane okwatshiywa yisiqhotho kanye lezihlahla zonke ezikhula egangeni. <verse eid="EXO 10:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="EXO 10:6"/>Zizagcwala ezindlini zakho lezezikhulu zakho zonke lezamaGibhithe, into oyihlo labokhokho bakho abangazange bayibone selokhu bahlala kulelilizwe kuze kube manje.’ ” Khonapho uMosi wabe efulathela esuka kuFaro.<verse eid="EXO 10:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="EXO 10:7"/>Izikhulu zikaFaro zathi kuye, “Koze kube nini na indoda le ilokhu iyisifu kithi? Yekela abantu bahambe bayekhonza <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wabo. Ulokhu ungaboni yini ukuthi ilizwe leGibhithe selichithekile?”<verse eid="EXO 10:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="EXO 10:8"/>UMosi lo-Aroni basebebuyiswa kuFaro. Wathi, “Hambani liyokhonza <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wenu. Kanti konje ngobani abahambayo?”<verse eid="EXO 10:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="EXO 10:9"/>UMosi waphendula wathi, “Sizahamba labatsha labadala bethu; lamadodana lamadodakazi ethu, lemihlambi yethu ngoba kumele senzele <char style="nd">uThixo</char> umkhosi.”<verse eid="EXO 10:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="EXO 10:10"/>UFaro wathi, “<char style="nd">uThixo</char> kabe lani, kumbe likhumbula ukuthi ngizaliyekela lihambe labesifazane labantwana! Kusobala ukuthi liqonde ukwenza okubi. <verse eid="EXO 10:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="EXO 10:11"/>Hatshi! Akuhambe amadoda kuphela; amkhonze <char style="nd">uThixo</char> ngoba phela yikho ebelivele likukhalela.” Ngakho uMosi lo-Aroni basebexotshwa phambi kukaFaro.<verse eid="EXO 10:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="EXO 10:12"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wasesithi kuMosi, “Yelula isandla sakho phezu kweGibhithe ukuze kwehle isikhongwane, izintethe, kulolonke ilizwe zidle zigugude konke okukhulayo emangweni, konke lokho okwatshiywa yisiqhotho.”<verse eid="EXO 10:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="EXO 10:13"/>UMosi wayiphakamisa intonga yakhe phezu kweGibhithe, <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wasequbula umoya wempumalanga wavunguza elizweni lonke ngalelolanga lobusuku bakhona. Ekuseni umoya waletha izintethe. <verse eid="EXO 10:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="EXO 10:14"/>Zalihlasela lonke elaseGibhithe zagcwala silikici kuzozonke izindawo zelizwe ngobunengi bazo. Kwakungakaze kube lesikhongwane esingako njalo singeyikufa saba khona njalo lanini. <verse eid="EXO 10:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="EXO 10:15"/>Intethe lezo zavala umhlabathi waba mnyama bhuqe. Zatshaya zabhuqa konke okwakusele ngesikhathi sesiqhotho, konke okwakukhula emangweni kanye lezithelo zezihlahla. Akusalanga lutho oluluhlaza ezihlahleni loba isilimo bani kulolonke ilizwe laseGibhithe.<verse eid="EXO 10:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="EXO 10:16"/>UFaro waphanga wabiza uMosi lo-Aroni wathi, “Ngonile <char style="nd">kuThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wenu lakini. <verse eid="EXO 10:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="EXO 10:17"/>Manje-ke ngixolelani njalo libuye likhuleke <char style="nd">kuThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wenu ukuthi asuse loluhlupho olubhubhisayo.”<verse eid="EXO 10:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="EXO 10:18"/>UMosi wasesuka kuFaro wayakhuleka <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>. <verse eid="EXO 10:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="EXO 10:19"/><char style="nd">UThixo</char> wasewuguqula umoya waphephetha uvelela entshonalanga ulamandla. Wazidudula izintethe wazitshovela oLwandle Olubomvu. Akusalanga ntethe layinye loba ngaphi eGibhithe. <verse eid="EXO 10:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="EXO 10:20"/>Kodwa <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wayenza yaba lukhuni inhliziyo kaFaro, kaze abavumela abako-Israyeli ukuthi bahambe.<verse eid="EXO 10:20"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Uhlupho Lomnyama</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="EXO 10:21"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wasesithi kuMosi, “Yelulela isandla sakho emkhathini ukwenzela ukuthi umnyama wembese iGibhithe lonke, umnyama obambekayo.” <verse eid="EXO 10:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="EXO 10:22"/>Ngakho uMosi waseselulela isandla sakhe phezulu, kwathi gubu umnyama okhasa phansi, walembesa lonke elaseGibhithe okwensuku ezintathu. <verse eid="EXO 10:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="EXO 10:23"/>Kakho owayesabona omunye njalo kakho owayengasuka endaweni yakhe okwalezonsuku ezintathu. Kodwa ama-Israyeli ayelakho ukukhanya ezindaweni ayehlala kuzo.<verse eid="EXO 10:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="EXO 10:24"/>UFaro wasebiza uMosi wathi, “Hambani liyekhonza <char style="nd">uThixo</char>. Ngitsho labesifazane benu labantwana hambani labo; litshiye kuphela imihlambi yezifuyo zenu.”<verse eid="EXO 10:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="EXO 10:25"/>Kodwa uMosi wathi, “Kumele usivumele ukuthi siyokwenza imihlatshelo leminikelo yokutshiswa <char style="nd">kuThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wethu. <verse eid="EXO 10:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="EXO 10:26"/>Izifuyo zethu lazo zimele zihambe lathi kungasali lasinye. Kumele siyosebenzisa ezinye zazo ekukhonzeni <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wethu. Phela kasisoze sazi ukuthi sizasebenzisa siphi isifuyo ukukhonza <char style="nd">uThixo</char> size sifike khonale.”<verse eid="EXO 10:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="EXO 10:27"/>Kodwa <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wayenza yaba lukhuni inhliziyo kaFaro, kaze afuna ukubayekela bahambe. <verse eid="EXO 10:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="EXO 10:28"/>UFaro wathi kuMosi, “Suka phambi kwami! Phinde ngikubone futhi. Mhla wangibona futhi ufile wena.”<verse eid="EXO 10:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="EXO 10:29"/>UMosi waphendula wathi, “Akube njengokuba usitsho. Phinde ungibone njalo lapha.”<verse eid="EXO 10:29"/></para>
  <chapter eid="EXO 10"/>
  <chapter number="11" style="c" sid="EXO 11"/>
  <para style="s1">Uhlupho Lokubulawa Kwamazibulo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="EXO 11:1"/>Ngalesosikhathi <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wathi kuMosi, “Sekusele ukuthi ngehlise uhlupho olulodwa kuFaro laphezu kweGibhithe. Ngemva kwalokho uzaliyekela lisuke lapha, njalo liphume eselixotsha lonke. <verse eid="EXO 11:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="EXO 11:2"/>Tshela abantu ukuthi amadoda labafazi ngokufananayo bacele kubomakhelwane babo izinto zesiliva legolide.” <verse eid="EXO 11:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="EXO 11:3"/>(<char style="nd">UThixo</char> wenza amaGibhithe aba lomusa ebantwini, loMosi uqobo wahlonitshwa kakhulu yizikhulu zikaFaro langabantu.)<verse eid="EXO 11:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="EXO 11:4"/>Ngakho uMosi wasesithi, “Nanku okutshiwo <char style="nd">nguThixo</char>: ‘Phakathi kobusuku ngizahambahamba kulolonke elaseGibhithe. <verse eid="EXO 11:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="EXO 11:5"/>Wonke owesilisa olizibulo eGibhithe uzakufa, kusukela ezibulweni likaFaro ohlezi esihlalweni sobukhosi kuthathe kanye lezibulo lesigqili sentombazana esisebenza ukuchola, kanye lamazibulo enkomo uqobo. <verse eid="EXO 11:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="EXO 11:6"/>Kuzakuba lesililo esikhulu eGibhithe lonke, isililo esingakaze sibe khona njalo esingayikuba khona lanini. <verse eid="EXO 11:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="EXO 11:7"/>Kodwa kwabako-Israyeli akuyikuba lanja ezakhonkotha umuntu loba inyamazana.’ Lapho-ke lizakwazi ukuthi <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uyawehlukanisa amaGibhithe kwabako-Israyeli. <verse eid="EXO 11:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="EXO 11:8"/>Zonke izikhulu zakho lezi zizakuza kimi zikhothamisele ubuso phansi phambi kwami zisithi, ‘Hambani, wena labo bonke abakulandelayo!’ Ngemva kwalokho ngizasuka.” UMosi wasesuka kuFaro elokhu ezonde evutha umlilo.<verse eid="EXO 11:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="EXO 11:9"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wayesetshilo kuMosi wathi, “UFaro uzaqinisa intamo, ukuze zande izimangaliso zami eGibhithe.” <verse eid="EXO 11:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="EXO 11:10"/>UMosi lo-Aroni bazenza zonke izimangaliso lezi emehlweni kaFaro, kodwa <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wayenza yaba lukhuni inhliziyo kaFaro kaze abavumela abako-Israyeli ukuthi baphume elizweni lakhe.<verse eid="EXO 11:10"/></para>
  <chapter eid="EXO 11"/>
  <chapter number="12" style="c" sid="EXO 12"/>
  <para style="s1">Umdabuko WePhasika LoMkhosi WeSinkwa EsingelaMvubelo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="EXO 12:1"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wathi kuMosi lo-Aroni beseGibhithe, <verse eid="EXO 12:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="EXO 12:2"/>“Inyanga le kayibe yinyanga yakuqala kini, inyanga yokuqala emnyakeni wenu. <verse eid="EXO 12:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="EXO 12:3"/>Tshelani bonke abomndeni ka-Israyeli ukuthi ngelanga letshumi lale inyanga indoda ngayinye kayithathele abomuzi wayo izinyane libe linye indlu ngendlu. <verse eid="EXO 12:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="EXO 12:4"/>Nxa abendlu bebalutshwana kakhulu ukuthi abangeke baliqede lelozinyane kababelane labomakhelwane abaseduze kwabo kusiya ngenani labo ukuthi bangaki. Kumele uphawule ukuthi kungadingeka izinyane elingakanani kusiya ngokuthi umuntu emunye angadla inyama engakanani. <verse eid="EXO 12:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="EXO 12:5"/>Kumele ukhethe amazinyane amaduna alomnyaka owodwa angelasici, njalo ungakhetha ezimvini loba embuzini. <verse eid="EXO 12:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="EXO 12:6"/>Agcine amazinyane lawo kuze kube lusuku lwetshumi lane lwenyanga, lapho isizwe sonke sako-Israyeli esizawahlaba khona nxa kuhwalala. <verse eid="EXO 12:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="EXO 12:7"/>Lapho-ke kuzamele bathathe igazi baligcobe emaceleni laphezulu kwemigubazi yalezozindlu abazadlela khona amazinyane. <verse eid="EXO 12:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="EXO 12:8"/>Ngalobobusuku kumele badle inyama eyoswe emlilweni, lesinkwa esingelamvubelo lemibhida ebabayo. <verse eid="EXO 12:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="EXO 12:9"/>Lingayidli inyama iluhlaza loba iphekwe ngamanzi, kodwa yoseni emlilweni konke lenhloko yakhona lamangqina kanye lezangaphakathi. <verse eid="EXO 12:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="EXO 12:10"/>Lingatshiyi lutho lwayo kuze kube sekuseni; kuthi nxa kukhona okuseleyo kwayo ekuseni kumele likutshise. <verse eid="EXO 12:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="EXO 12:11"/>Liboyidla inkalo zenu zibotshiwe, amanyathela egqokiwe lentonga zenu zisezandleni. Lidle ngokuphangisa; kuliPhasika <char style="nd">likaThixo</char>.<verse eid="EXO 12:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="EXO 12:12"/>Ngalobobusuku ngizadabula phakathi kweGibhithe ngibulala wonke amazibulo abantu lawezinyamazana njalo ngizakwahlulela bonke onkulunkulu bamaGibhithe. Mina <char style="nd">nginguThixo</char>. <verse eid="EXO 12:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="EXO 12:13"/>Igazi lizakuba yisibonakaliso sezindlu lapho elikhona lina; kuzakuthi ngingabona igazi ngedlule kini. Akulasijeziso esibhidlizayo esizalithinta lina nxa sengichitha iGibhithe.<verse eid="EXO 12:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="EXO 12:14"/>Leli akube lilanga lesikhumbuzo, kuthi zonke izizukulwane ezizayo ziligcine ngomkhosi omkhulu <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>, kube yisimiso sanini lanini. <verse eid="EXO 12:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="EXO 12:15"/>Okwensuku eziyisikhombisa kumele lidle isinkwa esingelamvubelo. Ngelanga lakuqala khuphani imvubelo ezindlini zenu, kuthi lowo odla loba yini elemvubelo ngelanga lakuqala kusiya kwelesikhombisa kumele akhutshwe ko-Israyeli. <verse eid="EXO 12:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="EXO 12:16"/>Ngosuku lwakuqala lenze umbuthano ongcwele, liphinde omunye ngosuku lwesikhombisa. Lingenzi msebenzi ngamalanga lawa ngaphandle kokulungisa ukudla kwabantu, yikho kodwa elingakwenza.<verse eid="EXO 12:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="EXO 12:17"/>Gcinani uMkhosi weSinkwa esingelaMvubelo ngoba kwakulilanga engehlukanisa ngalo amaviyo enu eGibhithe. Gcinani lelilanga njengesimiso sanini lanini kuzizukulwane ezizayo. <verse eid="EXO 12:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="EXO 12:18"/>Ngenyanga yakuqala kumele lidle isinkwa esingelamvubelo, kusukela kusihlwa ngelanga letshumi lane kuze kube kusihlwa ngelanga lamatshumi amabili lanye. <verse eid="EXO 12:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="EXO 12:19"/>Okwensuku eziyisikhombisa akumelanga kutholakale imvubelo ezindlini zenu. Akuthi lowo odla loba yini elemvubelo asuswe phakathi kwabantu bako-Israyeli, loba engowezizweni kumbe owosendo lwenu. <verse eid="EXO 12:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="EXO 12:20"/>Lingadli lutho olufakwe imvubelo. Loba kungaphi elihlala khona libokudla isinkwa esingelamvubelo.”<verse eid="EXO 12:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="EXO 12:21"/>Ngakho uMosi wasebiza bonke abadala bako-Israyeli wathi kubo, “Hambani khona manje liyokhetha amazinyane ezindlu zenu lihlabe izinyane lePhasika. <verse eid="EXO 12:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="EXO 12:22"/>Lithathe ilixha lehisophi liyigxamuze emganwini olegazi beselithatha elinye igazi liligcobe phezulu lakunxa zonke zomgubazi. Akungabikhona lamunye wenu ozaphuma emnyango wendlu yakhe kuze kuse. <verse eid="EXO 12:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="EXO 12:23"/>Lapho <char style="nd">uThixo</char> edabula phakathi kwelizwe ebulala amaGibhithe uzalibona igazi phezulu lemaceleni omgubazi, aceze awedlule lowomnyango angamvumeli umbhubhisi ukungena endlini alibulale.<verse eid="EXO 12:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="EXO 12:24"/>Lalelani imilayo le njengezimiso zaphakade kini lasezizukulwaneni zenu. <verse eid="EXO 12:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="EXO 12:25"/>Nxa lingangena elizweni <char style="nd">uThixo</char> azalinika lona njengokuthembisa kwakhe, liwugcine umkhosi lo. <verse eid="EXO 12:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="EXO 12:26"/>Nxa abantwabenu belibuza besithi, ‘Umkhosi lo ngowani?’ <verse eid="EXO 12:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="EXO 12:27"/>libatshele lithi, ‘UliPhasika lomhlatshelo <char style="nd">kaThixo</char> owadlula eceza izindlu zabako-Israyeli eGibhithe, waphephisa imizi yethu mhla egadla amaGibhithe.’ ” Khonapho abantu bakhothama bakhonza. <verse eid="EXO 12:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="EXO 12:28"/>Abako-Israyeli bakwenza lokho <char style="nd">uThixo</char> akuyala uMosi lo-Aroni.<verse eid="EXO 12:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="EXO 12:29"/>Phakathi kobusuku <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wawagongoda wonke amazibulo eGibhithe, kusukela ezibulweni likaFaro owayesesihlalweni sobukhosi kusiya ezibulweni lesibotshwa esasisentolongweni, kanye lamazibulo ezifuyo. <verse eid="EXO 12:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="EXO 12:30"/>UFaro lezikhulu zakhe zonke lawo wonke amaGibhithe bavuka ebusuku basiqhinqa isililo esikhulu eGibhithe ngoba kungekho ndlu layinye lapho okwakungafiwanga khona.<verse eid="EXO 12:30"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukuphuma EGibhithe</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="EXO 12:31"/>Ebusuku uFaro wabiza uMosi lo-Aroni wathi, “Hambani! Sukani ebantwini bami, lina labako-Israyeli. Hambani liyekhonza <char style="nd">uThixo</char> njengokucela kwenu. <verse eid="EXO 12:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="EXO 12:32"/>Thathani imihlambi yenu, njengokutsho kwenu lihambe. Njalo lingibusise.”<verse eid="EXO 12:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="EXO 12:33"/>AmaGibhithe akhuthaza ukuthi baphangise baphume elizweni. Bathi, “Engxenye singafa sonke!” <verse eid="EXO 12:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="EXO 12:34"/>Ngakho abantu bathatha inhlama yabo yesinkwa ingakafakwa mvubelo bayithwala emahlombe ngemiganu yokuvubela igoqelwe ngamalembu. <verse eid="EXO 12:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="EXO 12:35"/>Abako-Israyeli benza lokho uMosi abayala khona, bacela kumaGibhithe izinto ezenziwe ngesiliva langegolide kanye lezigqoko. <verse eid="EXO 12:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="EXO 12:36"/><char style="nd">UThixo</char> wenza amaGibhithe aba lomusa abapha konke abakucelayo. Ngakho bawemuka impahla ezinengi amaGibhithe.<verse eid="EXO 12:36"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="37" style="v" sid="EXO 12:37"/>Uhambo lwabako-Israyeli lwasukela eRamesesi baqonda eSukhothi. Kwakulamadoda azinkulungwane ezingamakhulu ayisithupha ehamba ngenyawo ngaphandle kwabesifazane labantwana. <verse eid="EXO 12:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="EXO 12:38"/>Abanye abantu abanengi bahamba labo kanye lemihlambi eminengi yezifuyo, izimvu lenkomo. <verse eid="EXO 12:38"/><verse number="39" style="v" sid="EXO 12:39"/>Inhlama abaphuma layo eGibhithe bapheka ngayo isinkwa esingelamvubelo. Inhlama leyo yayingelamvubelo ngoba basuka eGibhithe sebexotshwa abazabe besaba lesikhathi sokuzilungisela umphako.<verse eid="EXO 12:39"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="40" style="v" sid="EXO 12:40"/>Abako-Israyeli babehlale eGibhithe okweminyaka engamakhulu amane lamatshumi amathathu (430). <verse eid="EXO 12:40"/><verse number="41" style="v" sid="EXO 12:41"/>Ekupheleni kwaleyominyaka engamakhulu amane lamatshumi amathathu (430) kungeqanga suku wonke amaviyo <char style="nd">kaThixo</char> asuka eGibhithe. <verse eid="EXO 12:41"/><verse number="42" style="v" sid="EXO 12:42"/>Kwathi ngoba <char style="nd">uThixo</char> walinda ngalobobusuku esakhupha abako-Israyeli eGibhithe, yikho-ke labo abako-Israyeli bonke kumele bawugcine umlindo lo behlonipha <char style="nd">uThixo</char> kuzozonke izizukulwane ezizayo.<verse eid="EXO 12:42"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Izibopho ZePhasika</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="43" style="v" sid="EXO 12:43"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wathi kuMosi lo-Aroni, “Nansi imilayo yePhasika:</para>
  <para style="p" vid="EXO 12:43">Akungabi lamuntu wezizweni olidlayo. <verse eid="EXO 12:43"/><verse number="44" style="v" sid="EXO 12:44"/>Isigqili esithengwe ngemali singalidla nxa sesisokile, <verse eid="EXO 12:44"/><verse number="45" style="v" sid="EXO 12:45"/>kodwa isihambi sezizweni lesisebenzi esiqhatshiweyo kabavunyelwa ukulidla.<verse eid="EXO 12:45"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="46" style="v" sid="EXO 12:46"/>Kalidlelwe endlini eyodwa, kungabi lanyama ephumela phandle kwendlu. Akungabi lathambo elephulwayo. <verse eid="EXO 12:46"/><verse number="47" style="v" sid="EXO 12:47"/>Isizwe sonke sako-Israyeli kumele siwugcine lumkhosi.<verse eid="EXO 12:47"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="48" style="v" sid="EXO 12:48"/>Owezizweni ohlala phakathi kwenu nxa efuna ukulidla iPhasika <char style="nd">likaThixo</char> kasoke bonke abesilisa abahlala endlini yakhe. Lapho-ke usengahlanganyela adle njengomunye wenzalo yalelolizwe. Owesilisa ongasokwanga kangalidli. <verse eid="EXO 12:48"/><verse number="49" style="v" sid="EXO 12:49"/>Umthetho lo ugoqela bonke abantu, abayinzalo yakini labezizweni abahlala phakathi kwenu.”<verse eid="EXO 12:49"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="50" style="v" sid="EXO 12:50"/>Bonke abako-Israyeli benza khona lokhu <char style="nd">uThixo</char> ayekulaye uMosi lo-Aroni. <verse eid="EXO 12:50"/><verse number="51" style="v" sid="EXO 12:51"/>Njalo ngalelolanga <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wakhupha abako-Israyeli eGibhithe ngamaviyo abo.<verse eid="EXO 12:51"/></para>
  <chapter eid="EXO 12"/>
  <chapter number="13" style="c" sid="EXO 13"/>
  <para style="s1">Amazibulo Ahlukaniselwa <char style="nd">uThixo</char></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="EXO 13:1"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wathi kuMosi, <verse eid="EXO 13:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="EXO 13:2"/>“Ngahlukanisela wonke amazibulo esilisa. Konke okuzalwa kuqala phakathi kwabako-Israyeli kungokwami, kungaba ngumuntu loba isifuyo.”<verse eid="EXO 13:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="EXO 13:3"/>Ngakho uMosi wasesithi ebantwini, “Lugcineni lube lusuku lwesikhumbuzo lolu, ilanga elaphuma ngalo eGibhithe, liphuma elizweni lobugqili, ngoba <char style="nd">uThixo</char> walikhupha khona ngamandla amakhulu. Lingadli lutho olulemvubelo. <verse eid="EXO 13:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="EXO 13:4"/>Lamuhla ngenyanga ka-Abhibhi, liyasuka. <verse eid="EXO 13:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="EXO 13:5"/>Kuzakuthi <char style="nd">uThixo</char> angalifikisa elizweni lamaKhenani, amaHithi, ama-Amori, amaHivi lamaJebusi, ilizwe afunga kubokhokho benu ukuthi uzalinika lona, ilizwe eligeleza uchago loluju, kufanele liwugcine lumkhosi ngayonale inyanga. <verse eid="EXO 13:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="EXO 13:6"/>Okwensuku eziyisikhombisa lidle isinkwa esingelamvubelo kuthi ngosuku lwesikhombisa lithakazelele umkhosi <char style="nd">kaThixo</char>; <verse eid="EXO 13:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="EXO 13:7"/>kungabonwa lutho olulemvubelo phakathi kwenu, kuvele kungabonwa mvubelo elizweni lenu lonke. <verse eid="EXO 13:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="EXO 13:8"/>Ngalelolanga ngulowo lalowo atshele indodana yakhe athi, ‘Lokhu ngikwenza ngenxa yalokho <char style="nd">uThixo</char> angenzela khona ekuphumeni kwami eGibhithe.’ <verse eid="EXO 13:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="EXO 13:9"/>Lesisikhumbuzo kuwe sizakuba luphawu esandleni sakho lesikhumbuzo ebunzini lakho ukuthi umlayo <char style="nd">kaThixo</char> ube sezindebeni zakho. Ngoba <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wakukhupha eGibhithe ngesandla sakhe esilamandla amakhulu. <verse eid="EXO 13:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="EXO 13:10"/>Kalibosigcina lesisimiso ngesikhathi esimisiweyo minyaka yonke.<verse eid="EXO 13:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="EXO 13:11"/>Nxa <char style="nd">uThixo</char> eselingenisile elizweni lamaKhenani walinika lona njengokuthembisa kwakhe kini lakubokhokho benu, <verse eid="EXO 13:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="EXO 13:12"/>kumele lahlukanisele <char style="nd">uThixo</char> konke okuzalwa kuqala yizo zonke izibeletho. Wonke amazibulo esilisa ezifuyo zenu <char style="nd">ngakaThixo</char>. <verse eid="EXO 13:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="EXO 13:13"/>Lizahlenga izibulo likababhemi ngezinyane, kodwa nxa lingalihlenganga lephuleni intamo. Lihlenge njalo wonke amadodana enu angamazibulo.<verse eid="EXO 13:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="EXO 13:14"/>Nxa indodana yakho ikubuza ngesikhathi esizayo isithi, ‘Kutshoni lokhu?’ ubokuthi kuyo, ‘<char style="nd">uThixo</char> wasikhupha eGibhithe ngesandla sakhe esilamandla amakhulu, wasikhupha elizweni lobugqili. <verse eid="EXO 13:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="EXO 13:15"/>Kwathi uFaro eqholoza esala ukuthi sihambe, <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wabulala wonke amazibulo eGibhithe, awabantu lawezinyamazana. Yikho-nje nginikela <char style="nd">kuThixo</char> izibulo lesilisa lenzalo yonke ngiphinde ngihlenge wonke amadodana ami angamazibulo.’ <verse eid="EXO 13:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="EXO 13:16"/>Lokhu kuzakuba njengophawu esandleni sakho lesibonelo ebunzini lakho ukuthi <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wakukhupha eGibhithe ngesandla sakhe esilamandla amakhulu.”<verse eid="EXO 13:16"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukuchatshwa KoLwandle Olubomvu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="EXO 13:17"/>UFaro esebavumele abantu ukuthi bahambe, uNkulunkulu kabakhokhelanga ngendlela edabula elizweni lamaFilistiya loba yona yayiquma. Ngoba uNkulunkulu wathi, “Nxa behlangana lempi mhlawumbe bangethuka babuyele eGibhithe.” <verse eid="EXO 13:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="EXO 13:18"/>Yikho uNkulunkulu wabahola ngendlela yenkangala eya oLwandle Olubomvu. Abako-Israyeli baphuma eGibhithe behlomele impi.<verse eid="EXO 13:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="EXO 13:19"/>
    <note caller="+" style="f">
      <char style="fr" closed="false">13.19 UGenesisi 50.25</char>
    </note>UMosi wawathwala amathambo kaJosefa ngoba uJosefa wayenze isifungo lamadodana ka-Israyeli wathi, “Ngempela uNkulunkulu uzalikhulula. Lapho-ke libowathwala amathambo ami lisuke lawo kule indawo.”<verse eid="EXO 13:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="EXO 13:20"/>Sebesukile eSukhothi bayamisa e-Ethamu indawo egudlene lenkangala. <verse eid="EXO 13:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="EXO 13:21"/>Emini <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wahamba phambi kwabo ngensika yeyezi ebahola endleleni yabo, kwathi ebusuku wabahola ngensika yomlilo ukubakhanyisela ukuze bahambe emini lebusuku. <verse eid="EXO 13:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="EXO 13:22"/>Insika yeyezi emini loba insika yomlilo ebusuku kakuzange kusuke endaweni yakho phambi kwabantu.<verse eid="EXO 13:22"/></para>
  <chapter eid="EXO 13"/>
  <chapter number="14" style="c" sid="EXO 14"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="EXO 14:1"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wathi kuMosi, <verse eid="EXO 14:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="EXO 14:2"/>“Tshela abako-Israyeli ukuthi babuyele emuva bayomisa ePhi-Hahirothi phakathi laphakathi kweMigidoli lolwandle. Kabamise eceleni kolwandle malungana leBhali-Zefoni. <verse eid="EXO 14:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="EXO 14:3"/>UFaro uzacabanga ukuthi abako-Israyeli bayantula nje elizweni besangene ngoba sebesithwe yinkangala. <verse eid="EXO 14:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="EXO 14:4"/>Njalo ngizayenza ibe lukhuni inhliziyo kaFaro abeselandela exotshana labo. Kodwa ngizazizuzela udumo ngoFaro kanye lempi yakhe yonke, lamaGibhithe azakwazi ukuthi mina <char style="nd">nginguThixo</char>.” Ngakho abako-Israyeli bakwenza lokhu.<verse eid="EXO 14:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="EXO 14:5"/>Kwathi inkosi yaseGibhithe isitsheliwe ukuthi abantu sebebalekile, uFaro lezikhulu zakhe baguqula ingqondo zabo ngabako-Israyeli bathi, “Sesenzeni manje? Sesiyekele abako-Israyeli bahamba salahlekelwa yikusetshenzelwa yibo!” <verse eid="EXO 14:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="EXO 14:6"/>UFaro waselungisa inqola yakhe yamabhiza waphuma lempi yakhe. <verse eid="EXO 14:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="EXO 14:7"/>Wathatha izinqola ezikhethekileyo ezingamakhulu ayisithupha zahamba kanye lezinye izinqola zaseGibhithe, yinye ngayinye ilenduna yayo. <verse eid="EXO 14:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="EXO 14:8"/><char style="nd">UThixo</char> wayenza yaba lukhuni inhliziyo kaFaro inkosi yaseGibhithe, ngakho waxotshana labako-Israyeli ababehamba ngesibindi. <verse eid="EXO 14:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="EXO 14:9"/>AmaGibhithe kugoqela wonke amabhiza kaFaro lezinqola, abagadi bamabhiza lamabutho, abaxhuma abako-Israyeli abedlula bemise ngasolwandle eduzane lePhi-Hahirothi malungana leBhali-Zefoni.<verse eid="EXO 14:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="EXO 14:10"/>Kwathi uFaro esondela abako-Israyeli bathi bevusa amehlo babona nanko amaGibhithe asebanxwanele. Besaba bathuthumela bakhala <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>. <verse eid="EXO 14:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="EXO 14:11"/>Bathi kuMosi, “Kambe yikuthi kwakungelamangcwaba yini eGibhithe uze usilethe lapha enkangala ukuba sizofela khona? Manje wenzeni ngokusikhupha eGibhithe? <verse eid="EXO 14:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="EXO 14:12"/>Asitshongo kuwe yini siseGibhithe ukuthi siyekele? Satsho sathi siyekele sikhonze amaGibhithe. Kwakuzaba ngcono kithi ukukhonza amaGibhithe kulokufela enkangala!”<verse eid="EXO 14:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="EXO 14:13"/>UMosi wabaphendula abantu wathi, “Lingesabi. Manini isibindi, lizabona ukuthi <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uzalihlenga njani lamuhla. AmaGibhithe eliwabonayo lamuhla kalisoze liphinde liwabone futhi. <verse eid="EXO 14:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="EXO 14:14"/><char style="nd">UThixo</char> uzalilwela; lina manini lithule.”<verse eid="EXO 14:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="EXO 14:15"/>Ngakho <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wasesithi kuMosi, “Kanti ukhalelani kimi na? Tshela abako-Israyeli baphume bahambe. <verse eid="EXO 14:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="EXO 14:16"/>Phakamisa intonga yakho welulele isandla sakho phezu kolwandle amanzi adabuke phakathi ukuze abako-Israyeli bahambe phakathi kolwandle emhlabathini owomileyo. <verse eid="EXO 14:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="EXO 14:17"/>Ngizazenza zibe lukhuni inhliziyo zamaGibhithe ukuze angene abaxhume. Njalo ngizazuza udumo ngoFaro lempi yakhe yonke, langezinqola zakhe labagadi bakhe bamabhiza. <verse eid="EXO 14:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="EXO 14:18"/>AmaGibhithe azakwazi ukuthi mina yimi <char style="nd">uThixo</char> nxa sengizuza udumo ngoFaro, langezinqola zakhe labagadi bakhe bamabhiza.”<verse eid="EXO 14:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="EXO 14:19"/>Kwathi khonapho ingilosi kaNkulunkulu eyayikade ihamba phambili kwempi yabako-Israyeli yasuka yabhoda ngemva kwabo. Insika yeyezi layo yasuka phambili yayakuma ngemva kwabo, <verse eid="EXO 14:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="EXO 14:20"/>yehlukanisa impi yamaGibhithe leyabako-Israyeli. Ubusuku bonke iyezi laletha ubumnyama kwelinye icele labuye laletha ukukhanya ngakwelinye icele; ngakho kabakho abasondela kwabanye ubusuku bonke.<verse eid="EXO 14:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="EXO 14:21"/>Ngakho uMosi waseselulela isandla sakhe phezu kolwandle, ngalobobusuku <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wafuqela ulwandle emuva ngomoya wempumalanga olamandla kwasala umhlabathi owomileyo. Amanzi adabukana phakathi, <verse eid="EXO 14:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="EXO 14:22"/>abako-Israyeli bazihambela phakathi kolwandle emhlabathini owomileyo amanzi ezindonga ngapha langapha kwabo.<verse eid="EXO 14:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="EXO 14:23"/>AmaGibhithe abalandela, amabhiza wonke kaFaro, izinqola labagadi bamabhiza bonke babalandela phakathi kolwandle. <verse eid="EXO 14:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="EXO 14:24"/>Kwathi ngomlindo wokucina wobusuku <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wakhangela phansi esensikeni yomlilo leyezi, wakhangela phansi empini yamaGibhithe wayidunga yasanganiseka. <verse eid="EXO 14:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="EXO 14:25"/>Wenza ukuthi amavili ezinqola zawo akhumuke okwenza kwaba nzima ukuthi aqhubeke lula. AmaGibhithe asesithi, “Kasehlukaneni labako-Israyeli! <char style="nd">UThixo</char> uyabalwela ukuba behlule amaGibhithe.”<verse eid="EXO 14:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="EXO 14:26"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wasesithi kuMosi, “Phakamisa isandla sakho phezu kolwandle ukuze amanzi abuyele ambokothe amaGibhithe lezinqola zawo labagadi bamabhiza.” <verse eid="EXO 14:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="EXO 14:27"/>UMosi waseselula isandla sakhe phezu kolwandle, kwathi emadabukakusa amanzi abuyela endaweni yawo. AmaGibhithe ayebaleka eqonda emanzini, <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wawagubuzela ngamanzi olwandle. <verse eid="EXO 14:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="EXO 14:28"/>Amanzi aqubuka abuyela emuva ambokotha izinqola labagadi bamabhiza, layo yonke impi kaFaro eyalandela abako-Israyeli olwandle. Akusilanga loyedwa kubo.<verse eid="EXO 14:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="EXO 14:29"/>Kodwa abako-Israyeli badabula olwandle emhlabathini owomileyo kulezindonga zamanzi esandleni sokudla lakwesokhohlo. <verse eid="EXO 14:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="EXO 14:30"/>Ngalolosuku <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wasindisa u-Israyeli ezandleni zamaGibhithe, njalo abako-Israyeli bawabona amaGibhithe ethe dandalazi okhunjini lolwandle esefile. <verse eid="EXO 14:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="EXO 14:31"/>Kwathi abako-Israyeli bebona amandla amakhulu <char style="nd">uThixo</char> awatshengisa kumaGibhithe, abantu bamesaba <char style="nd">uThixo</char> babeka ithemba labo kuye lakuMosi inceku yakhe.<verse eid="EXO 14:31"/></para>
  <chapter eid="EXO 14"/>
  <chapter number="15" style="c" sid="EXO 15"/>
  <para style="s1">Ingoma KaMosi LoMiriyemu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="EXO 15:1"/>Ngakho uMosi labako-Israyeli basebehlabelela lelihubo <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="EXO 15:1">“Ngizamhlabelela <char style="nd">uThixo</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="EXO 15:1">ngoba uphakeme kakhulu.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="EXO 15:1">Ibhiza lomgadi walo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="EXO 15:1">ukuphosele ngamandla olwandle.<verse eid="EXO 15:1"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="EXO 15:2"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> ungamandla ami lehubo lami;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="EXO 15:2">useyikusindiswa kwami.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="EXO 15:2">UnguNkulunkulu wami, ngizamdumisa;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="EXO 15:2">uNkulunkulu kababa ngizamphakamisa.<verse eid="EXO 15:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="EXO 15:3"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> ulibutho;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="EXO 15:3">
    <char style="nd">nguThixo</char> ibizo lakhe.<verse eid="EXO 15:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="EXO 15:4"/>Izinqola zikaFaro lempi yakhe</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="EXO 15:4">ukuphosele ngamandla olwandle.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="EXO 15:4">Izikhulu zikaFaro ezithenjiweyo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="EXO 15:4">zigalule oLwandle oluBomvu.<verse eid="EXO 15:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="EXO 15:5"/>Inziki zamanzi zibagubuzele;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="EXO 15:5">batshona ekujuleni njengelitshe.<verse eid="EXO 15:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="EXO 15:6"/>Isandla sakho sokunene, Oh <char style="nd">Thixo</char>,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="EXO 15:6">saba lamandla obukhosi.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="EXO 15:6">Isandla sakho sokunene, Oh <char style="nd">Thixo</char>,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="EXO 15:6">sasihlikiza isitha.<verse eid="EXO 15:6"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="EXO 15:7"/>Ebukhulwini bobukhosi bakho</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="EXO 15:7">wabasakazela phansi abakuphikisayo.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="EXO 15:7">Wavulela ulaka lwakho oluvuthayo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="EXO 15:7">lwabatshisa njengencwathi.<verse eid="EXO 15:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="EXO 15:8"/>Ngokuphefumula kwamakhala akho</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="EXO 15:8">amanzi aqoqana aba yinqwaba.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="EXO 15:8">Amanzi ageleza ngenhlokomo ema enza udonga;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="EXO 15:8">amanzi azikileyo ajiya enzikini yolwandle.<verse eid="EXO 15:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="EXO 15:9"/>Isitha sakloloda sathi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="EXO 15:9">‘Ngizabaxhuma, ngibedlule.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="EXO 15:9">Ngizakwaba impango;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="EXO 15:9">ngizazitika ngokungokwabo.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="EXO 15:9">Ngizakhokha inkemba yami,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="EXO 15:9">isandla sami sibabhubhise.’<verse eid="EXO 15:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="EXO 15:10"/>Kodwa wena wavuthela ngomoya wokuphefumula kwakho,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="EXO 15:10">ulwandle lwabasibekela.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="EXO 15:10">Batshona njengomnuso</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="EXO 15:10">emanzini esabekayo.<verse eid="EXO 15:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="EXO 15:11"/>Ngubani kubonkulunkulu bonke</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="EXO 15:11">onjengawe, <char style="nd">Thixo</char>?</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="EXO 15:11">Ngubani onjengawe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="EXO 15:11">olobukhosi ebungcweleni bakhe,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="EXO 15:11">owesabekayo ngenkazimulo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="EXO 15:11">owenza izimangaliso?<verse eid="EXO 15:11"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="EXO 15:12"/>Welula isandla sakho sokunene</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="EXO 15:12">umhlabathi uziginye izitha zakho.<verse eid="EXO 15:12"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="EXO 15:13"/>Ngothando lwakho olungapheliyo uzabahola</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="EXO 15:13">abantu obahlengileyo.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="EXO 15:13">Ngamandla akho uzabaholela</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="EXO 15:13">endaweni yakho engcwele.<verse eid="EXO 15:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="EXO 15:14"/>Izizwe zizakuzwa zithuthumele;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="EXO 15:14">umhedehede ubahlukuluze abantu baseFilistiya.<verse eid="EXO 15:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="EXO 15:15"/>Izinduna zase-Edomi zizatshaywa luvalo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="EXO 15:15">abakhokheli baseMowabi bafikelwe yikwesaba,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="EXO 15:15">abantu baseKhenani banyamalale nya!<verse eid="EXO 15:15"/></para>
  <para style="q2">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="EXO 15:16"/>Ukwesaba lokuthuthumela kuzabehlela.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="EXO 15:16">Ngamandla engalo yakho,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="EXO 15:16">bazathula njengelitshe,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="EXO 15:16">abantu bakho baze bedlule, Oh <char style="nd">Thixo</char>,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="EXO 15:16">abantu owabadalayo baze bedlule.<verse eid="EXO 15:16"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="EXO 15:17"/>Uzabangenisa ubahlanyele</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="EXO 15:17">entabeni yelifa lakho,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="EXO 15:17">indawo, Oh <char style="nd">Thixo</char>,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="EXO 15:17">owayenzela ukuthi uhlale kuyo,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="EXO 15:17">indawo engcwele, Oh <char style="nd">Thixo</char>,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="EXO 15:17">eyamiswa ngezandla zakho.<verse eid="EXO 15:17"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="EXO 15:18"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> uzabusa</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="EXO 15:18">kuze kube nini lanini.”<verse eid="EXO 15:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="EXO 15:19"/>Kwathi lapho amabhiza kaFaro, izinqola kanye labagadi bamabhiza sebengenile olwandle, <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wawabuyisa amanzi alo phezu kwabo, kodwa abako-Israyeli bona bazihambela badabula ulwandle phezu komhlabathi owomileyo. <verse eid="EXO 15:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="EXO 15:20"/>Khonapho uMiriyemu umphrofethikazi, udadewabo ka-Aroni, wathatha isigubhu sakhe ngesandla, bamlandela bonke abesifazane bephethe izigubhu begida. <verse eid="EXO 15:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="EXO 15:21"/>UMiriyemu wabahlabelela wathi:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="EXO 15:21">“Mhlabeleleni <char style="nd">uThixo</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="EXO 15:21">ngoba uphakeme kakhulu.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="EXO 15:21">Ibhiza lomgadi walo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="EXO 15:21">ukuphosele ngamandla olwandle.”<verse eid="EXO 15:21"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Amanzi EMara Le-Elimi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="EXO 15:22"/>UMosi wasebahola abako-Israyeli basuka oLwandle Olubomvu baya enkangala yeShuri bengatholi manzi. <verse eid="EXO 15:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="EXO 15:23"/>Kwathi befika eMara behluleka ukunatha amanzi akhona ngoba ayebaba. (Yikho indawo leyo kuthiwa yiMara.) <verse eid="EXO 15:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="EXO 15:24"/>Abantu basebekhonona kuMosi besithi, “Sinatheni-ke manje?”<verse eid="EXO 15:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="EXO 15:25"/>UMosi wasekhala <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>, <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wasemtshengisa isigojwana. Wasiphosela emanzini, amanzi aphenduka aba mnandi.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="EXO 15:25">Khonapho <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wabenzela isimiso lomthetho, njalo khonapho wabalinga. <verse eid="EXO 15:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="EXO 15:26"/>Wathi, “Nxa lilalela kakuhle ilizwi <char style="nd">likaThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wenu, lenze okulungileyo kuye, lilandele imilayo yakhe njalo ligcine lezimiso zakhe, kangisoze ngilehlisele iziga lezo engazehlisela amaGibhithe; ngoba <char style="nd">nginguThixo</char> olisilisayo.”<verse eid="EXO 15:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="EXO 15:27"/>Basebefika e-Elimi lapho okwakulemithombo yamanzi elitshumi lambili khona, lezihlahla zelala ezingamatshumi ayisikhombisa. Basebemisa khona lapho eduze kwamanzi.<verse eid="EXO 15:27"/></para>
  <chapter eid="EXO 15"/>
  <chapter number="16" style="c" sid="EXO 16"/>
  <para style="s1">Imana Lezagwaca</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="EXO 16:1"/>Uzulu wonke wako-Israyeli wasuka e-Elimi, wafika enkangala yeSini ephakathi laphakathi kwe-Elimi leSinayi ngelanga letshumi lanhlanu enyangeni yesibili besuke eGibhithe. <verse eid="EXO 16:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="EXO 16:2"/>Enkangala uzulu wakhonona kuMosi lo-Aroni. <verse eid="EXO 16:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="EXO 16:3"/>Abako-Israyeli bathi kubo, “Ngabe sazifela ngesandla <char style="nd">sikaThixo</char> eGibhithe, lapho esasihlala sigombolozele imbiza zenyama lakho konke ukudla esasikufumana, kodwa lina selisilethe lapha enkangala ukuze ixuku lonke leli liyathe ngendlala.”<verse eid="EXO 16:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="EXO 16:4"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wasesithi kuMosi, “Ngizalehlisela isinkwa sivela ezulwini. Abantu kumele baphume nsuku zonke bayebutha okwanela lelolanga. Ngale indlela ngizabalinga ukuze ngibone ukuthi bayayilandela yini imilayo yami. <verse eid="EXO 16:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="EXO 16:5"/>Ngelanga lesithupha kumele balungise lokho abayabe bekulethile, okumele kube ngokuphindwe kabili kulokho abakubutha kwezinye insuku.”<verse eid="EXO 16:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="EXO 16:6"/>Yikho-ke uMosi lo-Aroni bathi kubo bonke abako-Israyeli, “Kusihlwa lizakwazi ukuthi <char style="nd">nguThixo</char> olikhuphe kweleGibhithe, <verse eid="EXO 16:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="EXO 16:7"/>njalo ekuseni lizabona inkazimulo <char style="nd">kaThixo</char> ngoba ukuzwile ukukhonona kwenu. Singobani thina ukuba lisisole?” <verse eid="EXO 16:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="EXO 16:8"/>UMosi wathi, “Lizakwazi ukuthi <char style="nd">bekunguThixo</char> nxa eselipha inyama yokudla kusihlwa lesinkwa sonke elisifunayo ekuseni ngenxa yokuthi usekuzwile ukukhonona kwenu kuye. Singobani? Kalikhononi kithi kodwa <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>.”<verse eid="EXO 16:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="EXO 16:9"/>Ngakho uMosi watshela u-Aroni wathi, “Khuluma lozulu wonke wako-Israyeli uthi, ‘Wozani <char style="nd">kuThixo</char> ngoba usekuzwile ukukhonona kwenu.’ ”<verse eid="EXO 16:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="EXO 16:10"/>Ngesikhathi u-Aroni ekhuluma lozulu wonke wako-Israyeli, bakhangela enkangala basebebona inkazimulo <char style="nd">kaThixo</char> ibonakala eyezini.<verse eid="EXO 16:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="EXO 16:11"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wathi kuMosi: <verse eid="EXO 16:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="EXO 16:12"/>“Sengizwile ukukhonona kwabako-Israyeli. Batshele ukuthi, ‘Kusihlwa lizakudla inyama njalo ekuseni lizasuthiswa ngesinkwa. Lapho-ke lizakwazi ukuthi <char style="nd">nginguThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wenu.’ ”<verse eid="EXO 16:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="EXO 16:13"/>Ngalokhokuhlwa kweza izagwaca zagcwala indawo yonke ababehlala kuyo, njalo ekuseni kwaba lamazolo ngaphandle kwezihonqo. <verse eid="EXO 16:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="EXO 16:14"/>Kwathi amazolo esenyamalele kwabonakala izicecedwana ezifana longqwaqwane phezu kwenkangala. <verse eid="EXO 16:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="EXO 16:15"/>Kwathi abako-Israyeli bekubona lokhu bakhulumisana besithi, “Kuyini lokhu?” Ngoba babengakwazi ukuthi kwakuyini.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="EXO 16:15">UMosi wathi kubo, “Yisinkwa elisiphiwe <char style="nd">nguThixo</char> ukuthi lidle. <verse eid="EXO 16:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="EXO 16:16"/>Lokhu yikho okulaywe <char style="nd">nguThixo</char> ukuthi: ‘Umuntu emunye uzathatha okwaneleyo akuswelayo. Thathela umuntu ngamunye osethenteni lakho isilinganiso se-omeri.’ ”<verse eid="EXO 16:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="EXO 16:17"/>Abako-Israyeli benza njengokulaywa kwabo. Abanye babutha okunengi abanye okulutshwana. <verse eid="EXO 16:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="EXO 16:18"/>Bathi sebekulinganisa nge-omeri babona ukuthi lowo owabutha okunengi kabanga lokunengi kakhulu, lalowo owabutha okulutshwana kabanga lokulutshwana kakhulu. Umuntu wonke wabutha okwakumenela.<verse eid="EXO 16:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="EXO 16:19"/>Ngakho-ke uMosi wathi kubo, “Akumelanga kubekhona ozagcina okunye kwalokho kuze kube sekuseni.”<verse eid="EXO 16:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="EXO 16:20"/>Lanxa kunjalo abanye kabazange bamlalele uMosi: bagcina eyinye ingxenye kwaze kwaba sekuseni. Kodwa kwakugcwele impethu njalo kwasekulephunga elibi. UMosi wabathukuthelela.<verse eid="EXO 16:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="EXO 16:21"/>Nsuku zonke ekuseni umuntu emunye wabutha isilinganiso ayesifuna, njalo ilanga lathi selitshisa kwancibilika. <verse eid="EXO 16:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="EXO 16:22"/>Ngelanga lesithupha babutha isilinganiso esiphindwe kabili ama-omeri amabili umuntu emunye, njalo abakhokheli babantu beza ukuzobika kuMosi. <verse eid="EXO 16:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="EXO 16:23"/>Wathi kubo, “Lokhu yikho okwalaywa <char style="nd">nguThixo</char>: ‘Kusasa lilanga lokuphumula iSabatha elingcwele <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>. Ngakho bhekhani konke elifuna ukukubhekha, libilise konke elifuna ukukubilisa. Gcinani konke okuseleyo kuze kube sekuseni.’ ”<verse eid="EXO 16:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="EXO 16:24"/>Ngakho bakugcina kwaze kwaba sekuseni njengokulaya kukaMosi njalo kakuzange kube lephunga kumbe impethu. <verse eid="EXO 16:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="EXO 16:25"/>UMosi wathi, “Kudleni namuhla, ngoba namuhla liSabatha <char style="nd">likaThixo</char>, kalisoze lithole lutho phandle namuhla. <verse eid="EXO 16:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="EXO 16:26"/>Okwensuku eziyisithupha lizakubutha, kodwa ngelanga lesikhombisa eleSabatha akusoze kube lalutho.”<verse eid="EXO 16:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="EXO 16:27"/>Lanxa kunjalo abanye abantu ngelanga lesikhombisa bahamba ukuba bayobutha kodwa bafica kungelalutho. <verse eid="EXO 16:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="EXO 16:28"/><char style="nd">UThixo</char> wasesithi kuMosi, “Kuzaze kube nini lisala ukulandela imithetho lemilayo yami na? <verse eid="EXO 16:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="EXO 16:29"/>Kufakeni ezingqondweni zenu ukuthi <char style="nd">uThixo</char> ulinikile iSabatha, yikho ngelanga lesithupha elinika isinkwa esenela insuku ezimbili. Wonke umuntu kumele ahlale lapho ayabe ekhona ngelanga lesikhombisa. Akulamuntu okumele aphume phandle.” <verse eid="EXO 16:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="EXO 16:30"/>Yikho-ke abantu baphumula ngelanga lesikhombisa.<verse eid="EXO 16:30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="EXO 16:31"/>Abantu bako-Israyeli babiza isinkwa leso bathi yimana. Sasimhlophe njengentanga zekhoriyanda, sihlabusa njengamakhekhe enziwe ngoluju. <verse eid="EXO 16:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="EXO 16:32"/>UMosi wathi, “Lokhu yikho okutshiwo <char style="nd">nguThixo</char> ukuthi: ‘Thathani imana eyisilinganiso se-omeri ligcinele izizukulwane ezizayo ukuze zibone isinkwa engalinika sona ukuba lisidle enkangala ekulikhupheni kwami eGibhithe.’ ”<verse eid="EXO 16:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="EXO 16:33"/>UMosi wasesithi ku-Aroni, “Thatha inkonxa ufake phakathi imana eyisilinganiso se-omeri. Ibeke phambi <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char> ukuze igcinelwe izizukulwane ezizayo.”<verse eid="EXO 16:33"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="EXO 16:34"/>Njengoba <char style="nd">uThixo</char> walaya uMosi, u-Aroni wabeka imana lezibhebhedu zobufakazi ukuze igcinakale. <verse eid="EXO 16:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="EXO 16:35"/>Abako-Israyeli badla imana okweminyaka engamatshumi amane baze bafika endaweni eyayihlala abantu, badla imana baze bafika emngceleni weKhenani.<verse eid="EXO 16:35"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="EXO 16:36"/>(I-omere iyisilinganiso sokulitshumi sehefa.)<verse eid="EXO 16:36"/></para>
  <chapter eid="EXO 16"/>
  <chapter number="17" style="c" sid="EXO 17"/>
  <para style="s1">Amanzi Ampompoza Edwaleni</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="EXO 17:1"/>Uzulu wonke wako-Israyeli wasuka enkangala yeSini, wahamba njengokulaya <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char>. Bake bahlala okwesikhathi esifitshane eRefidimu kodwa kwakungelamanzi okuthi abantu banathe. <verse eid="EXO 17:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="EXO 17:2"/>Ngakho baxabana loMosi basebesithi, “Sinike amanzi okunatha.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="EXO 17:2">UMosi waphendula wathi “Kungani lixabana lami? Kungani lilinga <char style="nd">uThixo</char>?”<verse eid="EXO 17:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="EXO 17:3"/>Kodwa abantu basebomele amanzi kuleyondawo, ngakho bakhonona kuMosi. Bathi kuye, “Wasikhupha eGibhithe ukwenzela ukuthi thina labantwabethu kanye lezifuyo sibulawe yikoma na?”<verse eid="EXO 17:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="EXO 17:4"/>Ngakho uMosi wakhala <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>, wathi, “Kambe ngithini ngalababantu? Sebezimisele ukuthi bangikhande ngamatshe.”<verse eid="EXO 17:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="EXO 17:5"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> waphendula uMosi wathi “Khokhela abantu. Thatha abanye abadala bako-Israyeli ubusuthatha njalo intonga leyana owake watshaya ngayo amanzi emfuleni uNayili lihambe. <verse eid="EXO 17:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="EXO 17:6"/>Ngizakuma lapho phambi kwenu eduzane ledwala eHorebhi. Utshaye idwala; kuzaphuma amanzi kulo ukuba abantu banathe.” Ngakho uMosi wenza lokho abadala bako-Israyeli bekhangele. <verse eid="EXO 17:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="EXO 17:7"/>Wabiza indawo leyo ngegama elithi Masa leMeribha ngenxa yokuthi abantu bako-Israyeli baxabana njalo balinga <char style="nd">uThixo</char> besithi “Kambe <char style="nd">uThixo</char> ulathi yini kumbe hatshi?”<verse eid="EXO 17:7"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukunqotshwa Kwama-Amaleki</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="EXO 17:8"/>Ama-Amaleki eza ukuzohlasela abako-Israyeli eRefidimu. <verse eid="EXO 17:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="EXO 17:9"/>UMosi wathi kuJoshuwa, “Khetha amanye amadoda phakathi kwethu uphume liyekulwa lama-Amaleki. Kusasa ngizakuma phezu koqaqa ngiphethe intonga kaNkulunkulu ezandleni zami.”<verse eid="EXO 17:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="EXO 17:10"/>Ngakho uJoshuwa walwa lama-Amaleki njengokulaya kukaMosi, njalo uMosi, u-Aroni loHuri bakhwela phezu koqaqa. <verse eid="EXO 17:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="EXO 17:11"/>Kwakusithi nxa uMosi ephakamise izandla zakhe abako-Israyeli babenqoba, kodwa wayesithi angehlisa izandla zakhe ama-Amaleki yiwo ayenqoba. <verse eid="EXO 17:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="EXO 17:12"/>Kwathi izandla zikaMosi sezidiniwe bathatha ilitshe balifaka ngaphansi kwakhe wasehlala phezu kwalo. U-Aroni loHuri baphakamisa izandla zakhe, omunye ekuleli icele omunye kwelinye ukuze izandla zakhe zale ziphakeme laze latshona ilanga. <verse eid="EXO 17:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="EXO 17:13"/>Ngakho uJoshuwa wehlula ibutho lama-Amaleki ngenkemba.<verse eid="EXO 17:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="EXO 17:14"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wasesithi kuMosi, “Bhala lokhu ogwalweni njengento okumele ikhunjulwe njalo ubone ukuthi uJoshuwa uyakuzwa lokhu ngenxa yokuthi ngizatshabalalisa umkhumbulo wonke omayelana lama-Amaleki ngaphansi kwezulu.”<verse eid="EXO 17:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="EXO 17:15"/>UMosi wakha i-alithari walibiza ngokuthi <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uLuphawu Lwami. <verse eid="EXO 17:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="EXO 17:16"/>Wathi, “Ngoba izandla zaphakanyiselwa esihlalweni <char style="nd">sikaThixo</char>. <char style="nd">UThixo</char> uzakulwa impi lezizukulwane zama-Amaleki.”<verse eid="EXO 17:16"/></para>
  <chapter eid="EXO 17"/>
  <chapter number="18" style="c" sid="EXO 18"/>
  <para style="s1">UJethro Wethekelela UMosi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="EXO 18:1"/>UJethro, umphristi waseMidiyani owayenguyisezala kaMosi, wezwa konke uNkulunkulu ayekwenzele uMosi labantu bakhe bako-Israyeli, lokuthi <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wayebakhuphe njani eGibhithe abako-Israyeli.<verse eid="EXO 18:1"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="EXO 18:2"/>Ngemva kokuba uMosi esethumele umkakhe uZiphora kibo, uyisezala uJethro wamemukela, <verse eid="EXO 18:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="EXO 18:3"/>lamadodana akhe amabili. Eyinye indodana kwakuthiwa nguGeshomu, ngoba uMosi wathi, “Sengibe ngumuntu wezizweni elizweni elingayisilo lami.” <verse eid="EXO 18:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="EXO 18:4"/>Eyinye kwakuthiwa ngu-Eliyezari ngoba wathi, “UNkulunkulu kababa wayengumsizi wami: wangisindisa enkembeni kaFaro.”<verse eid="EXO 18:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="EXO 18:5"/>UJethro, uyisezala kaMosi kanye lamadodana lenkosikazi kaMosi beza kuye enkangala lapho ayehlala khona eduzane lentaba kaNkulunkulu. <verse eid="EXO 18:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="EXO 18:6"/>UJethro wayethumele ilizwi kuye wathi, “Mina uyihlozala uJethro ngiyeza kuwe lenkosikazi yakho lamadodana ayo amabili.”<verse eid="EXO 18:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="EXO 18:7"/>Ngakho uMosi waphuma wayahlangabeza uyisezala wasemkhothamela, wamanga. Babingelelana basebengena ethenteni. <verse eid="EXO 18:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="EXO 18:8"/>UMosi watshela uyisezala ngakho konke <char style="nd">uThixo</char> ayekwenze kuFaro labantu baseGibhithe ngenxa yabantu bako-Israyeli langezinhlupho zonke ezabehlela endleleni lokuthi <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wayebasindise njani.<verse eid="EXO 18:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="EXO 18:9"/>UJethro wathokoza ukuzwa ngezinto zonke ezinhle <char style="nd">uThixo</char> ayezenzele u-Israyeli ekubasindiseni esandleni samaGibhithe. <verse eid="EXO 18:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="EXO 18:10"/>Wathi, “Kadunyiswe <char style="nd">uThixo</char> owalisindisa esandleni samaGibhithe loFaro, njalo owasindisa abantu esandleni samaGibhithe. <verse eid="EXO 18:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="EXO 18:11"/>Khathesi sengikwazi ukuthi <char style="nd">uThixo</char> ulamandla ukwedlula abanye onkulunkulu ngenxa yokuthi wenza lokhu kubo bonke abaphatha u-Israyeli ngobuqholo.” <verse eid="EXO 18:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="EXO 18:12"/>Lapho-ke uJethro, uyisezala kaMosi, waletha umnikelo wokutshiswa leminye imihlatshelo kuNkulunkulu, njalo u-Aroni weza labadala bako-Israyeli ukuze bazokudla isinkwa loyisezala kaMosi phambi kukaNkulunkulu.<verse eid="EXO 18:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="EXO 18:13"/>Ngelanga elilandelayo uMosi wathatha isihlalo sakhe sokuba ngumthonisi wabantu, njalo bema bemgombolozele kusukela ekuseni kwaze kwaba ntambama. <verse eid="EXO 18:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="EXO 18:14"/>Kwathi uyisezala esebone konke uMosi ayekwenzela abantu wathi, “Kuyini lokhu okwenzela abantu? Kungani uhlala unguwe wedwa ukuba ngumahluli, abantu bonke bemi bekuhanqile kusukela ekuseni kuze kube kusihlwa?”<verse eid="EXO 18:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="EXO 18:15"/>UMosi wamphendula wathi, “Ngenxa yokuthi abantu beza kimi ukuzodinga intando kaNkulunkulu. <verse eid="EXO 18:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="EXO 18:16"/>Lapho kusiba lengxabano, ilethwa kimi, njalo ngiyahlulela emaceleni womabili besengibatshela ngemithetho lemilayo kaNkulunkulu.”<verse eid="EXO 18:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="EXO 18:17"/>Uyisezala kaMosi waphendula wathi, “Konke okwenzayo kakulunganga. <verse eid="EXO 18:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="EXO 18:18"/>Wena labantu laba abeza kuwe lizazidinisa. Umsebenzi lo unzima kuwe: ungeke wawenza wedwa. <verse eid="EXO 18:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="EXO 18:19"/>Ngilalela ngikucebise, njalo uNkulunkulu makabe lawe. Kumele ube ngummeli wabantu kuNkulunkulu, ulethe ingxabano zabo kuye. <verse eid="EXO 18:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="EXO 18:20"/>Bafundise izimiso lemithetho yakhe, ubatshengise indlela yokuphila lokuthi baziphathe njani. <verse eid="EXO 18:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="EXO 18:21"/>Kodwa khetha amadoda alamandla phakathi kwabantu bonke, amadoda amesabayo uNkulunkulu, azonda inzuzo eza ngobuqili, ubusubabeka babe zinduna zezinkulungwane, zamakhulu, zamatshumi amahlanu, lezamatshumi. <verse eid="EXO 18:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="EXO 18:22"/>Benze babe ngabahluleli babantu ngezikhathi zonke, kodwa kabalethe wonke amacala anzima kuwe bona baqume amacala alula. Lokho kuzakwenza ukuthi umthwalo wakho ube lula ngoba bazabe besabelana lawe. <verse eid="EXO 18:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="EXO 18:23"/>Nxa ungakwenza lokhu njengokulaya kukaNkulunkulu, uzakwenelisa ukuphumuza ingqondo njalo abantu bonke laba bazabuyela emakhaya besuthisekile.”<verse eid="EXO 18:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="EXO 18:24"/>UMosi wamlalela uyisezala wenza konke ayekutshilo. <verse eid="EXO 18:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="EXO 18:25"/>Wakhetha amadoda alamandla phakathi kwabako-Israyeli wonke wawenza abakhokheli babantu, izinduna zezinkulungwane, ezamakhulu, ezamatshumi amahlanu lezamatshumi. <verse eid="EXO 18:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="EXO 18:26"/>Baba ngabahluleli babantu ngazozonke izikhathi. Amacala anzima bawaletha kuMosi, kodwa alula bawathonisa bona ngokwabo.<verse eid="EXO 18:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="EXO 18:27"/>UMosi wavalelisana loyisezala, uJethro wasebuyela elizweni lakhe.<verse eid="EXO 18:27"/></para>
  <chapter eid="EXO 18"/>
  <chapter number="19" style="c" sid="EXO 19"/>
  <para style="s1">Entabeni YeSinayi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="EXO 19:1"/>Ngosuku olufanayo, emva kwezinyanga ezintathu abantu bako-Israyeli besuke eGibhithe bafika enkangala yeSinayi. <verse eid="EXO 19:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="EXO 19:2"/>Sebesukile eRefidimu bangena enkangala yeSinayi bamisa amathente abo phansi kwentaba.<verse eid="EXO 19:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="EXO 19:3"/>Lapho-ke uMosi wakhuphukela kuNkulunkulu entabeni, <char style="nd">uThixo</char> esentabeni wabiza uMosi wathi kuye, “Tshela abantu bendlu kaJakhobe labantu bako-Israyeli, uthi <verse eid="EXO 19:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="EXO 19:4"/>‘Lina ngokwenu lizibonele engikwenze eGibhithe lokuthi ngilithwele ngamaphiko okhozi ngaliletha lapha kimi. <verse eid="EXO 19:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="EXO 19:5"/>Ngakho-ke lingangilalela ligcine isivumelwano sami lani lizakuba ligugu kimi phakathi kwezizwe zonke. Lanxa umhlaba wonke ungowami, <verse eid="EXO 19:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="EXO 19:6"/>lina kimi lizakuba ngumbuso wabaphristi lesizwe esingcwele.’ Yiwo amazwi okumele uwakhulume kwabako-Israyeli.”<verse eid="EXO 19:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="EXO 19:7"/>UMosi wabuyela ebantwini, wafika wabuthanisa abakhokheli babantu wabatshela okwakutshiwo <char style="nd">nguThixo</char>. <verse eid="EXO 19:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="EXO 19:8"/>Bonke bavuma ngalizwi linye bathi, “Sizakwenza konke <char style="nd">uThixo</char> athe sikwenze.” UMosi wambikela <char style="nd">uThixo</char> okwakukhulunywe ngabantu.<verse eid="EXO 19:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="EXO 19:9"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wasesithi kuMosi, “Ngizakuza kini nginjengeyezi elimnyama ukuze abantu bangizwe ngikhuluma lawe. Ngakho ngezikhathi zonke bazakholwa kuwe.” UMosi watshela <char style="nd">uThixo</char> okwakutshiwo ngabantu.<verse eid="EXO 19:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="EXO 19:10"/>Ngakho <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wathi kuMosi, “Buyela ebantwini ubangcwelise lamhla lakusasa. Batshele bagezise izigqoko zabo <verse eid="EXO 19:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="EXO 19:11"/>kuthi ngelanga lesithathu libe selilungiselele ngoba ngalelolanga <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uzakwehlela entabeni yeSinayi abantu bonke bekhangele. <verse eid="EXO 19:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="EXO 19:12"/>Yenzela abantu imingcele malungana lentaba, ubatshele uthi, ‘Limukani! Lingakhweli entabeni, kumbe ukufika phansi kwayo. Lowo ozasondela entabeni uzabulawa.’ <verse eid="EXO 19:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="EXO 19:13"/>Ngempela uzatshaywa ngamatshe kumbe acitshwe ngemitshoko kodwa angathintwa ngesandla. Akukhathalekile ukuthi ngumuntu loba yinyamazana akusoze kuvunyelwe ukuphila. Bazakhwela entabeni kuphela nxa uphondo lwenqama selukhale isikhathi eside.”<verse eid="EXO 19:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="EXO 19:14"/>Ngemva kokuba uMosi esehlile entabeni waya ebantwini wabangcwelisa basebegezisa lezigqoko zabo. <verse eid="EXO 19:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="EXO 19:15"/>Wathi ebantwini, “Lungiselelani ilanga lesithathu. Zilani omkenu.”<verse eid="EXO 19:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="EXO 19:16"/>Ekuseni ngelanga lesithathu kwaba lomdumo lombane othuthumelisayo, leyezi elikhulukazi lehlela phezu kwentaba, kwezwakala lomsindo omkhulu wecilongo. Abantu bonke ezihonqweni besaba, baqhaqhazela. <verse eid="EXO 19:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="EXO 19:17"/>UMosi wasebakhokhela ebasusa emathenteni ebasa kuNkulunkulu. Bafika bema ngaphansi kwentaba. <verse eid="EXO 19:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="EXO 19:18"/>Intaba yonke iSinayi yembeswa yintuthu ngoba <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wehlela phezu kwayo ngesimo somlilo. Intuthu yathunqa ngamandla isiya phezulu kungathi iphuma emphongolweni. <verse eid="EXO 19:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="EXO 19:19"/>Njalo umsindo wecilongo waya ulokhu ukhula. UMosi wakhuluma, kwathi ilizwi likaNkulunkulu lamphendula.<verse eid="EXO 19:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="EXO 19:20"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wehlela phezu kwentaba iSinayi, wabizela uMosi khona. Ngakho uMosi wakhwela, <verse eid="EXO 19:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="EXO 19:21"/><char style="nd">UThixo</char> wasesithi kuye, “Buyela phansi uyexwayisa abantu ukuba bangaqali ukweqa imingcele ukuba babone <char style="nd">uThixo</char> ngoba bangafa ngobunengi. <verse eid="EXO 19:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="EXO 19:22"/>Labaphristi abaya <char style="nd">kuThixo</char> kumele bazenze babengcwele, funa <char style="nd">uThixo</char> ababhubhise.”<verse eid="EXO 19:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="EXO 19:23"/>UMosi wathi <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>, “Akulamuntu ongakhwela entabeni yeSinayi ngoba wena ngokwakho wathi bangakwenzi lokho. Uthe ngenze imingcele egombolozela intaba ngitshele abantu bangasondeli kuyo ngoba ingcwele.”<verse eid="EXO 19:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="EXO 19:24"/>Kodwa <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wathi, “Yehla uyebuya lo-Aroni. Kodwa abaphristi labantu akumelanga ukuba beqe imingcele besiza lapho ngoba ngingabaphendukela.”<verse eid="EXO 19:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="EXO 19:25"/>Ngakho uMosi wehla waya ebantwini wabatshela.<verse eid="EXO 19:25"/></para>
  <chapter eid="EXO 19"/>
  <chapter number="20" style="c" sid="EXO 20"/>
  <para style="s1">ImiThetho EliTshumi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="EXO 20:1"/>UNkulunkulu wakhuluma amazwi wonke la wathi:<verse eid="EXO 20:1"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="EXO 20:2"/>“<char style="nd">NginguThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wakho owakukhupha eGibhithe, elizweni lobugqili.<verse eid="EXO 20:2"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="EXO 20:3"/>Ungabi labanye onkulunkulu ngaphandle kwami.<verse eid="EXO 20:3"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="EXO 20:4"/>Ungazenzeli isithombe ngesimo saloba yini esezulwini phezulu loba phansi emhlabeni kumbe ngaphansi kwamanzi. <verse eid="EXO 20:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="EXO 20:5"/>Ungazikhothameli loba ukuzikhonza; ngoba mina <char style="nd">Thixo</char> uNkulunkulu wakho nginguNkulunkulu olobukhwele, ojezisa abantwana ngenxa yezono zabazali babo kuze kube yisizukulwane sesithathu lesesine salabo abangizondayo, <verse eid="EXO 20:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="EXO 20:6"/>kodwa ngitshengisela uthando kuzizukulwane eziyinkulungwane zalabo abangithandayo njalo begcina imilayo yami.<verse eid="EXO 20:6"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="EXO 20:7"/>Ungadlali ngebizo <char style="nd">likaThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wakho ngoba <char style="nd">uThixo</char> kayikumyekela olecala lokudlala ngebizo lakhe.<verse eid="EXO 20:7"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="EXO 20:8"/>Khumbula usuku lweSabatha ngokulwenza lubengcwele. <verse eid="EXO 20:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="EXO 20:9"/>Okwensuku eziyisithupha uzasebenza wenze yonke imisebenzi yakho, <verse eid="EXO 20:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="EXO 20:10"/>kodwa usuku lwesikhombisa luyiSabatha <char style="nd">kuThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wakho. Ngalo awuyikwenza loba yiwuphi umsebenzi, wena, loba indodana yakho, loba indodakazi yakho, loba inceku kumbe incekukazi yakho, loba izifuyo zakho loba isihambi esikwethekeleleyo emzini wakho. <verse eid="EXO 20:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="EXO 20:11"/>Ngoba ngensuku eziyisithupha <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wenza amazulu lomhlaba, ulwandle lakho konke okukukho, kodwa waphumula ngosuku lwesikhombisa. Ngakho-ke walubusisa usuku lweSabatha walwenza lwaba ngcwele.<verse eid="EXO 20:11"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="EXO 20:12"/>Hlonipha uyihlo lonyoko ukuze impilo yakho ibende elizweni akunika lona <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wakho.<verse eid="EXO 20:12"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="EXO 20:13"/>Ungabulali.<verse eid="EXO 20:13"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="EXO 20:14"/>Ungafebi.<verse eid="EXO 20:14"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="EXO 20:15"/>Ungantshontshi.<verse eid="EXO 20:15"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="EXO 20:16"/>Ungafakazi amanga ngomakhelwane wakho.<verse eid="EXO 20:16"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="EXO 20:17"/>Ungahawukeli indlu kamakhelwane wakho. Ungahawukeli umfazi kamakhelwane wakho, loba inceku kumbe incekukazi yakhe, inkabi yakhe loba ubabhemi wakhe loba yini ekamakhelwane wakho.”<verse eid="EXO 20:17"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="EXO 20:18"/>Kwathi abantu besizwa umdumo bebona lombane, besizwa icilongo njalo bebona intaba ithunqa intuthu, bathuthumela ngokwesaba. Bema khatshana, <verse eid="EXO 20:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="EXO 20:19"/>bathi kuMosi, “Khuluma kithi wena sizakulalela. Kodwa uNkulunkulu kangakhulumi kithi yena ngokwakhe ngoba singafa.”<verse eid="EXO 20:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="EXO 20:20"/>UMosi wathi, “Lingesabi, uNkulunkulu uzelihlola ukuze limesabe lokuze lingoni.”<verse eid="EXO 20:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="EXO 20:21"/>Abantu basala belokhu bemi bucwadlanyana, uMosi wangena phakathi komnyama waya lapho okwakuloNkulunkulu khona.<verse eid="EXO 20:21"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Izithombe Lama-alithare</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="EXO 20:22"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wathi kuMosi, “Tshela abantu bako-Israyeli uthi, ‘Lizibonele lina ngokwenu ukuthi ngikhulume lani ngisezulwini. <verse eid="EXO 20:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="EXO 20:23"/>Lingenzi onkulunkulu ukuba babekhona kanye lami; lingazenzeli onkulunkulu besiliva kumbe onkulunkulu begolide.<verse eid="EXO 20:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="EXO 20:24"/>Ngakhelani i-alithari ngomhlabathi lenzele kulo umhlatshelo womnikelo wokutshiswa, leminikelo yobudlelwano, izimvu lembuzi kanye lenkomo zenu. Loba kungaphi lapho engizakwenza ibizo lami lihlonitshwe khona, ngizakuza kini ngilibusise. <verse eid="EXO 20:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="EXO 20:25"/>Nxa lingakhela i-alithari ngamatshe, lingaze lawabaza lawomatshe ngoba lizalingcolisa nxa lingasebenzisa okokubaza kulo. <verse eid="EXO 20:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="EXO 20:26"/>Lingaze laya e-alithareni lami ngezikhwelo funa ubunqunu benu bembulwe khona lapho.’ ”<verse eid="EXO 20:26"/></para>
  <chapter eid="EXO 20"/>
  <chapter number="21" style="c" sid="EXO 21"/>
  <para style="s1">Imithetho Etshiyeneyo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="EXO 21:1"/>“Nansi imithetho ozayethula phambi kwabo.”<verse eid="EXO 21:1"/></para>
  <para style="s2">Izinceku EzingamaHebheru</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="EXO 21:2"/>“Nxa ungathenga isisebenzi esingumHebheru kumele sikusebenzele okweminyaka eyisithupha. Kodwa emnyakeni wesikhombisa kuzamele usikhulule kungelanhlawulo. <verse eid="EXO 21:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="EXO 21:3"/>Nxa sifike sodwa, kumele sikhululwe sihambe sodwa kodwa nxa silomfazi ekufikeni kwasokumele sihambe laye. <verse eid="EXO 21:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="EXO 21:4"/>Nxa umqhatshi waso angasipha umfazi asizalele amadodana lamadodakazi, owesifazane labantwabakhe bazakuba ngabomqhatshi, njalo indoda izazihambela yodwa ikhululekile.<verse eid="EXO 21:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="EXO 21:5"/>Kodwa nxa isisebenzi singathi, ‘Ngiyayithanda inkosi yami lomkami labantwabami, njalo kangifuni kukhululwa,’ <verse eid="EXO 21:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="EXO 21:6"/>ngakho inkosi yaso kumele isihambise kubahluleli. Izasisa emnyango kumbe emgubazini abesesibhoboza indlebe yaso ngosungulo. Ngakho-ke sizakuba yisisebenzi sayo okwempilo yaso yonke.<verse eid="EXO 21:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="EXO 21:7"/>Nxa indoda ingathengisa indodakazi yayo njengesigqili, indodakazi kayingakhululeki njengalokho okwenza ezinye inceku. <verse eid="EXO 21:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="EXO 21:8"/>Nxa singathokozisi umnini waso oyabe esikhethile ukuze sibe ngesakhe kumele asiyekele sihlengwe. Akalamvumo yokusithengisa kwabezizwe, ngoba esikhohlisile. <verse eid="EXO 21:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="EXO 21:9"/>Angasikhethela indodana yakhe kumele asinike amalungelo alingana lawendodakazi yakhe. <verse eid="EXO 21:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="EXO 21:10"/>Angathatha omunye umfazi akumelanga asincitshe ukudla, izigqoko lamalungelo okwenda. <verse eid="EXO 21:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="EXO 21:11"/>Angayekela ukusipha izinto lezi ezintathu sikhululekile ukuthi sizihambele kungahlawulwanga mali.”<verse eid="EXO 21:11"/></para>
  <para style="s2">Imithetho Ngabalimazanayo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="EXO 21:12"/>“Wonke umuntu otshaya omunye ambulale laye kumele abulawe. <verse eid="EXO 21:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="EXO 21:13"/>Kodwa nxa engakwenzanga ngabomo, uNkulunkulu evumele ukuba kwenzakale, kumele abalekele endaweni engizayiphawula. <verse eid="EXO 21:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="EXO 21:14"/>Kodwa umuntu angaceba ukubulala omunye ngabomo, msuseni e-alithareni lami liyembulala.<verse eid="EXO 21:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="EXO 21:15"/>Wonke umuntu ohlasela uyise kumbe unina kumele abulawe.<verse eid="EXO 21:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="EXO 21:16"/>Wonke umuntu othumba omunye abesemthengisa kumbe aficwe elaye kumele abulawe.<verse eid="EXO 21:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="EXO 21:17"/>Wonke umuntu othuka uyise kumbe unina kumele abulawe.<verse eid="EXO 21:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="EXO 21:18"/>Nxa amadoda angaxabana omunye abesetshaya omunye ngelitshe kumbe ngenqindi, angafi kodwa agule alale phansi, <verse eid="EXO 21:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="EXO 21:19"/>lowo ophose inqindi kasoze anikwe umlandu nxa omunye angavuka abesehambahamba ephethe intonga yakhe; lanxa kunjalo kumele ahlawule indoda elimeleyo ngokulahlekelwa yisikhathi njalo ayelaphise.<verse eid="EXO 21:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="EXO 21:20"/>Nxa umuntu angatshaya isigqili sakhe sesilisa kumbe esesifazane ngomqwayi, isigqili besesisifa ngenxa yalesisenzo, kumele ajeziswe, <verse eid="EXO 21:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="EXO 21:21"/>kodwa kasoze ajeziswe nxa isigqili singasila ngemva kwelanga elilodwa kumbe insuku ezimbili, ngoba isigqili siyimpahla yakhe.<verse eid="EXO 21:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="EXO 21:22"/>Nxa amadoda alwayo angatshaya umfazi ozithweleyo abesebeletha isikhathi sakhe singakafiki, kodwa engalimalanga kakubi, owonileyo kumele ahlawuliswe lokho okuyabe kubizelwe yindoda yomfazi kwasekuvunywa ngumthethwandaba. <verse eid="EXO 21:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="EXO 21:23"/>Kodwa kungangabi lokulimala okubi, kumele impilo ibhadalwe ngempilo, <verse eid="EXO 21:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="EXO 21:24"/>ilihlo ngelihlo, izinyo ngezinyo, isandla ngesandla, unyawo ngonyawo. <verse eid="EXO 21:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="EXO 21:25"/>Ukutshiswa ngokutshiswa, isilonda ngesilonda, ukulimala ngokulimala.<verse eid="EXO 21:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="EXO 21:26"/>Nxa umuntu angatshaya isigqili sakhe sesilisa kumbe esesifazane elihlweni alipatshaze, kumele asiyekele isisebenzi sizihambele kube yinhlawulo yelihlo. <verse eid="EXO 21:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="EXO 21:27"/>Angatshaya akhumule izinyo lesigqili sesilisa kumbe esesifazane, kumele asiyekele isisebenzi sizihambele kube yinhlawulo yezinyo.<verse eid="EXO 21:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="EXO 21:28"/>Nxa inkunzi ingahlaba indoda kumbe umfazi afe, leyonkunzi kumele itshaywe ngamatshe ize ife njalo inyama yayo kayingadliwa. Kodwa umnikazi wenkunzi akumelanga etheswe umlandu. <verse eid="EXO 21:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="EXO 21:29"/>Kodwa nxa inkunzi ivele ilomkhuba wokuhlaba abantu, njalo umnikazi eseke wakhuzwa kodwa wekela ukuyivalela ibisibulala indoda kumbe umfazi, inkunzi kumele ibulawe ngamatshe lomnikazi abulawe. <verse eid="EXO 21:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="EXO 21:30"/>Kodwa kungathiwa kahlawule, angahlenga impilo yakhe ngokuhlawula lokho okuyabe kubiziwe. <verse eid="EXO 21:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="EXO 21:31"/>Umthetho lo uyasebenza njalo nxa inkunzi ingahlaba indodana kumbe indodakazi. <verse eid="EXO 21:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="EXO 21:32"/>Nxa inkunzi ingahlaba isigqili sesilisa kumbe esesifazane, umnikazi kumele ahlawule amashekeli angamatshumi amathathu esiliva kumnini wesigqili, njalo inkunzi kumele ibulawe ngamatshe.<verse eid="EXO 21:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="EXO 21:33"/>Nxa umuntu etshiya umgodi ukhamisile, loba esimba umgodi angawusibekeli kuwele kuwo inkabi ingabe ubabhemi, <verse eid="EXO 21:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="EXO 21:34"/>umninimgodi kahlawule; kahlawule umnikazi, isifuyo esifileyo besesisiba ngesakhe.<verse eid="EXO 21:34"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="EXO 21:35"/>Nxa inkunzi yomuntu ingalimaza eyomunye kuzamele ukuthi bathengise leyo ephilayo, babelane imali lesidumbu saleyo efileyo ngokulinganayo. <verse eid="EXO 21:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="EXO 21:36"/>Kodwa nxa kusaziwa ukuthi inkunzi ivele ilomkhuba wokuhlaba ezinye, kodwa umnikazi engayivaleli esibayeni, umnikazi kumele ahlawule isifuyo ngesinye isifuyo, njalo isifuyo esifileyo sizakuba ngesakhe.”<verse eid="EXO 21:36"/></para>
  <chapter eid="EXO 21"/>
  <chapter number="22" style="c" sid="EXO 22"/>
  <para style="s2">Ukuvikelwa Kwempahla</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="EXO 22:1"/>“Nxa umuntu angantshontsha inkabi kumbe imvu abeseyibulala kumbe ayithengise, kumele ahlawule ngenkomo ezinhlanu zokuhlawula inkabi, lezimvu ezine zokuhlawula imvu.<verse eid="EXO 22:1"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="EXO 22:2"/>Nxa isela lingafunyanwa ligqekeza ebusuku beselitshaywa life, lowo ozivikelayo kalacala lokuchitha igazi, <verse eid="EXO 22:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="EXO 22:3"/>kodwa kungenzeka ilanga selikhwelile uyabe elomlandu wokuchitha igazi.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="EXO 22:3">Isela kumele lihlawule sibili, kodwa nxa lingelalutho, kumele lithengiswe ukwenzela ukuthi lokhu kube yinhlawulo yokuntshontsha kwalo. <verse eid="EXO 22:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="EXO 22:4"/>Nxa isifuyo esintshontshiweyo singatholakala siphila ezandleni zesela, kungaba yinkabi kumbe ubabhemi loba imvu, kumele lihlawule okuphindwe kabili.<verse eid="EXO 22:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="EXO 22:5"/>Nxa umuntu angayadlisa izifuyo zakhe ensimini kumbe esivinini abeseziyekela zizihambela besezisiya kudla ensimini yeyinye indoda, kumele ahlawule ngezithelo ezinhle zensimu yakhe loba isivini sakhe.<verse eid="EXO 22:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="EXO 22:6"/>Nxa kuthungelwa umlilo ulumatha emeveni kuze kutshe lamahlanga amabele loba amabele angakavunwa loba insimu, othungele umlilo kumele ahlawule konke.<verse eid="EXO 22:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="EXO 22:7"/>Nxa umuntu anganika umakhelwane wakhe isiliva kumbe impahla ukuba amgcinele izinto lezi besezintshontshwa endlini kamakhelwane, isela lingabanjwa kumele lihlawule okuphindwe kabili. <verse eid="EXO 22:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="EXO 22:8"/>Kodwa nxa isela lingabanjwanga, umnikazi wendlu kumele ame phambi kwabahluleli ukuze kubonakale ingabe uke wabeka izandla empahleni zalowo omgcinisileyo na. <verse eid="EXO 22:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="EXO 22:9"/>Kuzozonke izehlakalo eziqondene lokugcina ngaphandle komthetho inkabi, ubabhemi, imvu, isigqoko kumbe yonke impahla elahlekileyo omunye umuntu angathi ngayo, ‘Lokhu ngokwami,’ wonke amacele womabili kumele alethe izindaba zawo phambi kwabahluleli. Lowo abahluleli abazakuthi ulecala kumele ahlawule okuphindwe kabili kumakhelwane wakhe.<verse eid="EXO 22:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="EXO 22:10"/>Nxa umuntu angasisela umakhelwane wakhe ubabhemi, inkabi, imvu kumbe esinye isifuyo ukuze kugcinakale besekusifa kumbe kulimale kumbe kuthathwe kungelamuntu okhangeleyo, <verse eid="EXO 22:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="EXO 22:11"/>udaba lwabantu laba luzaqedwa ngokufunga phambi <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char> ukuthi umakhelwane konanga impahla yomunye umuntu. Umnikazi kumele akwemukele lokhu njalo akulanhlawulo edingakalayo. <verse eid="EXO 22:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="EXO 22:12"/>Kodwa nxa isifuyo santshontshwa sikumasiselwa kumele ahlawule umnikazi. <verse eid="EXO 22:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="EXO 22:13"/>Nxa isifuyo sidatshudatshulwe yinyamazana yeganga saba yiziqa, uzaletha izicucu eziseleyo njengobufakazi njalo akusoze kudingakale ukuthi ahlawulele isifuyo esidatshudatshuliweyo.<verse eid="EXO 22:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="EXO 22:14"/>Nxa umuntu angaboleka isifuyo kumakhelwane wakhe, besesilimala kumbe sife ngesikhathi umniniso engekho, kumele ahlawule. <verse eid="EXO 22:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="EXO 22:15"/>Kodwa nxa umnikazi ekhona, lowo owasebolekayo akumelanga ahlawule. Nxa isifuyo siqhatshiwe, imali ehlawulwe ukusiqhatsha igoqela inhlawulo yokulahlekelwa.”<verse eid="EXO 22:15"/></para>
  <para style="s2">Imithetho Yokuhlalisana</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="EXO 22:16"/>“Nxa indoda ingaqila intombi egcweleyo engakathenjiswa ilale layo, kumele ikhuphe amalobolo, leyontombi ibe ngumkayo. <verse eid="EXO 22:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="EXO 22:17"/>Nxa uyise esala kokuphela ukuthi ayendisele, kumele akhuphe inhlawulo ekhutshelwa amantombazana agcweleyo.<verse eid="EXO 22:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="EXO 22:18"/>Lingavumeli umthakathi ukuthi aphile.<verse eid="EXO 22:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="EXO 22:19"/>Wonke umuntu olala lenyamazana kumele abulawe.<verse eid="EXO 22:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="EXO 22:20"/>Loba ngubani onikela kwabanye onkulunkulu ngaphandle <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char> kumele abhujiswe.<verse eid="EXO 22:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="EXO 22:21"/>Lingahlukuluzi owezizweni ngoba lani lalingabezizweni eGibhithe.<verse eid="EXO 22:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="EXO 22:22"/>Lingaqilibezeli umfelokazi kumbe intandane, <verse eid="EXO 22:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="EXO 22:23"/>ngoba lingakwenza, besebekhala kimi ngizakuzwa ukukhala kwabo; <verse eid="EXO 22:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="EXO 22:24"/>ulaka lwami luzavutha, ngibulale ngenkemba; abafazi benu babe ngabafelokazi labantwabenu babe zintandane.<verse eid="EXO 22:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="EXO 22:25"/>Nxa lingebolekisa imali omunye wabantu bami ohluphekayo phakathi kwenu, akumelanga lenze njengebhizimisi yokweboleka abanye imali, lingamhlawulisi inzuzo. <verse eid="EXO 22:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="EXO 22:26"/>Nxa ungathatha ijazi likamakhelwane wakho ulenze isibambiso, kumele ulibuyisele ilanga lingakatshoni, <verse eid="EXO 22:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="EXO 22:27"/>ngoba ijazi lelo yilo lodwa embesa ngalo ubunqunu bakhe. Kambe kuyini okunye abangalala kukho? Nxa bengakhala kimi, ngizabezwa ngoba ngilozwelo.<verse eid="EXO 22:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="EXO 22:28"/>Lingahlambazi uNkulunkulu kumbe lithuke umbusi wabantu bakini.<verse eid="EXO 22:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="EXO 22:29"/>Lingagodli iminikelo eziphaleni zenu loba ezimbizeni zewayini lenu.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="EXO 22:29">Kumele lilethe kimi amadodana enu angamazibulo. <verse eid="EXO 22:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="EXO 22:30"/>Yenzani njalo ngenkomo lezimvu zenu. Yekelani zihlale labonina okwensuku eziyisikhombisa kodwa linginike zona ngosuku lwesificaminwembili.<verse eid="EXO 22:30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="EXO 22:31"/>Lizakuba ngabantu bami abangcwele. Ngakho lingaze ladla inyama yenyamazana eyabe idatshudatshulwe yizilo zeganga; iphoseleni izinja.”<verse eid="EXO 22:31"/></para>
  <chapter eid="EXO 22"/>
  <chapter number="23" style="c" sid="EXO 23"/>
  <para style="s2">Imithetho Yokulunga Lomusa</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="EXO 23:1"/>“Ungahambi ukhuluma izindaba zamanga. Ungahlanganyeli lomuntu omubi ngoba ngufakazi olomona.<verse eid="EXO 23:1"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="EXO 23:2"/>Ungenzi okubi ulandela inengi labantu. Nxa ufakaza emthethwandaba, ungaphenduleli iqiniso ngokuvumelana labanengi, <verse eid="EXO 23:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="EXO 23:3"/>njalo ungazweli umuntu ecaleni ngoba engumyanga.<verse eid="EXO 23:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="EXO 23:4"/>Ungahlangana lenkomo kumbe ubabhemi wesitha sakho elahlekile, mnqande umbuyisele kumnikazi. <verse eid="EXO 23:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="EXO 23:5"/>Nxa ufica ubabhemi womuntu okuzondayo ewiswe ngumthwalo, ungamtshiyi, umncedise umvuse.<verse eid="EXO 23:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="EXO 23:6"/>Ahlulela kuhle abayanga bakini emacaleni. <verse eid="EXO 23:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="EXO 23:7"/>Ungabungeni ubufakazi bamanga, njalo ungabulali muntu ongelacala loba oqotho ngoba kangiyi kumyekela olecala.<verse eid="EXO 23:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="EXO 23:8"/>Lingavumi ukufunjathiswa ngoba ukufunjathiswa kufiphaza ababonayo besebeguqula amazwi omuntu omsulwa.<verse eid="EXO 23:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="EXO 23:9"/>Ungancindezeli owezizweni, lina ngokwenu liyakwazi ukuthi kunjani ukuba ngabezizweni, njengoba lalingabezizweni eGibhithe.”<verse eid="EXO 23:9"/></para>
  <para style="s2">Imithetho YeSabatha</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="EXO 23:10"/>“Okweminyaka eyisithupha lizalima amasimu enu livune amabele, <verse eid="EXO 23:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="EXO 23:11"/>kodwa kuzakuthi ngomnyaka wesikhombisa liyekele amasimu enu alaluke engalinywanga. Ngakho abangabayanga phakathi kwenu bazazuza ukudla kuwo, kuthi lezinyamazana zeganga zidle okuseleyo. Lizakwenza njalo okufananayo ngezivini zenu kanye lezihlahla zenu zama-oliva.<verse eid="EXO 23:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="EXO 23:12"/>Uzakwenza imisebenzi yakho okwensuku eziyisithupha, kodwa ngosuku lwesikhombisa ungasebenzi, ukuze inkabi yakho lobabhemi wakho kuphumule, kuthi isigqili esazalelwa endlini yakho kanye lowezizweni baphumule.<verse eid="EXO 23:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="EXO 23:13"/>Qaphelisisani lenze konke engilitshela khona. Lingamemezi amabizo abanye onkulunkulu; kawangezwakali ephuma ezindebeni zenu.”<verse eid="EXO 23:13"/></para>
  <para style="s2">Imikhosi Emithathu Yomnyaka</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="EXO 23:14"/>“Kathathu ngomnyaka kufanele lingithakazelele umkhosi.<verse eid="EXO 23:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="EXO 23:15"/>Lizathakazelela uMkhosi weSinkwa esingelaMvubelo; okwensuku eziyisikhombisa dlanini isinkwa esingelamvubelo, njengokulilaya kwami. Kwenzeni lokhu ngesikhathi esimisiweyo senyanga ka-Avivi, ngoba ngaleyonyanga yikho elaphuma khona eGibhithe.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="EXO 23:15">Kakungabi lamuntu ozakuma phambi kwami engaphathanga lutho.<verse eid="EXO 23:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="EXO 23:16"/>Lithakazelele uMkhosi wokuVuna lokolibo kwenu ezilimweni zenu zemasimini.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="EXO 23:16">Lithakazelele uMkhosi wokuButhelela nxa selibutha izilimo zenu emasimini.<verse eid="EXO 23:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="EXO 23:17"/>Kathathu ngomnyaka amadoda wonke kufanele ayebonakala phambi <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char> Wobukhosi.<verse eid="EXO 23:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="EXO 23:18"/>Linganikeli igazi lomhlatshelo kimi ndawonye laloba yini elemvubelo.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="EXO 23:18">Amahwahwa eminikelo yemikhosi yami akumelanga agcinwe kuze kuse.<verse eid="EXO 23:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="EXO 23:19"/>Lethani okolibo kwenu okuhle kakhulu endlini <char style="nd">kaThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wenu.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="EXO 23:19">Lingapheki izinyane lembuzi ngochago lukanina.”<verse eid="EXO 23:19"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ingilosi KaNkulunkulu Izalungisa Indlela</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="EXO 23:20"/>“Khangelani, sengithumela ingilosi phambi kwenu ukuze ilivikele endleleni yenu njalo ize ilifikise endaweni engililungisele yona. <verse eid="EXO 23:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="EXO 23:21"/>Liyinanzelele ingilosi yami njalo lilalele ekutshoyo. Lingayihlamukeli ngoba kayizukulithethelela nxa lingayihlamukela, njengoba iBizo lami likuyo. <verse eid="EXO 23:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="EXO 23:22"/>Nxa lingalalelisisa ekutshoyo njalo lenze konke engikutshoyo, ngizakuba yisitha sezitha zenu njalo ngizamelana lalabo abamisana lani. <verse eid="EXO 23:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="EXO 23:23"/>Ingilosi yami izahamba phambi kwenu ize ilingenise elizweni lama-Amori, lamaHithi, lamaPherizi, lamaKhenani lamaHivi kanye lamaJebusi njalo ngizababhubhisa. <verse eid="EXO 23:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="EXO 23:24"/>Lingabakhothameli onkulunkulu babo, lingabakhonzi njalo lingalandeli imikhuba yabo. Kufanele libhidlize onkulunkulu babo njalo lidilize amatshe abo abawakhonzayo. <verse eid="EXO 23:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="EXO 23:25"/>Mkhonzeni <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wenu, kuzakuthi isibusiso sakhe sibe phezu kokudla laphezu kwamanzi enu. Ngizasusa imikhuhlane phakathi kwenu, <verse eid="EXO 23:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="EXO 23:26"/>njalo kakho ozaswela loba abe yinyumba ezweni lenu. Ngizaphelelisa insuku zenu.<verse eid="EXO 23:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="EXO 23:27"/>Ngizathumela uchuku lwami phambi kwenu njalo ngisanganise zonke izizwe elizahlangana lazo. Ngizakwenza zonke izitha zenu zifulathele zilibalekele. <verse eid="EXO 23:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="EXO 23:28"/>Ngizathumela olonyovu phambi kwenu ukuze basuse amaHivi, amaKhenani kanye lamaHithi endleleni yenu. <verse eid="EXO 23:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="EXO 23:29"/>Kodwa angiyikubasusa ngomnyaka munye, ngoba ilizwe lingasala lingasela muntu besekusithi izinyamazana zeganga zande zilikhulele. <verse eid="EXO 23:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="EXO 23:30"/>Ngizabasusa kancanekancane phambi kwenu, lani lize lande lenelise ukuthatha ilizwe.<verse eid="EXO 23:30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="EXO 23:31"/>Ngizabeka imingcele kusukela oLwandle oluBomvu kusiya oLwandle lwamaFilistiya, njalo kusuka enkangala kusiya emfuleni uYufrathe. Ngakho abantu abahlala kulelolizwe ngizabanikela ezandleni zenu ukuze libadudule. <verse eid="EXO 23:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="EXO 23:32"/>Lingenzi isivumelwano labo loba labonkulunkulu babo. <verse eid="EXO 23:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="EXO 23:33"/>Kabangahlali lani ezweni lenu, funa balenze lingonele, ngoba ukukhonza kwabo onkulunkulu babo kuzakuba yisifu kini.”<verse eid="EXO 23:33"/></para>
  <chapter eid="EXO 23"/>
  <chapter number="24" style="c" sid="EXO 24"/>
  <para style="s1">Ukumiswa Kwesivumelwano</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="EXO 24:1"/>Ngakho <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wasesithi kuMosi, “Woza <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>, wena lo-Aroni, uNadabi lo-Abhihu, kanye labadala bako-Israyeli abangamatshumi ayisikhombisa. Lizakhonza libucwala, <verse eid="EXO 24:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="EXO 24:2"/>kodwa uMosi yedwa zwi uzasondela <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>; abanye kabafanelanga ukusondela eduze. Kanti-ke abantu kabafanelanga ukuza laye.”<verse eid="EXO 24:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="EXO 24:3"/>Kwathi uMosi esebuyele ebantwini wabatshela wonke amazwi kanye lemilayo <char style="nd">kaThixo</char>, abantu bakwamukela, bavungama ngalizwi linye bathi, “Konke okutshiwo <char style="nd">nguThixo</char> sizakwenza.” <verse eid="EXO 24:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="EXO 24:4"/>UMosi waseloba konke <char style="nd">uThixo</char> ayekutshilo.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="EXO 24:4">Ngosuku olulandelayo uMosi wavuka kusesele wakha i-alithari ewatheni lwentaba wamisa khona izinsika zamatshe alitshumi lambili emele izizwe ezilitshumi lambili zako-Israyeli. <verse eid="EXO 24:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="EXO 24:5"/>Wasethuma amajaha ako-Israyeli ahamba ayanikela umnikelo wokutshiswa njalo benza imihlatshelo ngenkunzi ezincane njengomnikelo wobudlelwano <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>. <verse eid="EXO 24:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="EXO 24:6"/>UMosi wasethatha ingxenye yegazi walithela emiganwini eyayizingubhe, elinye wachela ngalo phezu kwe-alithari. <verse eid="EXO 24:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="EXO 24:7"/>Ngakho wathatha iNcwadi yeSivumelwano wayifundela abantu. Bona bavuma besithi, “Sizakwenza konke okutshiwo <char style="nd">nguThixo</char>; sizamlalela.”<verse eid="EXO 24:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="EXO 24:8"/>Ngemva kwalokho uMosi wathatha igazi wachela ngalo abantu esithi kubo, “Leli ligazi lesivumelwano <char style="nd">sikaThixo</char> asenze lani ngokuqondene lawo wonke lamazwi.”<verse eid="EXO 24:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="EXO 24:9"/>UMosi lo-Aroni, uNadabi lo-Abhihu kanye labadala bako-Israyeli abangamatshumi ayisikhombisa bakhwela <verse eid="EXO 24:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="EXO 24:10"/>bayabona uNkulunkulu ka-Israyeli. Ngaphansi kwezinyawo zakhe kwakungani ngumgwaqo owenziwe ngesafaya, kukhanya njengokukhanya komkhathi uqobo. <verse eid="EXO 24:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="EXO 24:11"/>Kodwa uNkulunkulu kazange abanine ngesandla sakhe laba bakhokheli bako-Israyeli; sebembonile uNkulunkulu badla banatha.<verse eid="EXO 24:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="EXO 24:12"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wathi kuMosi, “Khwela uze kimi entabeni njalo uhlale lapha, ngizakunika izibhebhedu zamatshe, engilobe kuzo imithetho lemilayo eyiziqondiso zabo.”<verse eid="EXO 24:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="EXO 24:13"/>Ngakho uMosi wasuka loJoshuwa umsizi wakhe, uMosi wasekhwela entabeni kaNkulunkulu. <verse eid="EXO 24:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="EXO 24:14"/>Wathi ebadaleni, “Silindelani khonapha size siphenduke. U-Aroni loHuri bazasala lani, kuzakuthi abaxabanayo babonane labo.”<verse eid="EXO 24:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="EXO 24:15"/>Kwathi uMosi esekhwele intaba, yasibekelwa liyezi, <verse eid="EXO 24:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="EXO 24:16"/>inkazimulo <char style="nd">kaThixo</char> yagcwala entabeni yaseSinayi. Iyezi lembesa intaba okwensuku eziyisithupha kwathi ngosuku lwesikhombisa <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wabiza uMosi eseyezini. <verse eid="EXO 24:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="EXO 24:17"/>Ebantwini bako-Israyeli inkazimulo <char style="nd">kaThixo</char> yabonakala injengomlilo otshisa uqothule phezu kwentaba. <verse eid="EXO 24:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="EXO 24:18"/>Ngakho uMosi wangena eyezini ekhwela intaba. Wahlala khonale entabeni okwensuku ezingamatshumi amane lobusuku obungamatshumi amane.<verse eid="EXO 24:18"/></para>
  <chapter eid="EXO 24"/>
  <chapter number="25" style="c" sid="EXO 25"/>
  <para style="s1">Iminikelo YeThabanikeli</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="EXO 25:1"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wathi kuMosi, <verse eid="EXO 25:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="EXO 25:2"/>“Tshela abako-Israyeli bangilethele umnikelo. Uzakwamukela umnikelo emuntwini munye ngamunye ofuqwa yinhliziyo yakhe ukuthi anikele.<verse eid="EXO 25:2"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="EXO 25:3"/>Le yiyo iminikelo ozayamukela nxa sebenikela:</para>
  <para style="b" vid="EXO 25:3"/>
  <para style="li1" vid="EXO 25:3">igolide, isiliva kanye lethusi,<verse eid="EXO 25:3"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="EXO 25:4"/>okwelukiweyo lamalembu aluhlaza, ayibubende kanye labomvu, lelembu elicolekileyo,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="EXO 25:4">loboya bembuzi,<verse eid="EXO 25:4"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="EXO 25:5"/>izikhumba zenqama eziphendulwe ngomphendulo obomvu, kanye lezikhumba zezinyamazana eziqinileyo,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="EXO 25:5">lezigodo zesihlahla somʼakhakhiya,<verse eid="EXO 25:5"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="EXO 25:6"/>amafutha e-oliva awokukhanyisa isibane,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="EXO 25:6">amakha azasetshenziswa lamafutha okugcoba abakhethiweyo lephunga lempepha elimnandi,<verse eid="EXO 25:6"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="EXO 25:7"/>amatshe e-onikisi, lamanye amatshe aligugu azathungelwa esembathweni semahlombe lesesifubeni.<verse eid="EXO 25:7"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="EXO 25:8"/>Bangakhele indlu engcwele, ngalokho ngizahlala phakathi kwabo. <verse eid="EXO 25:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="EXO 25:9"/>Yenza ithabanikeli leli kanye leziceciso zalo ngendlela engizakutshengisa yona.”<verse eid="EXO 25:9"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Umtshokotsho Wesivumelwano</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="EXO 25:10"/>“Kabenze umtshokotsho ngezigodo zesihlahla somʼakhakhiya, ubude bawo kube zingalo ezimbili ezilengxenye, ububanzi kube yingalo elengxenye njalo ukuyaphezulu kwawo kube yingalo elengxenye. <verse eid="EXO 25:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="EXO 25:11"/>Lilihuqe ngegolide elicolekileyo, ngaphakathi langaphandle, ubuye ulizingelezele ngomqolo wegolide. <verse eid="EXO 25:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="EXO 25:12"/>Libumbele amasongo amane egolide liwanamathisele ezinyaweni zalo zozine, amabili kwelinye icele kuthi amabili kwelinye njalo. <verse eid="EXO 25:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="EXO 25:13"/>Beselisenza imijabo ngesihlahla somʼakhakhiya liyihuqe ngegolide. <verse eid="EXO 25:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="EXO 25:14"/>Hlomani imijabo kulawo masongo asemaceleni omtshokotsho kube yizibambo. <verse eid="EXO 25:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="EXO 25:15"/>Izigodo lezi zizahlala emasongweni alumtshokotsho, zingakhitshwa. <verse eid="EXO 25:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="EXO 25:16"/>Beselifaka ubufakazi emtshokotshweni engizakunika bona.<verse eid="EXO 25:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="EXO 25:17"/>Yenzani isihlalo somusa ngegolide elicolekileyo, ubude baso bube zingalo ezimbili ezilengxenye lengxenye eyodwa ububanzi. <verse eid="EXO 25:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="EXO 25:18"/>Lizakwenza amakherubhi amabili ngegolide elikhandiweyo, liwenze ekucineni kwesisibekelo esiyisihlalo somusa emaceleni womabili. <verse eid="EXO 25:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="EXO 25:19"/>Yenzani ikherubhi elilodwa nganxanye kuthi ngakwelinye icele lenze elinye, uzawenza amakherubhi abe yinto yinye lesisibekelo emaceleni womabili. <verse eid="EXO 25:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="EXO 25:20"/>Amakherubhi kumele elulele amaphiko awo phezulu embese isisibekelo ngawo. Kuzamele amakherubhi akhangelane, ubuso bawo bukhangele isisibekelo. <verse eid="EXO 25:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="EXO 25:21"/>Bekani isisibekelo phezu komtshokotsho, ubusufaka ubufakazi engizakunika bona ebhokisini lesivumelwano. <verse eid="EXO 25:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="EXO 25:22"/>Kulapho engizahlangana lawe khona ngikunika imithetho ka-Israyeli ngisesihlalweni somusa, phakathi laphakathi kwamakherubhi aphezu komtshokotsho wobufakazi.”<verse eid="EXO 25:22"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Itafula Yezinkwa</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="EXO 25:23"/>“Bazani itafula ngezigodo zesihlahla somʼakhakhiya, ubude bayo bube zingalo ezimbili, ububanzi bayo bube yingalo eyodwa, kuthi ukudepha kwayo kube yingalo elengxenye. <verse eid="EXO 25:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="EXO 25:24"/>Liyihuqe ngegolide elicolekileyo, beseliyizingelezela ngomthando wegolide. <verse eid="EXO 25:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="EXO 25:25"/>Lenze kuyo ibhanti eliyizingelezileyo, elilingana lobubanzi besandla, beselibumbela kuyo umthando wegolide phezu kwebhanti. <verse eid="EXO 25:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="EXO 25:26"/>Lenze amasongo amane egolide liwafake emagumbini womane enyaweni zetafula. <verse eid="EXO 25:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="EXO 25:27"/>Amasongo kumele asondelelane lebhanti ukuze abambe imijabo ezasetshenziswa ukuthwala itafula. <verse eid="EXO 25:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="EXO 25:28"/>Lungisani imijabo ngesihlahla somʼakhakhiya, liyihuqe ngegolide ukuze lithwale itafula ngayo. <verse eid="EXO 25:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="EXO 25:29"/>Njalo yenzani imiganu lezinditshi zayo ngegolide elicolekileyo kanye lenkezo, imiganu eyingubhe lezitsha zokuthululela iminikelo. <verse eid="EXO 25:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="EXO 25:30"/>Libeke etafuleni isinkwa esiNgcwele ukuze sibe phambi kwami ngezikhathi zonke.”<verse eid="EXO 25:30"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Uluthi Lwesibane</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="EXO 25:31"/>“Lizakwenza uluthi lwesibane ngegolide elicolekileyo. Likhande isidindi salo lomqwayi walo, imbizana zalo lamahlumela alo lamaluba alo likwenze kube yinto yinye. <verse eid="EXO 25:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="EXO 25:32"/>Ingatsha eziyisithupha zixhunywe emaceleni oluthi, ezintathu nganxanye kuthi ezintathu kwelinye icele. <verse eid="EXO 25:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="EXO 25:33"/>Inkezo ezintathu ezibunjwe okwamaluba e-alimondi, amahlumela lamaluba kumele abe sogatsheni lunye, ezintathu egatsheni olulandelayo, kube njalo kuzozonke ingatsha ezixhunywe emqwayini woluthi lwesibane. <verse eid="EXO 25:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="EXO 25:34"/>Kuzakuthi oluthini lwesibane kube lezimbizana ezine ezibunjwe okwamaluba e-alimondi, zilamahlumela lamaluba. <verse eid="EXO 25:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="EXO 25:35"/>Kumele kube lehlumela ngaphansi kwengatsha ezimbili ezixhunywe oluthini lwesibane, ihlumela lesibili ngaphansi kwezinye ezimbili, kuthi ihlumela lesithathu lalo libe ngaphansi kwezinye njalo ezimbili, zonke ingatsha zibe yisithupha. <verse eid="EXO 25:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="EXO 25:36"/>Amahlumela lezingatsha kuzakuba yinto yinye loluthi lwesibane, kukhandwe ngegolide elicolekileyo.<verse eid="EXO 25:36"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="37" style="v" sid="EXO 25:37"/>Ngakho lizalwenzela izibane eziyisikhombisa lizimise phezu kwalo ukuze zikhanyise phambi kwalo. <verse eid="EXO 25:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="EXO 25:38"/>Incijana zentambo lembizana zalo zibe ngezegolide elicolekileyo. <verse eid="EXO 25:38"/><verse number="39" style="v" sid="EXO 25:39"/>Uluthi lwesibane kanye lakho konke okuphathelene laso kuzenziwa ngegolide elicolekileyo eliyisisindo sethalenta elilodwa. <verse eid="EXO 25:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="EXO 25:40"/>Qaphela ukuba wenze konke njengalokhu owakutshengiswa entabeni.”<verse eid="EXO 25:40"/></para>
  <chapter eid="EXO 25"/>
  <chapter number="26" style="c" sid="EXO 26"/>
  <para style="s1">IThabanikeli</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="EXO 26:1"/>“Lenze ithabanikeli ngamakhetheni alitshumi elembu eliphothwe kuhle ngentambo eziluhlaza, eziyibubende kanye lezibomvu, aceciswe ngamakherubhi elukelwe kuhle ngumuntu oleminwe. <verse eid="EXO 26:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="EXO 26:2"/>Amakhetheni wonke kumele ukuthi alingane, abezingalo ezingamatshumi amabili lesificaminwembili ubude njalo ububanzi abezingalo ezine. <verse eid="EXO 26:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="EXO 26:3"/>Lizahlanganisa amakhetheni amahlanu ndawonye, liphinde lenzenjalo lakwamanye amahlanu. <verse eid="EXO 26:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="EXO 26:4"/>Lenze izihitshela ngelembu eliluhlaza emphethweni wekhetheni elisekucineni kwamakhetheni amahlanu elixheni lakuqala, lenze okufanayo elixheni lesibili. <verse eid="EXO 26:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="EXO 26:5"/>Lizakwenza izihitshela ezingamatshumi amahlanu ekhethenini elilodwa liphinde lenze ezinye izihitshela ezingamatshumi amahlanu ekhethenini lokucina elixheni lesibili, izihitshela zikhangelene. <verse eid="EXO 26:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="EXO 26:6"/>Emva kwalokho lizakwenza ingwegwe zegolide ezingamatshumi amahlanu, lizisebenzise ukuhlanganisa amakhetheni ukuze ithabanikeli libe yintonye.<verse eid="EXO 26:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="EXO 26:7"/>Yenzani amakhetheni ngoboya bembuzi abe ngawethente lokubekwa phezu kwethabanikeli, abelitshumi lanye esewonke. <verse eid="EXO 26:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="EXO 26:8"/>Amakhetheni wonke alitshumi lanye alingane, abezingalo ezingamatshumi amathathu ubude, ububanzi abezingalo ezine. <verse eid="EXO 26:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="EXO 26:9"/>Hlanganisani amakhetheni amahlanu abelilixha elilodwa kuthi ayisithupha abe kwelinye ilixha. Ligoqe ikhetheni lesithupha liphindwe kabili phambi kwethente. <verse eid="EXO 26:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="EXO 26:10"/>Yenzani izihitshela ezingamatshumi amahlanu zilandele umphetho wekhetheni elisekucineni kwelixha lakuqala, lenzenjalo lakwelinye ilixha. <verse eid="EXO 26:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="EXO 26:11"/>Beselilungisa ingwegwe zethusi ezingamatshumi amahlanu lizifake ezihitsheleni ukuze zibophe ithente kube yinto yinye. <verse eid="EXO 26:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="EXO 26:12"/>Kuzakuthi-ke isiqa esiseleyo sekhetheni lethente, ingxenye yekhetheni eseleyo, ilenge emuva kwethabanikeli. <verse eid="EXO 26:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="EXO 26:13"/>Amakhetheni ethente azakwedlula ngengalo eyodwa inxa zonke, kuthi okuseleyo kulenge emaceleni ethabanikeli ukuze alembese. <verse eid="EXO 26:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="EXO 26:14"/>Lenze isembeso sethente ngezikhumba zenqama eziphendulwe ngomphendulo obomvu, kuthi phezu kwalokho kube lesembeso sezikhumba eziqinileyo.<verse eid="EXO 26:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="EXO 26:15"/>Yenzani amathala ethabanikeli amiswayo ngezigodo zesihlahla somʼakhakhiya. <verse eid="EXO 26:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="EXO 26:16"/>Ithala linye kumele libe lide okuzingalo ezilitshumi, kuthi ububanzi bube yingalo elengxenye, <verse eid="EXO 26:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="EXO 26:17"/>kube lemisuka emibili ephutshayo ilinganisene. Wonke amathala ethabanikeli enziwe ngale indlela. <verse eid="EXO 26:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="EXO 26:18"/>Yenzani amathala ecele elisezansi kwethabanikeli angamatshumi amabili, <verse eid="EXO 26:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="EXO 26:19"/>beselizenza izisekelo zesiliva ezingamatshumi amane ezizahamba ngaphansi kwawo, izisekelo ezimbili ethaleni linye, sibe sinye ngaphansi kwensika inye ngayinye. <verse eid="EXO 26:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="EXO 26:20"/>Kulelicele elisenyakatho kwethabanikeli, misani amathala angamatshumi amabili <verse eid="EXO 26:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="EXO 26:21"/>kanye lezisekelo zesiliva ezingamatshumi amane, ezimbili ngaphansi kwepulanka linye. <verse eid="EXO 26:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="EXO 26:22"/>Yenzani amathala ayisithupha ecele elisekucineni ngentshonalanga kwethabanikeli, <verse eid="EXO 26:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="EXO 26:23"/>lenze amathala amabili amagumbi asekucineni. <verse eid="EXO 26:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="EXO 26:24"/>Emagumbini womabili la kumele abe lohlonzi oluphindwe kabili kusukela phansi kusiya phezulu, abesehlanganiswa ngesongo elilodwa, wonke abe njalo. <verse eid="EXO 26:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="EXO 26:25"/>Ngakho kuzakuba lamathala ayisificaminwembili lezisekelo zesiliva ezilitshumi lesithupha, ezimbili ngaphansi kwethala linye.<verse eid="EXO 26:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="EXO 26:26"/>Yenzani njalo imithando enqumayo ngezigodo zesihlahla somʼakhakhiya: emihlanu ibe ngeyamathala kwelinye icele lethabanikeli, <verse eid="EXO 26:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="EXO 26:27"/>emihlanu ibe njalo kwelinye icele, kuthi eminye njalo emihlanu ibe ngeyamathala asentshonalanga, ekucineni kwethabanikeli. <verse eid="EXO 26:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="EXO 26:28"/>Umthando waphakathi onqumayo uzakwedlula usuka kulelicele lokucina usiyacina kwelinye phakathi laphakathi kwamathala. <verse eid="EXO 26:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="EXO 26:29"/>Huqani amathala ngegolide lenze amasongo egolide abambe imithando enqumayo. Njalo lihuqe imithando enqumayo ngegolide.<verse eid="EXO 26:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="EXO 26:30"/>Limise ithabanikeli njengokutshengiswa kwakho entabeni.<verse eid="EXO 26:30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="EXO 26:31"/>Yenzani ikhetheni ngelembu elicolekileyo, eliphethwe kuhle ngentambo eziluhlaza, eziyibubende kanye lezibomvu, abe lamakherubhi elukelwe kuwo ngumuntu oleminwe. <verse eid="EXO 26:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="EXO 26:32"/>Liwalengise ngezingwegwana zegolide ensikeni ezine zesihlahla somʼakhakhiya ezihuqwe ngegolide njalo zimiswe phezu kwezisekelo zesiliva. <verse eid="EXO 26:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="EXO 26:33"/>Lengisani-ke ikhetheni ngezingwegwana beselibeka umtshokotsho wobufakazi ngemva kwekhetheni. Ikhetheni lizakwehlukanisa Indawo Engcwele kweNgcwelengcwele. <verse eid="EXO 26:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="EXO 26:34"/>Bekani isisibekelo esiyisihlalo somusa phezu komtshokotsho wobufakazi osendaweni eNgcwelengcwele. <verse eid="EXO 26:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="EXO 26:35"/>Bekani itafula ngaphandle kwekhetheni elisenyakatho kwethabanikeli, beselifaka uluthi lwesibane lukhangelane layo eceleni eliseningizimu.<verse eid="EXO 26:35"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="EXO 26:36"/>Yenzani ikhetheni lesango lethente ngelembu eliphethwe kuhle ngentambo eziluhlaza, eziyibubende kanye lezibomvu kube ngumsebenzi wombalazi ngokuthunga. <verse eid="EXO 26:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="EXO 26:37"/>Yenzelani ikhetheni ingwegwana zegolide kanye lezinsika ezinhlanu ezenziwe ngezigodo zesihlahla somʼakhakhiya ezihuqwe ngegolide. Njalo beseliwafakela izisekelo ezinhlanu ezibunjwe ngethusi.”<verse eid="EXO 26:37"/></para>
  <chapter eid="EXO 26"/>
  <chapter number="27" style="c" sid="EXO 27"/>
  <para style="s1">I-alithari Leminikelo Yokutshiswa</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="EXO 27:1"/>“Lakhe i-alithari ngezigodo zesihlahla somʼakhakhiya libe zingalo ezintathu ukudepha, kumele lilingane inxa zonke, ubude balo bube zingalo ezinhlanu lobubanzi balo bube zingalo ezinhlanu. <verse eid="EXO 27:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="EXO 27:2"/>Egumbini linye ngalinye le-alithari uzakwenza uphondo, kuthi impondo le-alithari kube yinto yinye, ubusulihuqa ngethusi. <verse eid="EXO 27:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="EXO 27:3"/>Izinto zonke ezizasetshenziswa kulo uzazenza ngethusi, imbiza zalo zokubutha umlotha, amafotsholo alo, imiganu yokuchela, amafologwe enyama kanye lezindengezi zokubasela umlilo. <verse eid="EXO 27:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="EXO 27:4"/>Lenzele iminxibo yokosa ngethusi njalo wenze isongo lethusi emagumbini wonke womane. <verse eid="EXO 27:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="EXO 27:5"/>Libeke ngaphansi komphetho we-alithare okuyingxenye yokuya phezulu. <verse eid="EXO 27:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="EXO 27:6"/>Libaze imijabo ye-alithare ngezigodo zesihlahla somʼakhakhiya liyihuqe ngethusi. <verse eid="EXO 27:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="EXO 27:7"/>Lihlome imijabo le emasongweni asemaceleni womabili e-alithare ukuze ibe yizibambo nxa selithwalwa. <verse eid="EXO 27:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="EXO 27:8"/>Beselithatha amapulanka lenze ngawo i-alithari libe ngumhome. Lenze njengalokhu owakutshengiswayo entabeni.”<verse eid="EXO 27:8"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Iguma Lethabanikeli</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="EXO 27:9"/>“Lilungise iguma lethabanikeli. Ubude becele lezansi bube zingalo ezilikhulu njalo libe lamakhetheni elembu eliphethwe kuhle, <verse eid="EXO 27:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="EXO 27:10"/>lensika ezingamatshumi amabili lezisekelo ezingamatshumi amabili konke kwenziwe ngethusi kanye lengwegwe zesiliva lamabhanti ensikeni. <verse eid="EXO 27:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="EXO 27:11"/>Icele lenyakatho lalo lizakuba yizingalo ezilikhulu ubude njalo libe lamakhetheni, libe lensika ezingamatshumi amabili lezisekelo ezingamatshumi amabili ethusi futhi kube lengwegwana lezibopho zesiliva ensikeni.<verse eid="EXO 27:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="EXO 27:12"/>Icele lentshonalanga yeguma lizakuba zingalo ezingamatshumi amahlanu ububanzi, lilamakhetheni, lensika ezilitshumi kanye lezisekelo ezilitshumi. <verse eid="EXO 27:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="EXO 27:13"/>Eceleni elisempumalanga, kusiya okuphuma khona ilanga, iguma lizakuba banzi okuzingalo ezingamatshumi amahlanu. <verse eid="EXO 27:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="EXO 27:14"/>Amakhetheni azingalo ezilitshumi lanhlanu ubude azakuba nganxanye kwesango, elezinsika ezintathu kanye lezisekelo ezintathu. <verse eid="EXO 27:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="EXO 27:15"/>Ngakwelinye icele lakho kuzakuba lamakhetheni azingalo ezilitshumi lanhlanu ubude kanye lezinsika ezintathu lezisekelo ezintathu.<verse eid="EXO 27:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="EXO 27:16"/>Esangweni leguma, lifake ikhetheni elizingalo ezingamatshumi amabili ubude, elelukwe laphethwa kuhle ngentambo eluhlaza, eyibubende kanye lebomvu, kube ngumsebenzi wombalazi ngokuthunga, kube lezinsika ezine lezisekelo ezine. <verse eid="EXO 27:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="EXO 27:17"/>Zonke izinsika ezihonqolozele iguma zibe lamabhanti lengwegwe zesiliva kanye lezisekelo zethusi. <verse eid="EXO 27:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="EXO 27:18"/>Ubude beguma buzakuba zingalo ezilikhulu lobubanzi obuzingalo ezingamatshumi amahlanu lamakhetheni elembu elelukwe kuhle libe lide okuzingalo ezinhlanu, lezisekelo zethusi. <verse eid="EXO 27:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="EXO 27:19"/>Zonke izinto ezizasetshenziswa emsebenzini wethabanikeli loba kuyini okwenziwayo kuhlanganisa lazozonke izikhonkwane zalo kanye lezeguma, kumele kube ngokwethusi.”<verse eid="EXO 27:19"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Amafutha Oluthi Lwesibane</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="EXO 27:20"/>“Laya abantu bako-Israyeli bakulethele amafutha acengekileyo, ahluzwe ema-oliveni, abe ngawokukhanyisa ukuze izibane zihlale zikhanyisa kokuphela. <verse eid="EXO 27:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="EXO 27:21"/>Ethenteni lokuhlangana, ngaphandle kwekhetheni eligudle umtshokotsho wobufakazi, u-Aroni lamadodana akhe bazagcina izibane phambi <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char> zibhebha kusukela ntambama kuze kuse. Lokhu kuzakuba yisimiso saphakade phakathi kwabako-Israyeli lakuzizukulwane ezizayo.”<verse eid="EXO 27:21"/></para>
  <chapter eid="EXO 27"/>
  <chapter number="28" style="c" sid="EXO 28"/>
  <para style="s1">Izembatho ZobuPhristi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="EXO 28:1"/>“Akulethwe kuwe phakathi kwabako-Israyeli umfowenu u-Aroni kanye lamadodana akhe uNadabi, u-Abhihu, u-Eliyazari lo-Ithamari, ubehlukanisele ukuba babe ngabaphristi bami. <verse eid="EXO 28:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="EXO 28:2"/>Wenzele u-Aroni umfowenu izembatho ezingcwele, ezizamenza abe lesithunzi njalo ahlonipheke. <verse eid="EXO 28:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="EXO 28:3"/>Atshele wonke amadoda azingcitshi lalenhlakanipho ngokuphathelane lalumsebenzi wokuthi benzele u-Aroni izembatho zokwahlukanisela umsebenzi wami wokuba ngumphristi. <verse eid="EXO 28:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="EXO 28:4"/>Yilezi izembatho abazazenza: isembatho sesifubeni, isembatho semahlombe, isigqoko, ibhatshi elelukiweyo, iqhiye kanye lebhanti. Kumele benzele umfowenu u-Aroni lamadodana akhe izembatho lezi ezingcwele ukuze babe ngabaphristi bami. <verse eid="EXO 28:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="EXO 28:5"/>Kabasebenzise intambo eziluhlaza, eziyibubende, ezibomvu kanye lelembu elicolekileyo.”<verse eid="EXO 28:5"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Isembatho Semahlombe</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="EXO 28:6"/>“Uzakwenza isembatho semahlombe ngelembu eliphethwe kuhle ngentambo eziligolide, eziluhlaza, eziyibubende kanye lezibomvu, kube ngumsebenzi womuntu oleminwe. <verse eid="EXO 28:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="EXO 28:7"/>Kumele sibe leziqa zemahlombe ezimbili zithungelwe emaceleni aso womabili ukuze sibotshwe. <verse eid="EXO 28:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="EXO 28:8"/>Kuzakuthi ibhanti laso lasekhalweni lelukwe ngobungcitshi lenziwe lifane laso, libe yinto yinye lesembatho semahlombe, lenziwe ngelembu eliphethwe kuhle ngentambo eligolide, eluhlaza, eyibubende kanye lebomvu.<verse eid="EXO 28:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="EXO 28:9"/>Thatha amatshe amabili ohlobo lwe-onikisi udwebele kuwo amabizo amadodana ka-Israyeli <verse eid="EXO 28:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="EXO 28:10"/>ngokulandelana kwawo, ayisithupha kwelinye ilitshe kuthi aseleyo uwadwebele kwelinye njalo. <verse eid="EXO 28:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="EXO 28:11"/>Dwebela amabizo amadodana ka-Israyeli ematsheni womabili njengombazi wamatshe aligugu edwebela uphawu. Ubusuwazingelezela ngeziceciso zegolide <verse eid="EXO 28:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="EXO 28:12"/>ubusuwathungela eziqeni zemahlombe kube ngamatshe esikhumbuzo samadodana ka-Israyeli. U-Aroni kumele athwale amabizo emahlombe akhe kube yisikhumbuzo phambi <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char>. <verse eid="EXO 28:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="EXO 28:13"/>Yenza iziceciso zegolide <verse eid="EXO 28:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="EXO 28:14"/>kanye lamaketane enziwe ngegolide elicolekileyo alukelwe ndawonye njengegoda uwabophele ezicecisweni zegolide.”<verse eid="EXO 28:14"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Isembatho Sesifubeni</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="EXO 28:15"/>“Uzakwenza isembatho sesifuba sokwahlulela, senziwe ngumuntu oleminwe. Usenze njengesembatho semahlombe: ngelembu eliphothwe kuhle ngentambo eligolide, eluhlaza, eyibubende kanye lebomvu. <verse eid="EXO 28:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="EXO 28:16"/>Kufanele silingane inxa zonke, isandla ubude lesandla ububanzi, sigoqwe saphindwa kabili. <verse eid="EXO 28:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="EXO 28:17"/>Ubusuthungela kuso imizila emine yamatshe aligugu. Emzileni wakuqala kuzakuba lerubhi, ithophazi kanye lebheriyeli, <verse eid="EXO 28:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="EXO 28:18"/>emzileni wesibili kube yi-emeralidi, isafaya, ledayimana, <verse eid="EXO 28:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="EXO 28:19"/>emzileni wesithathu ijasinti, i-agathi kanye le-amethisi, <verse eid="EXO 28:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="EXO 28:20"/>emzileni wesine ikhrisolathi, i-onikisi kanye lejaspa. Athungele ezicecisweni zegolide. <verse eid="EXO 28:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="EXO 28:21"/>Kumele kube lamatshe alitshumi lambili, lilinye limele ibizo lamadodana ka-Israyeli, linye ngalinye lilotshwe njengokudweba kombazi wamatshe, kungani luphawu, kulotshwe kulelo lalelo ibizo lezizwana zako-Israyeli ezilitshumi lambili.<verse eid="EXO 28:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="EXO 28:22"/>Isembatho sesifubeni selukelwe amaketane ngegolide elicolekileyo kube njengegoda. <verse eid="EXO 28:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="EXO 28:23"/>Yenza amasongo amabili ngegolide ubusuwabophela emagumbini amabili esembatho sesifubeni. <verse eid="EXO 28:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="EXO 28:24"/>Bophela amaketane amabili egolide emasongweni asemagumbini esembatho sesifubeni, <verse eid="EXO 28:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="EXO 28:25"/>kuthi ngapha acina khona abotshelwe ezicecisweni ezimbili, liwahlanganise eziqeni zemahlombe phambili kwesembatho semahlombe. <verse eid="EXO 28:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="EXO 28:26"/>Yenza amasongo amabili egolide uwabophele kwamanye amagumbi amabili esembatho sesifubeni ngaphakathi komphetho phansi kwesembatho semahlombe. <verse eid="EXO 28:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="EXO 28:27"/>Yenza amanye amasongo egolide amabili ubusuwabophela ngaphansi kweziqa zemahlombe phambi kwesembatho semahlombe, eduze komphetho ngaphezudlwana kwebhanti lasekhalweni lwesembatho semahlombe. <verse eid="EXO 28:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="EXO 28:28"/>Amasongo esembatho sesifubeni kumele abotshaniswe lamasongo esembatho semahlombe ngentambo eluhlaza, kusihlanganisa lebhanti lasokhalweni, ukwenzela ukuthi isembatho sesifubeni singatsheleli sehlukane lesembatho semahlombe.<verse eid="EXO 28:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="EXO 28:29"/>Kuzakuthi lapho u-Aroni engena Endaweni Engcwele, agqize phezu kwenhliziyo yakhe isembatho sesifubeni sokwahlulela esilamabizo amadodana ka-Israyeli kube yisikhumbuzo esiqhubekayo phambi <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char>. <verse eid="EXO 28:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="EXO 28:30"/>Faka njalo i-Urimi kanye leThumimi esambathweni sesifubeni, ukuze ziqondane laphezu kwenhliziyo ka-Aroni loba kunini engena endaweni <char style="nd">kaThixo</char>. Ngalokho u-Aroni uzabe ethwele amandla okunquma izinqumo kwabako-Israyeli phezu kwenhliziyo yakhe phambi <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char>.”<verse eid="EXO 28:30"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ezinye Izembatho ZabaPhristi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="EXO 28:31"/>“Yenza isigqoko sesembatho semahlombe ngelembu eliluhlaza kuphela, <verse eid="EXO 28:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="EXO 28:32"/>kube lesikhala sokungenisa ikhanda phakathi laphakathi. Kuzakuba lomphetho onjengebheqe othungwe walandelisela isikhala lesi ukuze isembatho singadabuki. <verse eid="EXO 28:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="EXO 28:33"/>Wenze emphethweni wesembatho amaphomegranathi ngentambo eluhlaza, eyibubende kanye lebomvu, uwugabanise lamabhera egolide. <verse eid="EXO 28:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="EXO 28:34"/>Amabhera egolide kumele agabane lamaphomegranathi emphethweni wesembatho. <verse eid="EXO 28:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="EXO 28:35"/>U-Aroni kufanele asembathe nxa esenza umsebenzi wokukhonza. Umsindo wamabhera uyabe uzwakala lapho engena eNdaweni eNgcwele phambi <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char> lalapho ephuma, ukuze angafi.<verse eid="EXO 28:35"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="EXO 28:36"/>Yenza icence legolide elicolekileyo udwebe, uloba kulo njengombazi wamatshe udwebela uphawu oluthi:</para>
  <para style="pc" vid="EXO 28:36">Ubungcwele kabube <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>.<verse eid="EXO 28:36"/></para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="37" style="v" sid="EXO 28:37"/>Ulibophele eqhiyeni ngentambo eluhlaza libe phambi kweqhiye. <verse eid="EXO 28:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="EXO 28:38"/>Lizakuba sebunzini lika-Aroni ukuze athwale amacala aqondene lezipho ezingcwele ezinikelwa ngabako-Israyeli, kungakhathalekile ukuthi yisipho bani. Lizakuba sebunzini lika-Aroni kokuphela ukuze abako-Israyeli bemukeleke <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>.<verse eid="EXO 28:38"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="EXO 28:39"/>Thunga ibhatshi ngelembu elicolekileyo kanye leqhiye yelembu elicolekileyo, elihle. Ibhanti lokhalo kumele lenziwe ngumbalazi ngokuthunga. <verse eid="EXO 28:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="EXO 28:40"/>Wenzele amadodana ka-Aroni amabhatshi, lamabhanti kanye lamaqhiye ukuze abe lesithunzi, ahlonipheke. <verse eid="EXO 28:40"/><verse number="41" style="v" sid="EXO 28:41"/>Emva kokugqokisa u-Aroni umfowenu kanye lamadodana akhe lezizembatho, bagcobe ubahlukanisele ukuba ngabaphristi bami.<verse eid="EXO 28:41"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="42" style="v" sid="EXO 28:42"/>Thunga izembatho zangaphansi ngelembu, zisukele ekhalweni kusiya emathangazini, zibe yizembatho zomzimba. <verse eid="EXO 28:42"/><verse number="43" style="v" sid="EXO 28:43"/>U-Aroni kanye lamadodana akhe bazazigqoka izikhathi zonke nxa bengena ethenteni lokuhlangana lanxa besondela e-alithareni ukwenza umsebenzi wokukhonza eNdaweni eNgcwele, ukuze bangabi lecala bafe.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="EXO 28:43">Lokhu kuzakuba yisimiso esingapheliyo ku-Aroni lakuzizukulwane zakhe.”<verse eid="EXO 28:43"/></para>
  <chapter eid="EXO 28"/>
  <chapter number="29" style="c" sid="EXO 29"/>
  <para style="s1">Ukugcotshwa KwabaPhristi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="EXO 29:1"/>“Lokhu yikho ozakwenza nxa ubagcoba ukuze bangisebenzele njengabaphristi: Thatha inkunzi esesencane lenqama ezimbili ezingelasici. <verse eid="EXO 29:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="EXO 29:2"/>Yenza izinkwa ezingelamvubelo ngefulawa ecolekileyo, izinkwa ezinkulu ezingelamvubelo, ezivutshwe ngamafutha e-oliva lezinkwa ezincane ezingelamvubelo, zigcotshwe ngamafutha e-oliva. <verse eid="EXO 29:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="EXO 29:3"/>Uzifake esitsheni ubusuziletha ndawonye lenkunzi kanye lenqama ezimbili. <verse eid="EXO 29:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="EXO 29:4"/>Emva kwalokho ulethe u-Aroni lamadodana akhe esangweni lethente lokuhlangana ubagezise ngamanzi. <verse eid="EXO 29:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="EXO 29:5"/>Thatha izembatho ugqokise u-Aroni ibhatshi, lesembatho samahlombe, isembatho samahlombe sona ngokwaso kanye lesigqoko sesifuba, umbophele isembatho samahlombe ngebhanti lokhalo elelukwe ngobungcwethi obukhulu. <verse eid="EXO 29:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="EXO 29:6"/>Mthwalise iqhiye yokuthandela ekhanda lakhe, unamathisele umqhele wamakhosi ongcwele eqhiyeni. <verse eid="EXO 29:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="EXO 29:7"/>Thatha amafutha okugcobela isikhundla umgcobe ngokuwathela phezu kwekhanda lakhe. <verse eid="EXO 29:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="EXO 29:8"/>Letha amadodana akhe uwagqokise amabhatshi <verse eid="EXO 29:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="EXO 29:9"/>ubabophe ngamabhanti emakhanda, u-Aroni lamadodana akhe, ube usubathwalisa izingowane. Ubuphristi ngobabo ngesimiso esingapheliyo.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="EXO 29:9">Ngale indlela uzagcoba u-Aroni lamadodana akhe.<verse eid="EXO 29:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="EXO 29:10"/>Letha inkunzi phambi kwethente lokuhlangana, u-Aroni lamadodana akhe babeke izandla zabo phezu kwekhanda layo, <verse eid="EXO 29:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="EXO 29:11"/>uyihlabe phambi <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char> esangweni lethente lokuhlangana. <verse eid="EXO 29:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="EXO 29:12"/>Uthathe igazi lenkunzi ulininde empondweni ze-alithare ngomunwe wakho, uthele igazi eliseleyo phansi e-alithareni. <verse eid="EXO 29:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="EXO 29:13"/>Emva kwalokho uthathe lonke idanga eligoqela ezangaphakathi, amahwahwa aphezu kwesibindi, izinso zonke lamahwahwa akuzo, ukutshise konke lokhu e-alithareni. <verse eid="EXO 29:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="EXO 29:14"/>Kodwa-ke inyama yenkunzi, isikhumba sayo lamathumbu ayo, ukutshisele ngaphandle kwesihonqo; kungumnikelo wesono.<verse eid="EXO 29:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="EXO 29:15"/>Thatha enye yenqama, u-Aroni lamadodana akhe babeke izandla zabo phezu kwekhanda layo, <verse eid="EXO 29:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="EXO 29:16"/>uyihlabe, uthathe igazi layo ulichele emaceleni wonke e-alithare. <verse eid="EXO 29:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="EXO 29:17"/>Emva kwalokho uhlahlele inqama ibe yiziqa ugezise ezangaphakathi lemilenze ukufake ndawonye lenhloko kanye lezinye iziqa, <verse eid="EXO 29:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="EXO 29:18"/>ubusutshisa inqama yonke e-alithareni. Lokhu kungumnikelo wokutshiswa <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>, iphunga elimnandi, umnikelo onikelwa <char style="nd">kuThixo</char> ngomlilo.<verse eid="EXO 29:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="EXO 29:19"/>Thatha enye inqama, u-Aroni lamadodana akhe babeke izandla zabo phezu kwekhanda layo. <verse eid="EXO 29:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="EXO 29:20"/>Uyihlabe, uthathe igazi layo ulininde esiqwini sendlebe yakwesokunene sika-Aroni lakwezamadodana akhe, lasezithupheni zabo zezandla zabo zokunene, lasemazwaneni amakhulu ezinyawo zabo zesandla sokunene. Emva kwalokho uchele igazi emaceleni wonke e-alithare. <verse eid="EXO 29:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="EXO 29:21"/>Thatha igazi elise-alithareni lamafutha okugcoba uchele u-Aroni lezembatho zakhe kanye lamadodana akhe lezembatho zawo. Lapho-ke yena lamadodana akhe lezivunulo zabo kuzabe sekungcwelisiwe.<verse eid="EXO 29:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="EXO 29:22"/>Thatha amahwahwa kule inqama, lomsila ononileyo, ledanga eligoqela ezangaphakathi, lamahwahwa aphezu kwesibindi, lezinso zombili lamahwahwa akuzo kanye lomlenze wesandla sokunene. (Le yinqama yokugcotshwa komphristi.) <verse eid="EXO 29:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="EXO 29:23"/>Esitsheni esilesinkwa esingelamvubelo esiphambi <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char>, thatha isinkwa esisodwa, isinkwa esisodwa esikhulu esixutshaniswe lamafutha e-oliva kanye lesinkwanyana. <verse eid="EXO 29:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="EXO 29:24"/>Konke lokhu kufake ezandleni zika-Aroni lezamadodana akhe, bakuzunguze phambi <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char> kube ngumnikelo wokuzunguzwa. <verse eid="EXO 29:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="EXO 29:25"/>Emva kwalokho kuthathe ezandleni zabo ukutshise e-alithareni ndawonye lomnikelo wokutshiswa ukuze kube liphunga elimnandi <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>, umhlatshelo wokudla onikelwa <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>. <verse eid="EXO 29:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="EXO 29:26"/>Emva kwalokho thatha isifuba senqama yokugcotshwa kuka-Aroni uzunguze phambi <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char> njengomnikelo wokuzunguzwa njalo sizakuba yisabelo sakho.<verse eid="EXO 29:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="EXO 29:27"/>Zenze zibengcwele lezozitho zenqama yokugcotshwa komphristi ezingezika-Aroni lamadodana akhe, isifuba esizunguziweyo lomlenze onikelweyo. <verse eid="EXO 29:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="EXO 29:28"/>Lokhu kuzaqhubeka kokuphela kuyisabelo sika-Aroni lamadodana akhe esivela kwabako-Israyeli. Kungumnikelo abako-Israyeli abawenzayo <char style="nd">kuThixo</char> uvela eminikelweni yabo yokuhlanganyela.<verse eid="EXO 29:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="EXO 29:29"/>Izembatho zika-Aroni ezingcwele zizakuba ngezezizukulwana zakhe ukuze bagcotshwe babekwe ubuphristi begqoke zona. <verse eid="EXO 29:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="EXO 29:30"/>Indodana yakhe ezakuba ngumphristi esikhundleni sakhe izazigqoka insuku eziyisikhombisa lapho isiza ethenteni lokuhlangana ukuzakhonza eNdaweni eNgcwele.<verse eid="EXO 29:30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="EXO 29:31"/>Thatha inqama yokugcotshwa komphristi uyiphekele endaweni engcwele. <verse eid="EXO 29:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="EXO 29:32"/>Ethenteni lokuhlangana, u-Aroni lamadodana akhe bazakudla inyama yenqama lesinkwa esisesitsheni. <verse eid="EXO 29:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="EXO 29:33"/>Kumele badle leyomnikelo okwenziwa ngayo inhlawulo yokubekwa lokugcotshwa kwabo. Kodwa omunye umuntu nje akayikukudla lokhu ngoba kungcwele. <verse eid="EXO 29:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="EXO 29:34"/>Njalo nxa eyinye yenyama yenqama yokugcotshwa komphristi kumbe isinkwa kusele kuze kube sekuseni, kutshise ngomlilo. Akumelanga kudliwe ngoba kungcwele.<verse eid="EXO 29:34"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="EXO 29:35"/>Menzele-ke u-Aroni lamadodana akhe konke engikulaye khona, ukugcotshwa kwabo kuthathe insuku eziyisikhombisa. <verse eid="EXO 29:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="EXO 29:36"/>Nikela inkunzi eyodwa usuku ngosuku njengomnikelo wesono wokwenza inhlawulo. Yenza i-alithari libengcwele ngokulenzela inhlawulo, uligcobe ukuba ulingcwelise. <verse eid="EXO 29:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="EXO 29:37"/>Yenza inhlawulelo ye-alithare okwensuku eziyisikhombisa ulingcwelise. Lapho-ke i-alithari lizakuba ngcwele kakhulu kuthi konke okulithintayo kube ngcwele.<verse eid="EXO 29:37"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="38" style="v" sid="EXO 29:38"/>Lokhu yikho ozakunikela e-alithareni usuku lunye ngalunye: amazinyane ezimvu amabili alomnyaka owodwa ezelwe. <verse eid="EXO 29:38"/><verse number="39" style="v" sid="EXO 29:39"/>Nikela elilodwa ekuseni, elinye unikele ngalo njalo kusihlwa. <verse eid="EXO 29:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="EXO 29:40"/>Kanye lezinyane lakuqala nikela okwetshumi kwehefa yefulawa ecolekileyo ehlanganiswe lokwesine kwehini yamafutha e-oliva ahluziweyo, lokwesine kwehini yewayini ukuba kube ngumnikelo onathwayo. <verse eid="EXO 29:40"/><verse number="41" style="v" sid="EXO 29:41"/>Elinye izinyane linikele kusihlwa ngomnikelo ofanayo wamabele kanye lomnikelo wokunathwayo njengowekuseni ukuba kube liphunga elimnandi, umnikelo wokutshiswa onikelwa <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>.<verse eid="EXO 29:41"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="42" style="v" sid="EXO 29:42"/>Kuzizukulwane ezizayo umnikelo wokutshiswa lo uzakwenziwa njalonjalo esangweni lethente lokuhlangana phambi <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char>, lapho engizahlangana lawe khona ngikhulume lawe. <verse eid="EXO 29:42"/><verse number="43" style="v" sid="EXO 29:43"/>Lapho futhi yikho engizahlangana khona labako-Israyeli, indawo leyo ingcweliswe yinkazimulo yami.<verse eid="EXO 29:43"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="44" style="v" sid="EXO 29:44"/>Ngokunjalo ngizakwenza ithente lokuhlangana kanye le-alithari kube ngcwele ukuba bangisebenzele bengabaphristi. <verse eid="EXO 29:44"/><verse number="45" style="v" sid="EXO 29:45"/>Lapho-ke ngizahlala phakathi kwabantu bako-Israyeli ngibe nguNkulunkulu wabo. <verse eid="EXO 29:45"/><verse number="46" style="v" sid="EXO 29:46"/>Bazakwazi ukuthi mina <char style="nd">nginguThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wabo, owabakhupha eGibhithe ukuze ngihlale phakathi kwabo. Mina <char style="nd">nginguThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wabo.”<verse eid="EXO 29:46"/></para>
  <chapter eid="EXO 29"/>
  <chapter number="30" style="c" sid="EXO 30"/>
  <para style="s1">I-Alithari Lokutshisela Impepha</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="EXO 30:1"/>“Yenza i-alithari lokutshisela impepha ngesihlahla somʼakhakhiya. <verse eid="EXO 30:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="EXO 30:2"/>Amacele womane kumele alingane, kube yingalo ubude lengalo ububanzi, kuthi ukudepha kube zingalo ezimbili, impondo zalo zibe yinto yinye lalo. <verse eid="EXO 30:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="EXO 30:3"/>Huqa phezulu lamacele wonke, lempondo zalo ngegolide elicolekileyo ubumbele umqolo wegolide inxa zonke. <verse eid="EXO 30:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="EXO 30:4"/>Yenza amasongo egolide amabili e-alithare abe ngaphansi komqolo emaceleni amabili ehlukeneyo ukuba abambe imijabo yokulithwala. <verse eid="EXO 30:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="EXO 30:5"/>Imijabo yenze ngesihlahla somʼakhakhiya uyihuqe ngegolide. <verse eid="EXO 30:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="EXO 30:6"/>Beka i-alithari phambi kwekhetheni elisithe umtshokotsho wobufakazi, nganeno kwesihlalo somusa esiphezu kwezibhebhedu zesivumelwano somthetho lapho engizahlangana lawe khona.<verse eid="EXO 30:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="EXO 30:7"/>U-Aroni kumele atshise impepha enuka mnandi e-alithareni nsuku zonke ekuseni elungisa izibane. <verse eid="EXO 30:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="EXO 30:8"/>Kumele impepha ayitshise futhi kusihlwa lapho eselumathisa izibane ukuze impepha itshe kokuphela phambi <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char> kuze kube kuzizukulwane ezizayo. <verse eid="EXO 30:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="EXO 30:9"/>Linganikeli kuleli-alithare olunye uhlobo lwempepha kumbe umnikelo wokutshiswa loba umnikelo wamabele, njalo lingatheli umnikelo wokunathwa phezu kwalo. <verse eid="EXO 30:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="EXO 30:10"/>Kanye ngomnyaka u-Aroni uzakwenza inhlawulelo empondweni zalo. Inhlawulo yeminyaka yonke le kumele yenziwe ngegazi lomnikelo wokuhlawulela izono zezizukulwane ezizayo. Ingcwele kakhulu <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>.”<verse eid="EXO 30:10"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Imali Yenhlawulo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="EXO 30:11"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wasesithi kuMosi, <verse eid="EXO 30:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="EXO 30:12"/>“Lapho usubala abantu bako-Israyeli omunye lomunye kumele anike <char style="nd">uThixo</char> inhlawulo yokuphila kwakhe. Ngalokho akuyikuba lesifo esizabehlela lapho ubabala. <verse eid="EXO 30:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="EXO 30:13"/>Akuthi lowo lalowo odlulela ngakulabo asebebaliwe anike ingxenye yeshekeli, ngokweshekeli lendawo engcwele, okuyisisindo esingamagera angamatshumi amabili. Ingxenye yeshekeli le ingumnikelo <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>. <verse eid="EXO 30:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="EXO 30:14"/>Wonke umuntu obaliweyo, kusukela koleminyaka engamatshumi amabili kusiya phezulu, uzanikela umnikelo <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>. <verse eid="EXO 30:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="EXO 30:15"/>Abanothileyo akumelanga banikele ngokwedlula ingxenye yeshekeli, labayanga kabanganikeli ngokungaphansi lapho selinikela <char style="nd">kuThixo</char> ukuba lenze inhlawulelo yokuphila kwenu. <verse eid="EXO 30:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="EXO 30:16"/>Wamukele imali yenhlawulo kwabako-Israyeli uyisebenzise enkonzweni yethente lokuhlangana. Izakuba yisikhumbuzo kwabako-Israyeli phambi <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char> ukwenzela inhlawulelo yokuphila kwenu.”<verse eid="EXO 30:16"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Inkonxa Yokugezela</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="EXO 30:17"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wasesithi kuMosi, <verse eid="EXO 30:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="EXO 30:18"/>“Yenza inkonxa yethusi ibe lensika yethusi, izakuba ngeyokugezela. Uyibeke phakathi laphakathi kwethente lokuhlangana le-alithari, uthele amanzi phakathi kwayo. <verse eid="EXO 30:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="EXO 30:19"/>U-Aroni lamadodana akhe bazageza izandla lezinyawo zabo ngamanzi akuyo. <verse eid="EXO 30:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="EXO 30:20"/>Nxa bengena ethenteni lokuhlangana bazageza ngamanzi ukuze bangafi. Phezu kwalokho, lapho besondela e-alithareni ukuba bakhonze ngokwethula umnikelo wokutshiswa onikelwa <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>, <verse eid="EXO 30:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="EXO 30:21"/>bazageza izandla zabo lezinyawo ukuze bangafi. Lokhu kuzakuba yisimiso esingapheliyo ku-Aroni lenzalo yakhe lakuzizukulwane ezizayo.”<verse eid="EXO 30:21"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Amafutha Okugcoba Abakhethiweyo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="EXO 30:22"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wasesithi kuMosi, <verse eid="EXO 30:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="EXO 30:23"/>“Thatha lezinhlobo zamakha amahle: Amashekeli angamakhulu amahlanu (500) emure elingamanzi, isinamoni enuka mnandi eyingxenye yalokho (okuyikuthi amakhulu amabili lamatshumi amahlanu (250) amashekeli), amashekeli angamakhulu amabili lamatshumi amahlanu (250) ekhalamu elilephunga elimnandi, <verse eid="EXO 30:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="EXO 30:24"/>amashekeli angamakhulu amahlanu (500) ekhasiya, konke kumayelana lamashekeli endawo engcwele, kanye lehini lamafutha ama-oliva. <verse eid="EXO 30:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="EXO 30:25"/>Lokhu kwenze kube ngamafutha angcwele okugcoba abakhethiweyo alungiswe ngumenzi wamakha, azakuba ngamafutha angcwele okugcoba abakhethiweyo. <verse eid="EXO 30:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="EXO 30:26"/>Ngawo-ke uzagcoba ithente lokuhlangana, umtshokotsho wobufakazi, <verse eid="EXO 30:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="EXO 30:27"/>itafula kanye lezitsha zawo zonke, uluthi lwesibane lezitsha zawo, i-alithari lempepha, <verse eid="EXO 30:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="EXO 30:28"/>i-alithari lomnikelo wokutshiswa lezitsha zawo lomganu wokugezela kanye lezinyawo zawo. <verse eid="EXO 30:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="EXO 30:29"/>Uzakungcwelisa konke ukuba kube ngcwele kakhulu, njalo loba yini ekuthintayo izakuba ngcwele.<verse eid="EXO 30:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="EXO 30:30"/>Mgcobe u-Aroni lamadodana akhe ubehlukanisele ukuba bangisebenzele bengabaphristi. <verse eid="EXO 30:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="EXO 30:31"/>Batshele abako-Israyeli uthi, ‘Lokhu kuzakuba ngamafutha ami angcwele okugcoba abakhethiweyo lakuzizukulwane zenu ezizayo. <verse eid="EXO 30:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="EXO 30:32"/>Lingawatheli emizimbeni yabantu, njalo lingenzi amanye amafutha ngale indlela yokuwenza. Ingcwele, izakuba ngcwele lakini. <verse eid="EXO 30:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="EXO 30:33"/>Lowo ozakwenza amakha afana lawo kumbe agcobe ngawo umuntu ongasuye mphristi, uzasuswa ebantwini bakibo.’ ”<verse eid="EXO 30:33"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Impepha</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="EXO 30:34"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wabuye wathi kuMosi, “Thatha amakha anuka mnandi, isitakete, i-onika legalibhanumi kanye lenhlaka enhle, konke kungesilinganiso esifanayo, <verse eid="EXO 30:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="EXO 30:35"/>wenze ingxube yempepha elephunga elimnandi njengomxubi wamakha, ifakwe itswayi ibenhle njalo ibe ngcwele. <verse eid="EXO 30:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="EXO 30:36"/>Chola enye yayo ibe yimpuphu uyifake phambi komtshokotsho wobufakazi phakathi kwethente lokuhlangana lapho engizahlangana lawe khona. Izakuba ngcwele kakhulu kini. <verse eid="EXO 30:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="EXO 30:37"/>Lingazenzeli eyenu impepha ngale indlela, iboneni njengento engcwele <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>. <verse eid="EXO 30:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="EXO 30:38"/>Lowo ozakwenza enye efana layo ukuba akholise ukunukelela kwayo kamnandi, kumele asuswe ebantwini bakibo.”<verse eid="EXO 30:38"/></para>
  <chapter eid="EXO 30"/>
  <chapter number="31" style="c" sid="EXO 31"/>
  <para style="s1">Ukukhethwa KukaBhezaleli Lo-Oholiyabhi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="EXO 31:1"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wathi kuMosi, <verse eid="EXO 31:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="EXO 31:2"/>“Khangela, sengikhethe uBhezaleli indodana ka-Uri oyindodana kaHuri owesizwe sikaJuda <verse eid="EXO 31:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="EXO 31:3"/>ngamgcwalisa ngomoya kaNkulunkulu, ukuhlakanipha, ukuqedisisa lolwazi ekwenzeni yonke imisebenzi yobungcitshi <verse eid="EXO 31:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="EXO 31:4"/>ukuze adwebe imisebenzi yobungcitshi ngesimo sezinto ezenziwa ngegolide, isiliva kanye lethusi, <verse eid="EXO 31:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="EXO 31:5"/>abaze amatshe awabeke kuhle, abaze izigodo kanye lokwenza yonke imisebenzi yomuntu oleminwe lobungcwethi. <verse eid="EXO 31:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="EXO 31:6"/>Phezu kwalokho, ngikhethe lo-Oholiyabhi indodana ka-Ahisamakhi, owesizwe sikaDani ukuba amncedise.</para>
  <para style="b" vid="EXO 31:6"/>
  <para style="li4" vid="EXO 31:6">Nginike ulwazi kuzozonke izingcitshi ukuba zenze konke engikulaye ukuba kwenziwe:<verse eid="EXO 31:6"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="EXO 31:7"/>ithente lokuhlangana,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="EXO 31:7">umtshokotsho wobufakazi, isihlalo somusa esikuwo,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="EXO 31:7">lakho konke okunye okokuhlobisa ithente:<verse eid="EXO 31:7"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="EXO 31:8"/>itafula lezitsha zalo,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="EXO 31:8">uluthi lwesibane lwegolide elicolekileyo lezitsha zalo zonke,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="EXO 31:8">i-alithari lempepha,<verse eid="EXO 31:8"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="EXO 31:9"/>i-alithari lomnikelo wokutshiswa kanye lezitsha zalo zonke,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="EXO 31:9">lomkolo kanye lezinyawo zawo<verse eid="EXO 31:9"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="EXO 31:10"/>lezembatho ezelukiweyo,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="EXO 31:10">lezembatho ezingcwele zika-Aroni umphristi</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="EXO 31:10">kanye lezembatho zamadodana akhe ezomsebenzi wabo wobuphristi,<verse eid="EXO 31:10"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="EXO 31:11"/>lamafutha okugcobela isikhundla, lempepha enuka mnandi eyeNdawo eNgcwele.</para>
  <para style="b" vid="EXO 31:11"/>
  <para style="li4" vid="EXO 31:11">Kumele bakwenze njengoba ngikulayile.”<verse eid="EXO 31:11"/></para>
  <para style="s1">ISabatha</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="EXO 31:12"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wasesithi kuMosi, <verse eid="EXO 31:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="EXO 31:13"/>“Batshele abako-Israyeli uthi, ‘Kumele ligcine amaSabatha ami. Lokhu kuzakuba luphawu phakathi kwami lani kuzizukulwane zenu ezizayo, ukuze lazi ukuthi mina <char style="nd">nginguThixo</char> olenza libengcwele.<verse eid="EXO 31:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="EXO 31:14"/>Gcinani iSabatha ngoba lingcwele kini. Lowo olonayo kumele abulawe, lalowo osebenzayo ngalolosuku uzasuswa ebantwini bakibo. <verse eid="EXO 31:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="EXO 31:15"/>Umsebenzi kawenziwe okwensuku eziyisithupha, kodwa usuku lwesikhombisa luliSabatha lokuphumula, lungcwele <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>. Lowo osebenzayo ngosuku lweSabatha kumele abulawe. <verse eid="EXO 31:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="EXO 31:16"/>Abako-Israyeli kumele bagcine iSabatha, baligcine kuzizukulwane zabo ezizayo njengesivumelwano esingapheliyo. <verse eid="EXO 31:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="EXO 31:17"/>Lizakuba luphawu phakathi kwami labako-Israyeli nini lanini. Ngoba ngezinsuku eziyisithupha <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wenza amazulu lomhlaba, kwathi ngosuku lwesikhombisa waphumula.’ ”<verse eid="EXO 31:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="EXO 31:18"/>Kwathi lapho <char style="nd">uThixo</char> eseqedile ukukhuluma loMosi entabeni yaseSinayi wamnika izibhebhedu ezimbili zamatshe obufakazi, izibhebhedu zamatshe alotshwe ngomunwe kaNkulunkulu.<verse eid="EXO 31:18"/></para>
  <chapter eid="EXO 31"/>
  <chapter number="32" style="c" sid="EXO 32"/>
  <para style="s1">Ithole Legolide</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="EXO 32:1"/>Kwathi lapho abantu bebona uMosi esephuzile ukwehla entabeni, babuthana ku-Aroni bathi kuye, “Lalela, senzele onkulunkulu abazahamba phambi kwethu, ngoba umuntu lo, uMosi owasikhupha elizweni laseGibhithe, asikwazi osekwenzakale kuye.”<verse eid="EXO 32:1"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="EXO 32:2"/>U-Aroni wabaphendula wathi, “Khuphani amacici egolide asendlebeni zamakhosikazi enu, amadodana enu lamadodakazi enu, liwalethe kimi.” <verse eid="EXO 32:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="EXO 32:3"/>Ngakho abantu bonke bawakhupha amacici abo bawasa ku-Aroni. <verse eid="EXO 32:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="EXO 32:4"/>Wathatha lokho abamnikeza khona wakwenza kwaba yisithombe esibunjwe ngesimo sethole esebenzisa insimbi yokukhanda. Basebesithi, “Laba yibo onkulunkulu benu, Oh Israyeli, abalikhupha elizweni laseGibhithe.”<verse eid="EXO 32:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="EXO 32:5"/>Kwathi u-Aroni ebona lokhu wakha i-alithari phambi kwethole wamemezela wathi, “Kusasa kuzakuba lomkhosi <char style="nd">kaThixo</char>.” <verse eid="EXO 32:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="EXO 32:6"/>Ngakho ngosuku olwalandelayo abantu bavuka ekuseni kakhulu banikela umnikelo wokutshiswa, baletha lomnikelo wobudlelwano. Emva kwalokho bahlala phansi badla, banatha; basukuma bagida.<verse eid="EXO 32:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="EXO 32:7"/>Lapho-ke <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wathi kuMosi, “Yehla uye phansi ngoba abantu bakho owabakhupha elizweni laseGibhithe sebegcwele ububi. <verse eid="EXO 32:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="EXO 32:8"/>Baphangisile badela konke engabalaya khona bazenzela isithombe esibunjwe safana lethole. Basikhothamele banikela iminikelo kiso bathi, ‘Laba yibo onkulunkulu benu, bako-Israyeli, abalikhupha eGibhithe.’ ”<verse eid="EXO 32:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="EXO 32:9"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wasebuya wathi kuMosi, “Sengibabonile abantu laba; ngabantu abantamo zilukhuni. <verse eid="EXO 32:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="EXO 32:10"/>Khathesi-ke ngiyekela ngingedwa ukuze ulaka lwami luvuthe phezu kwabo, ngibatshabalalise. Besengizakwenza isizwe esikhulu.”<verse eid="EXO 32:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="EXO 32:11"/>Kodwa uMosi wacela umusa <char style="nd">kuThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wakhe, wathi, “Awu <char style="nd">Thixo</char>, kungani ulaka lwakho kumele luvuthele abantu bakho owabakhupha eGibhithe ngamandla amakhulu langesandla esiqinileyo na? <verse eid="EXO 32:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="EXO 32:12"/>Kungani amaGibhithe kumele athi, ‘Wabakhupha elizweni ngenxa yenhloso embi ukuba ababulalele ezintabeni, ababhubhise baphele ebusweni bomhlaba’? Phenduka olakeni lwakho olwesabekayo, uthambise umoya wakho, ungaletheli abantu bakho ukubhujiswa. <verse eid="EXO 32:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="EXO 32:13"/>Khumbula izinceku zakho u-Abhrahama, u-Isaka lo-Israyeli owafunga kubo wena ngokwakho wathi, ‘Ngizakwandisa inzalo yenu ibe ngangezinkanyezi zasemkhathini, ngiyinike lonke ilizwe engalithembisa lona ukuba libe yilifa layo kuze kube nini lanini.’ ” <verse eid="EXO 32:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="EXO 32:14"/>Lapho-ke <char style="nd">uThixo</char> waguquka ebubini ayesemise ukubehlisela ebantwini bakhe.<verse eid="EXO 32:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="EXO 32:15"/>UMosi waphenduka wehla entabeni ephethe izibhebhedu ezimbili zamatshe obufakazi ezandleni zakhe. Zazilotshwe inxa zombili, phambili langemuva. <verse eid="EXO 32:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="EXO 32:16"/>Izibhebhedu zamatshe zazingumsebenzi kaNkulunkulu; umbhalo ungumbhalo kaNkulunkulu owawulotshwe ezibhebhedwini zamatshe.<verse eid="EXO 32:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="EXO 32:17"/>Kwathi lapho uJoshuwa esizwa umsindo wabantu beklabalala, wathi kuMosi, “Kulokuhlokoma kwempi ezihonqweni.”<verse eid="EXO 32:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="EXO 32:18"/>UMosi waphendula wathi:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="EXO 32:18">“Akusiyo nhlokomo yokunqoba,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="EXO 32:18">akusiyo nhlokomo yokunqotshwa;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="EXO 32:18">yinhlokomo yokuhlabela mina engiyizwayo.”<verse eid="EXO 32:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="EXO 32:19"/>Kwathi uMosi esebanga ezihonqweni ebona ithole kanye lokugida okwakusenziwa, ulaka lwakhe lwavutha, walahla izibhebhedu ezazisezandleni zakhe, zahlephuka zaba yizicucu ewatheni lwentaba. <verse eid="EXO 32:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="EXO 32:20"/>Wathatha ithole abebelenzile walitshisa emlilweni; walichola laba yimpuphu, wayiphosela emanzini, wathi bawanathe abako-Israyeli.<verse eid="EXO 32:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="EXO 32:21"/>Wasesithi ku-Aroni, “Abantu laba benzeni kuwe uze ubakhokhelele esonweni esikhulu kangaka na?”<verse eid="EXO 32:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="EXO 32:22"/>U-Aroni waphendula wathi, “Ungathukutheli nkosi yami. Uyakwazi ukuthi abantu laba bathanda ububi. <verse eid="EXO 32:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="EXO 32:23"/>Bathe kimi, ‘Senzele onkulunkulu abazahamba phambi kwethu. Umuntu lo, uMosi owasikhupha elizweni laseGibhithe, asikwazi osokwenzakale kuye.’ <verse eid="EXO 32:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="EXO 32:24"/>Ngakho mina ngathi kubo, ‘Loba ngubani olomceciso wegolide kawukhuphe.’ Basebengipha-ke igolide ngaliphosa emlilweni, kwasekuphuma ithole leli.”<verse eid="EXO 32:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="EXO 32:25"/>UMosi wabona ukuthi abantu babengasabambeki kanye lokuthi u-Aroni wayesebaxhwalisile baze baba yinhlekisa ezitheni zabo. <verse eid="EXO 32:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="EXO 32:26"/>Ngakho wema esangweni lezihonqo wathi, “Wonke <char style="nd">ongokaThixo</char>, keze kimi.” Wonke amadodana kaLevi ayabuthana kuye.<verse eid="EXO 32:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="EXO 32:27"/>Wasesithi kuwo, “Lokhu yikho okutshiwo <char style="nd">nguThixo</char>, uNkulunkulu ka-Israyeli, ukuthi, ‘Indoda ngayinye kayibophele inkemba yayo ngebhanti eceleni kwayo, lihambahambe phakathi kwezihonqo lisuka kwelinye icele lazo lisiya kwelinye, indoda ngayinye ibulale umfowabo, umzalwane lomakhelwane wayo.’ ” <verse eid="EXO 32:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="EXO 32:28"/>Amadodana kaLevi enza njengokulaywa kwawo nguMosi. Ngakho ngalolosuku kwafa abantu ababengaba zinkulungwane ezintathu. <verse eid="EXO 32:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="EXO 32:29"/>UMosi wasesithi kubo, “Lamuhla lina selahlukaniselwe <char style="nd">uThixo</char> ngoba limelane lamadodana enu labafowenu, ngalokho uselibusisile lamhla.”<verse eid="EXO 32:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="EXO 32:30"/>Ngelanga elalandelayo uMosi wathi ebantwini, “Lenze isono esikhulu kakhulu. Kodwa khathesi ngizaqansa ngiye phezulu <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>, mhlawumbe ngingenza inhlawulelo yesono senu.”<verse eid="EXO 32:30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="EXO 32:31"/>Ngakho uMosi wabuyela <char style="nd">kuThixo</char> wathi kuye, “Awu, abantu laba sebenze isono esikhulu kakhulu. Bazenzele onkulunkulu ngegolide. <verse eid="EXO 32:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="EXO 32:32"/>Ake ubathethelele izono zabo kodwa nxa kungenjalo, ngesula ogwalweni olulobileyo.”<verse eid="EXO 32:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="EXO 32:33"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wamphendula uMosi wathi, “Lowo owenze isono kimi ngizamesula ogwalweni lwami. <verse eid="EXO 32:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="EXO 32:34"/>Khathesi hamba, ukhokhelele abantu endaweni engakhuluma ngayo kuwe. Ingilosi yami izahamba phambi kwakho. Kodwa-ke nxa isikhathi sami sokujezisa sesifikile, ngizabajezisa ngenxa yesono sabo.”<verse eid="EXO 32:34"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="EXO 32:35"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wabajezisa abantu ngesifo ngenxa yalokho abakwenza ngethole elalenziwe ngu-Aroni.<verse eid="EXO 32:35"/></para>
  <chapter eid="EXO 32"/>
  <chapter number="33" style="c" sid="EXO 33"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="EXO 33:1"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wasesithi kuMosi, “Suka kule indawo wena labantu owabakhupha elizweni laseGibhithe, uye elizweni engalithembisa u-Abhrahama lo-Isaka loJakhobe ngifunga ngisithi, ‘Ngizalinika inzalo yakho.’ <verse eid="EXO 33:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="EXO 33:2"/>Ngizathuma ingilosi ihambe phambi kwakho ixotshe amaKhenani, ama-Amori, amaHithi, amaPherizi, amaHivi lamaJebusi. <verse eid="EXO 33:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="EXO 33:3"/>Yana elizweni eligeleza uchago loluju. Kodwa mina angiyikuhamba lani ngoba lingabantu abantamo zilukhuni, hlezi ngilibhubhise endleleni.”<verse eid="EXO 33:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="EXO 33:4"/>Kwathi lapho abantu sebezwe amazwi la adabukisayo baqalisa ukukhala, akwaze kwaba loyedwa owagqiza izigqizo zakhe. <verse eid="EXO 33:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="EXO 33:5"/>Phela <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wayethe kuMosi, “Tshela abako-Israyeli uthi, ‘Lina lingabantu abantamo zilukhuni. Nxa ngingahamba lani loba okomzuzwana nje, ngingalibhubhisa. Khathesi khululani izigqizo zenu; ngizakwenza isinqumo ukuthi ngenzeni ngani.’ ” <verse eid="EXO 33:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="EXO 33:6"/>Ngakho-ke abako-Israyeli bazikhipha izigqizo zabo entabeni yeHorebhi.<verse eid="EXO 33:6"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ithente Lokuhlangana</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="EXO 33:7"/>UMosi wayejwayele ukuthatha ithente ayelimisa ngaphandle bucwadlana lezihonqo. Walibiza ngokuthi “lithente lokuhlangana.” Ubani lobani owayedinga <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wayesiya ethenteni lokuhlangana ngaphandle kwezihonqo. <verse eid="EXO 33:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="EXO 33:8"/>Kwakusithi-ke lapho uMosi ephuma esiya kulelothente abantu bonke babesukuma bame eminyango yamathente abo bakhangele uMosi aze angene ethenteni. <verse eid="EXO 33:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="EXO 33:9"/>Kwakusithi uMosi esengena ethenteni insika yeyezi yehlele phansi ime emnyango wethente lapho <char style="nd">uThixo</char> ekhuluma loMosi. <verse eid="EXO 33:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="EXO 33:10"/>Kwakusithi abantu bangabona insika yeyezi isimi emnyango wethente basukume bonke bakhonze; lowo lalowo emnyango wethente lakhe. <verse eid="EXO 33:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="EXO 33:11"/><char style="nd">UThixo</char> wayekhuluma loMosi ubuso ngobuso njengomuntu ekhuluma lomngane wakhe. Ngemva kwalokho uMosi wayebuyela ezihonqweni, kodwa umncedisi wakhe owayesesemncane, uJoshuwa indodana kaNuni, wayengasuki ethenteni.<verse eid="EXO 33:11"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UMosi Lenkazimulo <char style="nd">KaThixo</char></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="EXO 33:12"/>UMosi wathi <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>, “Ubulokhu ungitshela usithi, ‘Khokhela abantu laba,’ kodwa kawungazisanga ukuthi ngubani ozamthuma ukuba ahambe lami. Utshilo wathi, ‘Ngiyakwazi ngebizo, njalo ufumene umusa kimi.’ <verse eid="EXO 33:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="EXO 33:13"/>Nxa uthokoza ngami, ngifundisa izindlela zakho ukuze ngikwazi, ngiqhubeke ngithola umusa kuwe. Khumbula futhi lokuthi isizwe lesi singabantu bakho.”<verse eid="EXO 33:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="EXO 33:14"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> waphendula wathi, “NgoBukhona bami ngizahamba lawe ngikuphumuze.”<verse eid="EXO 33:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="EXO 33:15"/>UMosi wathi kuye, “Nxa uBukhona bakho bungahambi lathi, ungasisusi lapha. <verse eid="EXO 33:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="EXO 33:16"/>Umuntu angakwazi njani ukuthi mina labantu bakho sifumene umusa kuwe ngaphandle kokuba uhamba lathi na? Kuyini okunye okungasiphawula, mina labantu bakho, kwabanye abantu bonke emhlabeni na?”<verse eid="EXO 33:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="EXO 33:17"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wathi kuMosi, “Ngizakwenza khona kanye lokhu okucelileyo ngoba ngiyathokoza ngawe, njalo ngikwazi ngebizo.”<verse eid="EXO 33:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="EXO 33:18"/>UMosi wasesithi, “Ngicela ukuba ungitshengise inkazimulo yakho.”<verse eid="EXO 33:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="EXO 33:19"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wasesithi, “Ngizakwenza ukulunga kwami kudlule phambi kwakho, njalo ngizamemezela ibizo lami, <char style="nd">uThixo</char>, phambi kwakho. Ngizakuba lesihawu kulowo engizakuba lesihawu kuye njalo ngibe lesisa kulowo engizakuba lesisa kuye.” <verse eid="EXO 33:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="EXO 33:20"/><char style="nd">UThixo</char> waqhubeka wathi, “Kodwa, ubuso bami awungeke ububone, ngoba kakho ongangibona aphile.”<verse eid="EXO 33:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="EXO 33:21"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wabuya wathi, “Kulendawo phansi kwami lapho ongema khona phezu kwedwala. <verse eid="EXO 33:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="EXO 33:22"/>Kuzakuthi lapho inkazimulo yami isedlula eduze, ngizakufaka emnkenkeni wedwala ngikusithe ngesandla sami ngize ngidlule. <verse eid="EXO 33:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="EXO 33:23"/>Emva kwalokho ngizasusa isandla sami ubone umhlane wami; kodwa ubuso bami akumelanga ububone.”<verse eid="EXO 33:23"/></para>
  <chapter eid="EXO 33"/>
  <chapter number="34" style="c" sid="EXO 34"/>
  <para style="s1">Izibhebhedu Zamatshe Ezintsha</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="EXO 34:1"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wathi kuMosi, “Baza ezinye izibhebhedu zamatshe ezimbili zifanane lezakuqala. Ngizabhala kuzo amazwi ayesezibhebhedwini zakuqala owaziphahlazayo. <verse eid="EXO 34:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="EXO 34:2"/>Ube usulungile ekuseni, ubuye phezulu entabeni iSinayi, uziveze kimi engqongweni yentaba. <verse eid="EXO 34:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="EXO 34:3"/>Akungabi lamuntu oza lawe kumbe oke abonakale loba kungaphi entabeni; ngitsho lezimvu lenkomo kazingadli phambi kwaleyontaba.”<verse eid="EXO 34:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="EXO 34:4"/>Ngakho uMosi wabaza izibhebhedu zamatshe ezimbili zaba njengezakuqala, wakhwela entabeni iSinayi ekuseni kakhulu njengokulaywa kwakhe <char style="nd">nguThixo</char> ephethe izibhebhedu ezimbili zamatshe ezandleni zakhe. <verse eid="EXO 34:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="EXO 34:5"/><char style="nd">UThixo</char> wehla ngeyezi wema khonapho laye wamemezela ibizo lakhe esithi, “<char style="nd">UThixo</char>.” <verse eid="EXO 34:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="EXO 34:6"/>Wedlula phambi kukaMosi ememezela esithi, “<char style="nd">UThixo</char>, <char style="nd">uThixo</char>; uNkulunkulu olesihawu lomusa, ophuzayo ukuthukuthela, ogcwele uthando lobuqotho, <verse eid="EXO 34:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="EXO 34:7"/>olothando olungapheliyo kuzinkulungwane ethethelela ububi, iziphosiso lezono. Ikanti abalamacala kabayekeli bengajeziswanga; wehlisela ububi baboyise phezu kwabantwana, laphezu kwabantwana babantwana kusiya kusizukulwane sesithathu lesesine.”<verse eid="EXO 34:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="EXO 34:8"/>UMosi waphanga wakhothamisela ikhanda lakhe phansi, wakhonza. <verse eid="EXO 34:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="EXO 34:9"/>Wathi, “Awu Thixo, nxa ngithole umusa kuwe, ngiyacela, <char style="nd">uThixo</char> kahambe lathi. Lanxa abantu laba bentamo zilukhuni, sithethelele ububi bethu lezono zethu, usithathe njengelifa lakho.”<verse eid="EXO 34:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="EXO 34:10"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wasesithi, “Sengisenza isivumelwano lawe. Phambi kwabantu bakho bonke ngizakwenza izimangaliso ezingakaze zenziwe lanini lakusiphi isizwe emhlabeni wonke. Abantu ohlala phakathi kwabo bazabona ukuthi umangalisa njani umsebenzi, mina <char style="nd">Thixo</char>, engizakwenzela wona. <verse eid="EXO 34:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="EXO 34:11"/>Lalela lokhu engikulaya khona lamhla. Ngizawaxotsha phambi kwakho ama-Amori, amaKhenani, amaHithi, amaPherizi, amaHivi lamaJebusi. <verse eid="EXO 34:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="EXO 34:12"/>Qaphela ukuba kungabi lesivumelwano osenza lalabo abahlala elizweni oya kulo ngoba bangaba yisifu kini. <verse eid="EXO 34:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="EXO 34:13"/>Adilizeni ama-alithare abo, libhidlize lezithombe zabo, liqume lezinsika zika-Ashera wabo abamkhonzayo. <verse eid="EXO 34:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="EXO 34:14"/>Lingakhonzi omunye unkulunkulu, ngoba <char style="nd">uThixo</char>, obizo lakhe linguBukhwele, nguNkulunkulu olobukhwele.<verse eid="EXO 34:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="EXO 34:15"/>Qaphelani lingenzi isivumelwano lalabo abahlala elizweni lelo ngoba nxa bephinga labonkulunkulu babo benikela iminikelo kubo, bazalinxusa beselisidla imihlatshelo yabo. <verse eid="EXO 34:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="EXO 34:16"/>Njalo lapho likhetha amanye amadodakazi abo ukuba abe ngabafazi bamadodana enu kuzakuthi lapho amadodakazi lawo esezibhixa kubonkulunkulu bawo, ahugele amadodana enu ekwenzeni okunjalo.<verse eid="EXO 34:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="EXO 34:17"/>Lingazenzeli onkulunkulu ababunjiweyo.<verse eid="EXO 34:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="EXO 34:18"/>Gcinani uMkhosi weSinkwa esingelaMvubelo. Okwensuku eziyisikhombisa dlanini isinkwa esenziwe kungekho mvubelo, njengokulaya kwami. Lokho kwenzeni ngesikhathi esimisiweyo enyangeni ka-Abhibhi, ngoba ngaleyonyanga laphuma eGibhithe.<verse eid="EXO 34:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="EXO 34:19"/>Inzalo yakuqala yonke ezelweyo ngeyami, kanye lamazibulo wonke amaduna ezifuyo zenu, loba engawenkomo kumbe awezimvu. <verse eid="EXO 34:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="EXO 34:20"/>Izibulo likababhemi lihlengeni ngezinyane. Kodwa nxa lingangalihlengi lephuleni intamo yalo. Ahlengeni wonke amadodana enu angamazibulo.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="EXO 34:20">Kakho ozakuza phambi kwami engaphethe lutho.<verse eid="EXO 34:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="EXO 34:21"/>Lizasebenza insuku eziyisithupha, kodwa ngosuku lwesikhombisa lizaphumula; langesikhathi sokulima lesokuvuna kuzamele liphumule.<verse eid="EXO 34:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="EXO 34:22"/>Thakazelelani uMkhosi wamaViki lokolibo kokuvuna kwenu ingqoloyi loMkhosi wokuButhelela ekupheleni komnyaka. <verse eid="EXO 34:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="EXO 34:23"/>Kathathu ngomnyaka bonke abesilisa bakho kumele babonakale phambi <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char> Wobukhosi, uNkulunkulu ka-Israyeli. <verse eid="EXO 34:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="EXO 34:24"/>Ngizaxotsha izizwe eziphambi kwenu njalo ngiqhelise ilizwe lenu, kakho ozahawukela ilizwe lenu ngesikhathi lisiyabonakala kathathu ngomnyaka phambi <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wenu.<verse eid="EXO 34:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="EXO 34:25"/>Linganikeli igazi lomhlatshelo kimi ndawonye laloba yini elemvubelo, njalo akungabi lomhlatshelo woMkhosi wePhasika ogcinwa kuze kuse.<verse eid="EXO 34:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="EXO 34:26"/>Lethani okolibo kwenu okuhle kakhulu endlini <char style="nd">kaThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wenu.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="EXO 34:26">Lingapheki izinyane lembuzi ngochago lukanina.”<verse eid="EXO 34:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="EXO 34:27"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wasesithi kuMosi, “Loba amazwi la, ngoba ngamazwi la sengenze isivumelwano lawe kanye lo-Israyeli.” <verse eid="EXO 34:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="EXO 34:28"/>UMosi wayekhonale <char style="nd">loThixo</char> insuku ezingamatshumi amane lobusuku obungamatshumi amane engadli sinkwa kumbe ukunatha amanzi. Amazwi esivumelwano ayimiThetho eliTshumi, wawaloba ezibhebhedwini zamatshe.<verse eid="EXO 34:28"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ubuso Obukhazimulayo BukaMosi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="EXO 34:29"/>Kwathi lapho uMosi esehla entabeni yeSinayi ephethe izibhebhedu ezimbili zamatshe obufakazi, wayengazi ukuthi ubuso bakhe babukhazimula ngenxa yokuthi wayekhulume <char style="nd">loThixo</char>. <verse eid="EXO 34:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="EXO 34:30"/>Kwathi u-Aroni labo bonke abako-Israyeli bebona uMosi, ubuso bakhe bukhazimula, besaba ukusondela kuye. <verse eid="EXO 34:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="EXO 34:31"/>Kodwa uMosi wababiza; ngakho u-Aroni lezinduna zonke zabantu beza kuye, wakhuluma labo. <verse eid="EXO 34:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="EXO 34:32"/>Emva kwalokho bonke abako-Israyeli basondela kuye wabanika yonke imilayo <char style="nd">kaThixo</char> ayemuphe yona entabeni yeSinayi.<verse eid="EXO 34:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="EXO 34:33"/>UMosi eseqedile ukukhuluma labo, wamboza ubuso bakhe ngeveli. <verse eid="EXO 34:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="EXO 34:34"/>Kodwa kwakusithi lapho esengena ukuba abe phambi <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char> ukuze akhulume laye, wayelisusa iveli aze aphume. Wayesithi angaphuma, njalo esebatshelile abako-Israyeli lokho ayekulayiwe, <verse eid="EXO 34:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="EXO 34:35"/>babebona ukuthi ubuso bakhe babukhazimula. Lapho-ke uMosi wayebumboza njalo ubuso bakhe ngeveli aze angene esiyakhuluma <char style="nd">loThixo</char>.<verse eid="EXO 34:35"/></para>
  <chapter eid="EXO 34"/>
  <chapter number="35" style="c" sid="EXO 35"/>
  <para style="s1">Imithetho YeSabatha</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="EXO 35:1"/>UMosi wabuthanisa isizwe sonke sako-Israyeli wathi kuso, “Lokhu yikho <char style="nd">uThixo</char> alilaye ukuba likwenze: <verse eid="EXO 35:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="EXO 35:2"/>Okwensuku eziyisithupha lizaqhuba imisebenzi, kodwa usuku lwesikhombisa luzakuba lusuku lwenu olungcwele, iSabatha lokuphumula <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>. Loba ngubani ozakwenza umsebenzi ngalolosuku kuzamele abulawe. <verse eid="EXO 35:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="EXO 35:3"/>Lingabasi umlilo loba kungaphi elihlala khona ngosuku lweSabatha.”<verse eid="EXO 35:3"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Impahla ZeThabanikeli</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="EXO 35:4"/>Ekhuluma lesizwe sonke sako-Israyeli uMosi wathi, “Lokhu yikho <char style="nd">uThixo</char> athe kwenziwe: <verse eid="EXO 35:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="EXO 35:5"/>Kulokho elilakho khiphani umnikelo <char style="nd">kaThixo</char>. Wonke ozimiseleyo ukuletha <char style="nd">kuThixo</char> umnikelo:</para>
  <para style="b" vid="EXO 35:5"/>
  <para style="li1" vid="EXO 35:5">wegolide, isiliva kanye lethusi,<verse eid="EXO 35:5"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="EXO 35:6"/>intambo eziluhlaza, eziyibubende kanye lezibomvu; lelembu elicolekileyo,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="EXO 35:6">uboya bembuzi,<verse eid="EXO 35:6"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="EXO 35:7"/>izikhumba zenqama eziphendulwe ngomphendulo obomvu kanye lezikhumba zezinyamazana eziqinileyo;</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="EXO 35:7">lezigodo zesihlahla somʼakhakhiya;<verse eid="EXO 35:7"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="EXO 35:8"/>amafutha e-oliva awokukhanyisa isibane,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="EXO 35:8">amakha azasetshenziswa lamafutha okugcoba abakhethiweyo lephunga lempepha elimnandi,<verse eid="EXO 35:8"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="EXO 35:9"/>amatshe e-onikisi lamanye amatshe aligugu azathungelwa esembathweni semahlombe lesesifubeni.<verse eid="EXO 35:9"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="EXO 35:10"/>Bonke abazingcitshi phakathi kwenu kumele beze bazokwenza konke lokho <char style="nd">uThixo</char> alaye ukuthi kwenziwe:<verse eid="EXO 35:10"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="EXO 35:11"/>ithabanikeli lethente lalo kanye lesisibekelo, ingwegwe, amathala, imithando enqumayo, izinsika lezisekelo;<verse eid="EXO 35:11"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="EXO 35:12"/>umtshokotsho wobufakazi lemijabo yawo kanye lesisibekelo esiyisihlalo somusa lekhetheni lokulisitha;<verse eid="EXO 35:12"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="EXO 35:13"/>itafula lemijabo yalo lezitsha zonke kanye lesinkwa esiNgcwele,<verse eid="EXO 35:13"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="EXO 35:14"/>uluthi lwesibane sokukhanyisa kanye lezitsha zalo, izibane lamafutha okukhanyisa,<verse eid="EXO 35:14"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="EXO 35:15"/>i-alithari lempepha lemijabo yalo, amafutha okugcoba abakhethiweyo kanye lempepha elephunga elimnandi,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="EXO 35:15">ikhetheni lomnyango esangweni lokuya ethabanikeleni,<verse eid="EXO 35:15"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="EXO 35:16"/>i-alithari leminikelo yokutshiswa leminxibo yokosa eyenziwe ngethusi, imijabo kanye lezitsha zalo zonke,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="EXO 35:16">inditshi yethusi kanye lesisekelo sayo,<verse eid="EXO 35:16"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="EXO 35:17"/>amakhetheni eguma kanye lezinsika zalo lezisekelo, njalo lekhetheni lesango leguma,<verse eid="EXO 35:17"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="EXO 35:18"/>izikhonkwane zethente, ezethabanikeli kanye lezeguma, lamagoda azo,<verse eid="EXO 35:18"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="EXO 35:19"/>izembatho ezelukiweyo ezisetshenziswa ekuphatheni umsebenzi endaweni engcwele, zonke izembatho ezingcwele zika-Aroni umphristi kanye lezembatho zamadodana akhe abazisebenzisayo emsebenzini wobuphristi.”<verse eid="EXO 35:19"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="EXO 35:20"/>Ngemva kwalokho isizwe sonke sako-Israyeli sasuka phambi kukaMosi, <verse eid="EXO 35:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="EXO 35:21"/>kwathi wonke umuntu owayezimisele lowayefuqwa yinhliziyo waletha umnikelo <char style="nd">kuThixo</char> ukuze usetshenziswe ethenteni lokuhlangana lakuzo zonke inkonzo zalo, kanye lakuzembatho ezingcwele. <verse eid="EXO 35:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="EXO 35:22"/>Bonke ababezimisele, abesilisa labesifazane ngokufanayo, baletha izinto zokucecisa ezemihlobo ngemihlobo ezenziwe ngegolide: izipenede, amacici, indandatho kanye lazozonke izinto zokucecisa. Bonke baletha igolide labo kwaba ngumnikelo wokuzunguzwa phambi <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char>. <verse eid="EXO 35:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="EXO 35:23"/>Wonke umuntu owayelentambo eziluhlaza, eziyibubende, ezibomvu kumbe ilembu elicolekileyo, kumbe uboya bembuzi, izikhumba zenqama eziphendulwe ngomphendulo obomvu loba izikhumba zenyamazana zolwandle wakuletha. <verse eid="EXO 35:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="EXO 35:24"/>Labo ababeleminikelo yesiliva kumbe eyethusi bayiletha njengomnikelo <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>, kanti laye wonke umuntu owayelezigodo zesihlahla somʼakhakhiya ezazingasetshenziswa kuloba yiwuphi umsebenzi, waziletha. <verse eid="EXO 35:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="EXO 35:25"/>Wonke owesifazane olobuciko bokweluka waletha ayekweluke ngezandla zakhe, intambo eziluhlaza, eziyibubende lezibomvu kumbe ilembu elicolekileyo. <verse eid="EXO 35:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="EXO 35:26"/>Kanjalo bonke abesifazane ababezimisele futhi belobuciko beluka ngoboya bembuzi. <verse eid="EXO 35:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="EXO 35:27"/>Abakhokheli baletha amatshe aligugu e-onikisi kanye lamanye njalo amatshe aligugu ukuthi athungelwe emahlombe lasesifubeni sesembatho. <verse eid="EXO 35:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="EXO 35:28"/>Baletha njalo leziyoliso kanye lamafutha e-oliva awokukhanyisa lawokugcoba abakhethiweyo kanye lempepha elephunga elimnandi. <verse eid="EXO 35:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="EXO 35:29"/>Bonke abako-Israyeli abesilisa labesifazane ababezimisele baletha iminikelo ngokukhululeka <char style="nd">kuThixo</char> ukuze kwenziwe yonke imisebenzi <char style="nd">uThixo</char> ayelaye uMosi ukuthi bayenze.<verse eid="EXO 35:29"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukukhethwa KukaBhezaleli Lo-Oholiyabhi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="EXO 35:30"/>Ngalokho uMosi wathi kwabako-Israyeli, “Khangelani, <char style="nd">uThixo</char> usekhethe uBhezaleli indodana ka-Uri, indodana kaHuri, owesizwe sikaJuda, <verse eid="EXO 35:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="EXO 35:31"/>njalo usemgcwalise ngoMoya kaNkulunkulu, ukuhlakanipha, ukuqedisisa kanye lolwazi ekwenzeni yonke imisebenzi yobungcitshi <verse eid="EXO 35:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="EXO 35:32"/>ukuba adwebe ngobungcitshi isimo sezinto ezizabazwa ngegolide, isiliva kanye lethusi, <verse eid="EXO 35:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="EXO 35:33"/>ukubaza amatshe lokuwamisa, ukubaza izigodo njalo enze yonke imisebenzi yomuntu oleminwe lobungcitshi. <verse eid="EXO 35:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="EXO 35:34"/>Njalo usenike uBhezaleli kanye lo-Oholiyabhi indodana ka-Ahisamakhi, owesizwe sikaDani ulwazi ekufundiseni abanye. <verse eid="EXO 35:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="EXO 35:35"/><char style="nd">UThixo</char> usebagcwalise ngobuciko bokwenza yonke imihlobo yemisebenzi njengezingcitshi, abadwebi kumbe ababumbi bezinto ezingathungwa kumbe ezingabazwa, abathungi beziceciso zentambo eziluhlaza, eziyibubende lezibomvu kanye lamalembu acolekileyo, labeluki, bonke bezingcitshi ezilolwazi olukhulu lababumbi bezinto ezingathungwa kumbe ezingabazwa.<verse eid="EXO 35:35"/></para>
  <chapter eid="EXO 35"/>
  <chapter number="36" style="c" sid="EXO 36"/>
  <para style="nb">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="EXO 36:1"/>Ngakho uBhezaleli, u-Oholiyabhi lomuntu wonke <char style="nd">uThixo</char> amuphe ubungcwethi lamandla okwazi ukwenza wonke lumsebenzi wokwakha indlu engcwele, kumele benze umsebenzi njengokulaywa kwabo <char style="nd">nguThixo</char>.”<verse eid="EXO 36:1"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="EXO 36:2"/>UMosi wasebiza uBhezaleli, u-Oholiyabhi labo bonke abalobungcwethi, <char style="nd">uThixo</char> ayebaphe amandla lowayezimisele ukuzokwenza lowomsebenzi. <verse eid="EXO 36:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="EXO 36:3"/>Bemukela abakuphiwa nguMosi okwakuyiminikelo yabako-Israyeli benikelela ukwakhiwa kwendlu engcwele. Abantu baqhubeka beletha iminikelo ngokukhululeka kwabo ukusa kwamalanga wonke. <verse eid="EXO 36:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="EXO 36:4"/>Ngakho zonke izingcitshi ezazisenza umsebenzi wonke wokwakha indlu engcwele zatshiya yonke imisebenzi yazo <verse eid="EXO 36:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="EXO 36:5"/>zathi kuMosi, “Abantu baletha okunengi kakhulu kulalokho <char style="nd">uThixo</char> alaya ukuba kwenziwe.”<verse eid="EXO 36:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="EXO 36:6"/>Ngakho uMosi wakhupha isiqondiso basebethumela ilizwi ezihonqweni elithi, “Kakho owesilisa loba owesifazane okusamele enze olunye ulutho ukuthi lube ngumnikelo wendlu engcwele.” Ngalokho abantu bavinjelwa ukuletha okunye futhi, <verse eid="EXO 36:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="EXO 36:7"/>ngoba abasebelakho kwasekukunengi okwedlula lokho okwakuzaphetha umsebenzi.<verse eid="EXO 36:7"/></para>
  <para style="s1">IThabanikeli</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="EXO 36:8"/>Wonke amadoda alobungcwethi phakathi kwabasebenzayo akha ithabanikeli ngamakhetheni alitshumi enziwe ngelembu eliphothwe kuhle ngentambo eziluhlaza, eziyibubende kanye lezibomvu, laceciswe ngamakherubhi elukelwa kuhle yingcitshi. <verse eid="EXO 36:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="EXO 36:9"/>Wonke amakhetheni ayelingana ubude bawo buzingalo ezingamatshumi amabili lesificaminwembili njalo ububanzi ezingalo ezine. <verse eid="EXO 36:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="EXO 36:10"/>Babambanisa amakhetheni amahlanu ndawonye, benza njalo lakwamanye amahlanu. <verse eid="EXO 36:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="EXO 36:11"/>Basebesenza izihitshela ngelembu eliluhlaza belandela umphetho wekhetheni elisekucineni kwelixha lakuqala, kwenziwa okufananayo elixheni lesibili. <verse eid="EXO 36:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="EXO 36:12"/>Benza njalo ezinye izihitshela ezingamatshumi amahlanu ekhethenini elilodwa, benza futhi ezinye izihitshela ezingamatshumi amahlanu ekhethenini lokucina lelixha lesibili, izihitshela zazikhangelene. <verse eid="EXO 36:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="EXO 36:13"/>Basebesenza ingwegwe zegolide ezingamatshumi amahlanu, bazisebenzisa ukuhlanganisa izixha zombili zamakhetheni ukuze ithabanikeli libe yintonye.<verse eid="EXO 36:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="EXO 36:14"/>Benza amakhetheni ngoboya bembuzi aba ngawethente lokubekwa phezu kwethabanikeli, wonke abalitshumi lanye. <verse eid="EXO 36:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="EXO 36:15"/>Wonke amakhetheni alitshumi lanye ayelingana, ezingalo ezingamatshumi amathathu ubude, ububanzi ezingalo ezine. <verse eid="EXO 36:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="EXO 36:16"/>Bahlanganisa amakhetheni amahlanu aba lilixha layisithupha kwelinye ilixha. <verse eid="EXO 36:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="EXO 36:17"/>Benza izihitshela ezingamatshumi amahlanu zilandela umphetho wekhetheni elisekucineni kwelixha lakuqala, benza okufananayo ekhethenini lelixha lesibili. <verse eid="EXO 36:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="EXO 36:18"/>Balungisa ingwegwe zethusi ezingamatshumi amahlanu ukuze babophe ngazo ithente libe yinto yinye. <verse eid="EXO 36:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="EXO 36:19"/>Benza isembeso sethente ngezikhumba zenqama eziphendulwe ngomphendulo obomvu, kwathi ngaphezu kwalokho benza isembeso ngezikhumba eziqinileyo.<verse eid="EXO 36:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="EXO 36:20"/>Benza amathala ethabanikeli okumiswa ngezigodo zesihlahla somʼakhakhiya. <verse eid="EXO 36:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="EXO 36:21"/>Ithala linye lalilide okuzingalo ezilitshumi, kwathi ububanzi laba yingalo elengxenye, <verse eid="EXO 36:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="EXO 36:22"/>kulemisuka emibili ephutsha ilinganisene. Wonke amathala ethabanikeli enziwa ngale indlela. <verse eid="EXO 36:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="EXO 36:23"/>Benza amathala ecele elisezansi kwethabanikeli angamatshumi amabili, <verse eid="EXO 36:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="EXO 36:24"/>benza izisekelo zesiliva ezingamatshumi amane ezazihamba ngaphansi kwawo, izisekelo ezimbili ethaleni linye, isisekelo sinye ngaphansi kwensika inye ngayinye. <verse eid="EXO 36:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="EXO 36:25"/>Kuleli elinye icele, icele elisenyakatho kwethabanikeli, bamisa amathala angamatshumi amabili <verse eid="EXO 36:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="EXO 36:26"/>kanye lezisekelo zesiliva ezingamatshumi amane, ezimbili ngaphansi kwethala lilinye. <verse eid="EXO 36:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="EXO 36:27"/>Benza amathala ayisithupha ecele elisekucineni ngentshonalanga kwethabanikeli, <verse eid="EXO 36:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="EXO 36:28"/>benza amathala amabili emagumbini asekucineni. <verse eid="EXO 36:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="EXO 36:29"/>Emagumbini womabili amathala ayelohlonzi oluphindwe kabili kusuka phansi kusiya phezulu, ehlanganiswe ngesongo elilodwa njalo womabili enziwa ngokufananayo. <verse eid="EXO 36:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="EXO 36:30"/>Ngakho kwenziwa amathala ayisificaminwembili lezisekelo zesiliva ezilitshumi lesithupha, zimbili ngaphansi kwethala linye.<verse eid="EXO 36:30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="EXO 36:31"/>Benza njalo imithando enqumayo ngezigodo zesihlahla somʼakhakhiya: emihlanu ingeyamathala akwelinye icele lethabanikeli, <verse eid="EXO 36:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="EXO 36:32"/>emihlanu yayingeyakwelinye icele, kwathi njalo eminye emihlanu yaba ngeyamathala asentshonalanga ekucineni kwethabanikeli. <verse eid="EXO 36:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="EXO 36:33"/>Umthando onquma phakathi bawenza wedlula usuka kwelinye icele usiya kwelinye phakathi laphakathi kwamathala. <verse eid="EXO 36:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="EXO 36:34"/>Bahuqa amathala ngegolide benza amasongo ngegolide abamba imithando. Njalo bahuqa imithando ngegolide.<verse eid="EXO 36:34"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="EXO 36:35"/>Benza ikhetheni ngelembu elicolekileyo, eliphethwe kuhle ngentambo eziluhlaza, eziyibubende lezibomvu, aba lamakherubhi elukelwe kuwo ngumuntu oleminwe. <verse eid="EXO 36:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="EXO 36:36"/>Bawenzela izinsika ezine ngezigodo zesihlahla somʼakhakhiya bazihuqa ngegolide. Izinsika bazenzela ingwegwe zegolide njalo bawamisela lezisekelo ezine zesiliva. <verse eid="EXO 36:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="EXO 36:37"/>Benza ikhetheni lesango lethente ngelembu elicolekileyo elilentambo eziphothiweyo eziluhlaza, eziyibubende lezibomvu, kwaba ngumsebenzi wombalazi ngokuthunga; <verse eid="EXO 36:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="EXO 36:38"/>njalo benza izinsika ezinhlanu zilengwegwe zazo. Bahuqa izihloko zensika kanye lamabhanti azo ngegolide njalo benza lezisekelo ezinhlanu ngethusi.<verse eid="EXO 36:38"/></para>
  <chapter eid="EXO 36"/>
  <chapter number="37" style="c" sid="EXO 37"/>
  <para style="s1">Umtshokotsho Wesivumelwano</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="EXO 37:1"/>UBhezaleli wabaza umtshokotsho ngezigodo zesihlahla somʼakhakhiya ubude bawo kuzingalo ezimbili ezilengxenye, ububanzi kuyingalo elengxenye njalo ukuyaphezulu kwawo kuyingalo elengxenye. <verse eid="EXO 37:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="EXO 37:2"/>Walihuqa ngegolide elicolekileyo, ngaphakathi langaphandle, wabuye walizingelezela ngomqolo wegolide. <verse eid="EXO 37:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="EXO 37:3"/>Wawubumbela amasongo amane egolide wawanamathisela ezinyaweni zalo zozine, kwathi amasongo amabili kwelinye icele lamabili kwelinye njalo. <verse eid="EXO 37:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="EXO 37:4"/>Wasebaza imijabo ngesihlahla somʼakhakhiya wayihuqa ngegolide. <verse eid="EXO 37:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="EXO 37:5"/>Wasehloma imijabo leyo emasongweni ayesemaceleni komtshokotsho wesivumelwano ukuze uthwalwe ngayo.<verse eid="EXO 37:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="EXO 37:6"/>Wenza isihlalo somusa ngegolide elicolekileyo, ubude baso buzingalo ezimbili ezilengxenye lengxenye, ububanzi saba yingalo elengxenye. <verse eid="EXO 37:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="EXO 37:7"/>Njalo wenza amakherubhi amabili ngegolide elikhandiweyo ekucineni kwesihlalo somusa emaceleni womabili. <verse eid="EXO 37:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="EXO 37:8"/>Wenza ikherubhi elilodwa nganxanye kwathi kwelinye icele wenza elinye aba yinto yinye lesisibekelo. <verse eid="EXO 37:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="EXO 37:9"/>Amakherubhi ayelulele amaphiko awo phezulu, embese isisibekelo ngawo. Amakherubhi ayekhangelene, ubuso bawo bukhangele isisibekelo.<verse eid="EXO 37:9"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Itafula</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="EXO 37:10"/>Babaza itafula ngezigodo zesihlahla somʼakhakhiya, ubude bayo babuzingalo ezimbili, ububanzi buyingalo eyodwa, ukuphakama kwayo kuyingalo elengxenye. <verse eid="EXO 37:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="EXO 37:11"/>Basebelihuqa ngegolide elicolekileyo njalo balizingelezela ngomthando wegolide. <verse eid="EXO 37:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="EXO 37:12"/>Babuya benza ibhanti eliyizingelezileyo, elalingangesandla somuntu ububanzi, basebefaka umthando wegolide phezu kwebhanti. <verse eid="EXO 37:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="EXO 37:13"/>Benza amasongo amane egolide bawafaka emagumbini womane enyaweni zetafula. <verse eid="EXO 37:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="EXO 37:14"/>Amasongo afakwa eduze lebhanti ukuze abambe imijabo eyayisetshenziswa ukuthwala itafula. <verse eid="EXO 37:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="EXO 37:15"/>Imijabo yokuthwalisa itafula yayenziwe ngezigodo zesihlahla somʼakhakhiya njalo ihuqwe ngegolide. <verse eid="EXO 37:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="EXO 37:16"/>Njalo benza ngegolide elicolekileyo izitsha zetafula ezibalisa imiganu, izinditshi, imiganu eyingubhe kanye lezitsha zokuthululela iminikelo enathwayo.<verse eid="EXO 37:16"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Uluthi Lwesibane</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="EXO 37:17"/>Benza uluthi lwesibane ngegolide elicolekileyo, bakhanda isidindi salo lomqwayi walo kwaba ngumsebenzi okhandiweyo, imbizana zalo, amahlumela alo kanye lamaluba alo kwenziwa kwaba yinto yinye. <verse eid="EXO 37:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="EXO 37:18"/>Ingatsha eziyisithupha zaxhunywa emaceleni oluthi lwesibane, ingatsha ezintathu nganxanye kwathi ezintathu kwelinye icele. <verse eid="EXO 37:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="EXO 37:19"/>Inkezo ezintathu ezibunjwe okwamaluba e-alimondi, amahlumela lamaluba kwakusogatsheni lunye, ezinye ezintathu ogatsheni olulandelayo, kwabanjalo kuwo wonke ayisithupha exhunywe oluthini lwesibane. <verse eid="EXO 37:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="EXO 37:20"/>Njalo oluthini lwesibane kwakulembizana ezine ezibunjwe okwamaluba e-alimondi elamahlumela kanye lamaluba. <verse eid="EXO 37:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="EXO 37:21"/>Ihlumela elilodwa lalingaphansi kwengatsha ezimbili, ihlumela lesibili lingaphansi kwezinye ezimbili lehlumela lesithathu lalingaphansi kwengatsha ezimbili, ingatsha zonke zaziyisithupha. <verse eid="EXO 37:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="EXO 37:22"/>Amahlumela lezingatsha kwakuyinto yinye loluthi lwesibane, kukhandwe ngegolide elicolekileyo.<verse eid="EXO 37:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="EXO 37:23"/>Balwenzela izibane eziyisikhombisa, incijana lembizana zalo ezenziwe ngegolide elicolekileyo. <verse eid="EXO 37:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="EXO 37:24"/>Uluthi lwesibane kanye lakho konke okuphathelene lalo kwenziwa ngegolide elicolekileyo eliyisisindo sethalenta elilodwa.<verse eid="EXO 37:24"/></para>
  <para style="s1">I-Alithari Lempepha</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="EXO 37:25"/>Benza i-alithari lempepha ngezigodo zesihlahla somʼakhakhiya. Lenziwa lalingana inxa zonke, ubude balo buyingalo eyodwa, lobubanzi buyingalo eyodwa, kanti ukudepha kuzingalo ezimbili, impondo zalo zenziwa zaba yinto yinye kanye lalo. <verse eid="EXO 37:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="EXO 37:26"/>Balihuqa ngegolide elicolekileyo phezulu, lemaceleni kanye lempondo zalo ngegolide elicolekileyo njalo balibumbela umqolo wegolide inxa zonke. <verse eid="EXO 37:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="EXO 37:27"/>Benza amasongo amabili kuleli icele lamanye amabili kwelinye njalo ukubambanisa imijabo yokuthwalisa i-alithari lempepha. <verse eid="EXO 37:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="EXO 37:28"/>Benza imijabo ngesihlahla somʼakhakhiya bayihuqa ngegolide.<verse eid="EXO 37:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="EXO 37:29"/>Benza njalo lamafutha angcwele okugcoba abakhethiweyo, lempepha elephunga elimnandi, kungumsebenzi womenzi wamakha.<verse eid="EXO 37:29"/></para>
  <chapter eid="EXO 37"/>
  <chapter number="38" style="c" sid="EXO 38"/>
  <para style="s1">I-Alithari Lomnikelo Wokutshiswa</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="EXO 38:1"/>Bakha i-alithari lomnikelo wokutshiswa ngezigodo zesihlahla somʼakhakhiya laba zingalo ezintathu ukudepha, ubude balo laba zingalo ezinhlanu, ububanzi laba zingalo ezinhlanu, lilingana inxa zonke. <verse eid="EXO 38:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="EXO 38:2"/>Benza uphondo kumagumbi womane e-alithare, kwathi impondo le-alithari kwaba yinto yinye, basebelihuqa ngethusi. <verse eid="EXO 38:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="EXO 38:3"/>Benza zonke izinto ezisetshenziswa kulo ngethusi, imbiza zalo, amafotsholo, imiganu yokuchela, amafologwe enyama kanye lezindengezi zokubasela umlilo. <verse eid="EXO 38:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="EXO 38:4"/>Benza iminxibo ye-alithare, bayenza ngethusi yaba ngaphansi kwesengamo se-alithare okuyingxenye yokuya phezulu. <verse eid="EXO 38:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="EXO 38:5"/>Benza amasongo ethusi okubambisa imijabo yemagumbini womane yeminxibo yethusi. <verse eid="EXO 38:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="EXO 38:6"/>Imijabo bayenza ngezigodo zesihlahla somʼakhakhiya bazihuqa ngethusi. <verse eid="EXO 38:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="EXO 38:7"/>Basebehloma imijabo leyo emasongweni yaba semaceleni kwe-alithari ukuze lithwalwe ngayo. Balenza ngamapulanka lafana lomkolo.<verse eid="EXO 38:7"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Umkolo Wokugezela</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="EXO 38:8"/>Benza umkolo wethusi lensika yawo yethusi yenziwa ngezibuko zethusi ezazingezabesifazane ababesebenza esangweni lethente lokuhlangana.<verse eid="EXO 38:8"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Iguma Lethabanikeli</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="EXO 38:9"/>Ngemva kwalokho balungisa iguma lethabanikeli. Ubude becele lezansi babuzingalo ezilikhulu njalo lilamakhetheni elembu elelukwe kuhle, <verse eid="EXO 38:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="EXO 38:10"/>lilensika ezingamatshumi amabili lezisekelo zethusi ezingamatshumi amabili, njalo lilezingwegwe zesiliva kanye lamabhanti ensikeni. <verse eid="EXO 38:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="EXO 38:11"/>Icele lenyakatho lalo lalizingalo ezilikhulu ubude njalo lilensika ezingamatshumi amabili, lezisekelo zethusi ezingamatshumi amabili, kanye lengwegwe zesiliva lamabhanti ensikeni.<verse eid="EXO 38:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="EXO 38:12"/>Icele lentshonalanga yeguma lalizingalo ezingamatshumi amahlanu ububanzi, lilamakhetheni, lilensika ezilitshumi, ingwegwe zesiliva kanye lamabhanti ensikeni. <verse eid="EXO 38:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="EXO 38:13"/>Eceleni lempumalanga kusiya okuphuma khona ilanga, lakhona iguma lalibanzi okwezingalo ezingamatshumi amahlanu. <verse eid="EXO 38:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="EXO 38:14"/>Amakhetheni azingalo ezilitshumi lanhlanu ubude ayenganxanye kwesango, kulezinsika ezintathu kanye lezisekelo ezintathu, <verse eid="EXO 38:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="EXO 38:15"/>ngakwelinye icele lakho kwakulamakhetheni azingalo ezilitshumi lanhlanu ubude, kulezinsika ezintathu kanye lezisekelo ezintathu. <verse eid="EXO 38:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="EXO 38:16"/>Wonke amakhetheni ayehonqolozele iguma lethabanikeli ayenziwe ngelembu eliphethwe kuhle. <verse eid="EXO 38:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="EXO 38:17"/>Izisekelo zensika zazingezethusi. Ingwegwe kanye lamabhanti ensikeni kwakuyisiliva, njalo izihloko zazo zihuqwe ngesiliva, ngokunjalo zonke izinsika zeguma zazilamabhanti esiliva, njalo izihloko zazo zihuqwe ngesiliva, ngakho zonke izinsika zeguma zazilamabhanti esiliva.<verse eid="EXO 38:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="EXO 38:18"/>Ikhetheni lesango leguma lalenziwe ngelembu eliphethwe kuhle ngentambo eluhlaza, eyibubende kanye lebomvu, kwaba ngumsebenzi wombalazi ngokuthunga. Ikhetheni lakhona lalizingalo ezingamatshumi amabili ubude, kanti njengekhetheni leguma ukudepha kwalo kwakuzingalo ezinhlanu, <verse eid="EXO 38:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="EXO 38:19"/>lilensika ezine lezisekelo zethusi ezine. Ingwegwe zalo kanye lamabhanti kuyisiliva, njalo izihloko zalo zihuqwe ngesiliva. <verse eid="EXO 38:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="EXO 38:20"/>Izikhonkwane zonke zethente lethabanikeli kanye lezizingelezele iguma zazenziwe ngethusi.<verse eid="EXO 38:20"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Okwasetshenziswa Ekwakheni</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="EXO 38:21"/>Lokhu yikho ngobunengi bakho, okwasetshenziswa ukwakha ithabanikeli, ithabanikeli lobufakazi, yikho okwalotshwa ngabaLevi ngokulawula kukaMosi ngaphansi kwesiqondiso sika-Ithamari indodana ka-Aroni, umphristi. <verse eid="EXO 38:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="EXO 38:22"/>(UBhezaleli indodana ka-Uri, indodana kaHuri, owesizwe sakoJuda, wenza konke uMosi ayekulaywe <char style="nd">nguThixo</char>, <verse eid="EXO 38:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="EXO 38:23"/>wayelo-Oholiyabhi indodana ka-Ahisamakhi owesizwe sikaDani owayeyingcitshi yomsebenzi njalo engumdwebi, njalo engumbalazi ngokuthunga ngentambo eluhlaza, eyibubende lebomvu, kanye lelembu elicolekileyo.) <verse eid="EXO 38:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="EXO 38:24"/>Isilinganiso segolide lonke lomnikelo wokuzunguzwa elasetshenziswa emsebenzini wonke wendawo engcwele lalingamathalenta ayisisindo esingamatshumi amabili lasificamunwemunye (29) kanye lamashekeli angamakhulu ayisikhombisa lamatshumi amathathu (730) kusiya ngamashekeli endawo engcwele.<verse eid="EXO 38:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="EXO 38:25"/>Isiliva esavela kulabo abahlala khona ababebaliwe ngesikhathi sokubalwa kwabantu sasilesisindo esingamathalenta alikhulu (100) lamashekeli ayinkulungwane lamakhulu ayisikhombisa alamatshumi ayisikhombisa lanhlanu (1,775), kusiya ngamashekeli endawo engcwele, <verse eid="EXO 38:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="EXO 38:26"/>ibhekha linye ngomuntu, okuyikuthi, ingxenye yeshekeli ngesilinganiso seshekeli endaweni engcwele, kubo bonke labo ababechaphele kwabasebebaliwe, abaleminyaka engamatshumi amabili okuzalwa loba ukwedlula lapho, kwaba ngamadoda azinkulungwane ezingamakhulu ayisithupha lantathu lamakhulu amahlanu lamatshumi amahlanu (603,550) esehlangene wonke. <verse eid="EXO 38:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="EXO 38:27"/>Isiliva esiyisisindo samathalenta alikhulu (100) sasetshenziswa ekwenzeni izisekelo zendawo engcwele kanye lekhetheni, izisekelo ezilikhulu (100) zenziwa ngesiliva esingamathalenta alikhulu (100), isilinganiso sethalenta linye ukwenza isisekelo esisodwa. <verse eid="EXO 38:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="EXO 38:28"/>Basebenzisa isiliva esilesisindo esingamashekeli ayinkulungwane elamakhulu ayisikhombisa lamatshumi ayisikhombisa lanhlanu (1,775) ukwenza ingwegwe zensika, ukuhuqa izihloko zensika, kanye lokwenza amabhanti ensika.<verse eid="EXO 38:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="EXO 38:29"/>Isilinganiso sethusi lonke lomnikelo wokuzunguzwa sasingamathalenta angamatshumi ayisikhombisa (70) lamashekeli azinkulungwane ezimbili ezilamakhulu amane (2,400). <verse eid="EXO 38:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="EXO 38:30"/>Balisebenzisa ukwenza izisekelo zesango lethente lokuhlangana, i-alithari lethusi, iminxibo yalo yethusi kanye lazozonke izitsha zalo, <verse eid="EXO 38:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="EXO 38:31"/>izisekelo ezihonqolozele iguma lalezo ezisesangweni kanye lezikhonkwane zethabanikeli lazozonke ezihonqolozele iguma.<verse eid="EXO 38:31"/></para>
  <chapter eid="EXO 38"/>
  <chapter number="39" style="c" sid="EXO 39"/>
  <para style="s1">Izembatho ZobuPhristi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="EXO 39:1"/>Benza izembatho zokwenza umsebenzi endaweni engcwele ngokuzeluka ngentambo eluhlaza, eyibubende lebomvu. Basebesenza isembatho sika-Aroni esingcwele, njengalokhu <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wayelaye uMosi.<verse eid="EXO 39:1"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Isembatho Semahlombe</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="EXO 39:2"/>Benza isembatho semahlombe ngegolide, kanye lentambo eluhlaza, eyibubende lebomvu langelembu elicolekileyo. <verse eid="EXO 39:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="EXO 39:3"/>Bakhanda izicecedu zegolide bazisika zaba zincingo bazeluka ngentambo eluhlaza, eyibubende lebomvu, kanye lelembu elicolekileyo, kwaba ngumsebenzi womuntu oleminwe. <verse eid="EXO 39:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="EXO 39:4"/>Benza iziqa zemahlombe esambathweni leso, ezathungelwa emaceleni womabili ukuze sibotshwe. <verse eid="EXO 39:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="EXO 39:5"/>Ukhalo lwaso olwelukwa ngobuciko lwalufanana laso, luyinto yinye lesembatho semahlombe, lwenziwe ngentambo eligolide, eluhlaza, eyibubende lebomvu, kanye lelembu eliphothwe kuhle, njengalokhu <char style="nd">uThixo</char> walaya uMosi.<verse eid="EXO 39:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="EXO 39:6"/>Bathungela amatshe aligugu ohlobo lwe-onikisi ezicecisweni zegolide bawadwebela njengophawu elamabizo amadodana ka-Israyeli. <verse eid="EXO 39:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="EXO 39:7"/>Basebewathungela eziqeni zemahlombe esembatho semahlombe njengamatshe esikhumbuzo samadodana ka-Israyeli, njengalokhu <char style="nd">uThixo</char> walaya uMosi.<verse eid="EXO 39:7"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Isembatho Sesifubeni</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="EXO 39:8"/>Benza isembatho sesifubeni, kwaba ngumsebenzi wezingcwethi. Basenza njengesembatho semahlombe: ngegolide, ngentambo eluhlaza, eyibubende lebomvu, kanye lelembu eliphothwe kuhle. <verse eid="EXO 39:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="EXO 39:9"/>Sasilingana inxa zonke, singumunwe ubude lomunwe ububanzi, sigoqwe saphindwa kabili. <verse eid="EXO 39:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="EXO 39:10"/>Basebethungela imizila emine yamatshe aligugu. Emzileni wakuqala kwakulerubhi, ithophazi kanye lebheriyeli; <verse eid="EXO 39:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="EXO 39:11"/>emzileni wesibili kwakule-emeralidi, isafaya kanye ledayimana; <verse eid="EXO 39:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="EXO 39:12"/>emzileni wesithathu kwakulejasinti, i-agathi kanye le-amethisi; <verse eid="EXO 39:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="EXO 39:13"/>emzileni wesine kwakulekhrisolathi, i-onikisi kanye lejaspa. Athungelwa esezicecisweni zegolide. <verse eid="EXO 39:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="EXO 39:14"/>Kwakulamatshe alitshumi lambili, lilinye limele ibizo ngalinye lamadodana ka-Israyeli, linye ngalinye lilotshwe njengokudweba kombazi wamatshe, kungani luphawu, ngalinye lilotshwe ibizo lezizwana zako-Israyeli ezilitshumi lambili.<verse eid="EXO 39:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="EXO 39:15"/>Isembatho sesifubeni selukelwa amaketane ngegolide elicolekileyo kungani ligoda. <verse eid="EXO 39:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="EXO 39:16"/>Benza iziceciso zegolide ezimbili, kanye lamasongo amabili egolide, basebebophela amasongo amabili emagumbini esembatho sesifubeni. <verse eid="EXO 39:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="EXO 39:17"/>Babophela amaketane amabili egolide emasongweni amabili asemagumbini esembatho sesifubeni, <verse eid="EXO 39:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="EXO 39:18"/>kwathi ngapha acina khona bawabophela ezicecisweni ezimbili, bawahlanganisa eziqeni zemahlombe phambi kwesembatho semahlombe. <verse eid="EXO 39:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="EXO 39:19"/>Benza amasongo amabili egolide bawabophela kwamanye amagumbi amabili esembatho sesifubeni ngaphakathi komphetho phansi kwesembatho semahlombe. <verse eid="EXO 39:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="EXO 39:20"/>Baphinda benza njalo amanye amasongo egolide amabili bawabophela ngaphansi kweziqa zemahlombe, eduze komphetho ngaphezudlwana kwebhanti lasokhalweni lwesembatho semahlombe <verse eid="EXO 39:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="EXO 39:21"/>Babophela amasongo esembatho sesifubeni emasongweni esembatho semahlombe ngentambo eziluhlaza, kuhlanganiselwa okhalweni ukuze isembatho sesifubeni singazunguzeki sehlukane lesembatho semahlombe njengalokhu <char style="nd">uThixo</char> walaya uMosi.<verse eid="EXO 39:21"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ezinye Izembatho ZobuPhristi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="EXO 39:22"/>Benza isigqoko sesembatho semahlombe ngelembu eliluhlaza kuphela kungumsebenzi womeluki, <verse eid="EXO 39:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="EXO 39:23"/>kulesikhala phakathi laphakathi kwesigqoko njengokuvuleka kwamabheqe; kulomphetho olandeliselwe isikhala lesi ukuze isembatho singadabuki. <verse eid="EXO 39:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="EXO 39:24"/>Benza emphethweni wesigqoko amaphomegranathi ngentambo eluhlaza, eyibubende lebomvu, kanye lelembu eliphothwe kuhle. <verse eid="EXO 39:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="EXO 39:25"/>Benza amabhera ngegolide elicolekileyo bawathungela emphethweni wesigqoko phakathi laphakathi kwamaphomegranathi. <verse eid="EXO 39:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="EXO 39:26"/>Amabhera kanye lamaphomegranathi athungelwa agatshaniswa emphethweni wesembatho esasizagqokwa ekwenzeni umsebenzi wenkonzo, njengalokhu <char style="nd">uThixo</char> walaya uMosi.<verse eid="EXO 39:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="EXO 39:27"/>U-Aroni kanye lamadodana akhe bathungelwa amabhatshi ngelembu elicolekileyo, kungumsebenzi womeluki uqobo lwakhe, <verse eid="EXO 39:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="EXO 39:28"/>kanye lamaqhiye elembu elicolekileyo, kanye lezembatho zangaphakathi zelembu elicolekileyo. <verse eid="EXO 39:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="EXO 39:29"/>Ibhanti lekhalweni lathungwa ngelembu elicolekileyo kanye lentambo eluhlaza, eyibubende lebomvu, kwaba ngumsebenzi wombalazi ngokuthunga, njengalokhu <char style="nd">uThixo</char> walaya uMosi.<verse eid="EXO 39:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="EXO 39:30"/>Benza icence lomqhele ongcwele ngegolide elicolekileyo bawudwebela khona njengombhalo wophawu othi:</para>
  <para style="pc" vid="EXO 39:30">Ubungcwele kabube <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>.<verse eid="EXO 39:30"/></para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="EXO 39:31"/>Basebebophela intambo eluhlaza ukuze bakuhlanganise leqhiye, njengalokhu <char style="nd">uThixo</char> walaya uMosi.<verse eid="EXO 39:31"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UMosi Uhlola IThabanikeli</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="EXO 39:32"/>Ngakho-ke wonke umsebenzi wethabanikeli lethente lokuhlangana wapheleliswa. Abako-Israyeli benza konke njengalokhu <char style="nd">uThixo</char> walaya uMosi. <verse eid="EXO 39:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="EXO 39:33"/>Basebeletha ithabanikeli kuMosi:</para>
  <para style="b" vid="EXO 39:33"/>
  <para style="li1" vid="EXO 39:33">ithente kanye lazozonke impahla zalo, ingwegwe, amathala, imithando, izinsika lezisekelo;<verse eid="EXO 39:33"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="EXO 39:34"/>isembeso esenziwe ngezikhumba zenqama eziphendulwe ngomphendulo obomvu, isembeso sezikhumba eziqinileyo kanye lekhetheni eliphothiweyo;<verse eid="EXO 39:34"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="EXO 39:35"/>umtshokotsho wobufakazi lemijabo yawo eyizibambo zawo kanye lesihlalo somusa;<verse eid="EXO 39:35"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="EXO 39:36"/>itafula lezitsha zalo zonke kanye lesinkwa esiNgcwele;<verse eid="EXO 39:36"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="37" style="v" sid="EXO 39:37"/>uluthi lwesibane lwegolide elicolekileyo lodwendwe lwezibane lazozonke izinto ezisetshenziswa kulo, kanye lamafutha e-oliva okukhanyisa;<verse eid="EXO 39:37"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="38" style="v" sid="EXO 39:38"/>i-alithari legolide, amafutha okugcoba abakhethiweyo, impepha elephunga elimnandi, kanye lekhetheni lesango lethente;<verse eid="EXO 39:38"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="EXO 39:39"/>i-alithari lethusi leminxibo yalo yethusi, izigodo zalo eziyizibambo lezitsha zalo zonke;</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="EXO 39:39">umkolo lezinyawo zawo; amakhetheni eguma lezinsika zawo kanye lezisekelo,<verse eid="EXO 39:39"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="40" style="v" sid="EXO 39:40"/>lekhetheni lesango leguma;</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="EXO 39:40">amagoda lezikhonkwane zethente leguma;</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="EXO 39:40">zonke impahla zethabanikeli, ithente lokuhlangana;<verse eid="EXO 39:40"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="41" style="v" sid="EXO 39:41"/>izembatho ezelukiweyo zokusetshenziswa emsebenzini wokukhonza endaweni engcwele, kuhlanganisa izembatho ezingcwele zika-Aroni lezamadodana akhe ababezazigqoka nxa besenza umsebenzi wobuphristi.<verse eid="EXO 39:41"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="42" style="v" sid="EXO 39:42"/>Abako-Israyeli basebenza wonke umsebenzi njengokulaywa kukaMosi <char style="nd">nguThixo</char>. <verse eid="EXO 39:42"/><verse number="43" style="v" sid="EXO 39:43"/>UMosi wawuhlola umsebenzi wabona ukuthi wawenziwe njengokulaya <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char>. Ngakho uMosi wababusisa.<verse eid="EXO 39:43"/></para>
  <chapter eid="EXO 39"/>
  <chapter number="40" style="c" sid="EXO 40"/>
  <para style="s1">Ukumiswa Kwethabanikeli</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="EXO 40:1"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wasesithi kuMosi: <verse eid="EXO 40:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="EXO 40:2"/>“Misa ithabanikeli, ithente lokuhlangana, ngosuku lokuqala lwenyanga yakuqala. <verse eid="EXO 40:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="EXO 40:3"/>Beka umtshokotsho wesivumelwano kulo ube ususitha umtshokotsho wobufakazi ngekhetheni. <verse eid="EXO 40:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="EXO 40:4"/>Ngenisa itafula ube usufaka izinto ezibekwa phezu kwayo. Letha-ke uluthi lwesibane ube usuxhuma izibane zalo. <verse eid="EXO 40:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="EXO 40:5"/>Beka i-alithari lempepha elenziwe ngegolide phambi komtshokotsho wobufakazi njalo ufake ikhetheni esangweni lethabanikeli.<verse eid="EXO 40:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="EXO 40:6"/>Beka i-alithari lomnikelo wokutshiswa phambi kwesango lethabanikeli, ithente lokuhlangana; <verse eid="EXO 40:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="EXO 40:7"/>beka umkolo phakathi laphakathi kwethente lokuhlangana le-alithari ube usuthela amanzi kuwo. <verse eid="EXO 40:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="EXO 40:8"/>Lungisa iguma eliwugombolozeleyo ubusufaka ikhetheni esangweni leguma.<verse eid="EXO 40:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="EXO 40:9"/>Thatha amafutha okugcoba abantu abakhethiweyo ezikhundleni, ugcobe ngawo ithabanikeli lakho konke okukulo, ulibusise kanye lempahla zalo, ngalokho lizakuba ngcwele. <verse eid="EXO 40:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="EXO 40:10"/>Gcoba-ke i-alithari lomnikelo wokutshiswa lazozonke izitsha zalo; ubusise i-alithari ukuze libe ngcwelengcwele. <verse eid="EXO 40:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="EXO 40:11"/>Gcoba umkolo lenyawo zawo ubusuwubusisa.<verse eid="EXO 40:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="EXO 40:12"/>Letha u-Aroni lamadodana akhe ethenteni lokuhlangana ubusubagezisa ngamanzi. <verse eid="EXO 40:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="EXO 40:13"/>Ubusugqokisa u-Aroni izembatho ezingcwele umgcobe ngamafutha umbusise ukuze angenzele umsebenzi wobuphristi. <verse eid="EXO 40:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="EXO 40:14"/>Letha amadodana akhe uwagqokise amabhatshi. <verse eid="EXO 40:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="EXO 40:15"/>Bagcobe labo njengokugcotshwa kukayise ukuze bangenzele umsebenzi wobuphristi. Ukugcotshwa kwabo kubapha umsebenzi wobuphristi kuzozonke izizukulwane ezizayo.” <verse eid="EXO 40:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="EXO 40:16"/>UMosi wenza konke njengokulaywa kwakhe <char style="nd">nguThixo</char>.<verse eid="EXO 40:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="EXO 40:17"/>Lamiswa-ke ithabanikeli ngosuku lwakuqala ngenyanga yakuqala emnyakeni wesibili. <verse eid="EXO 40:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="EXO 40:18"/>Kwathi uMosi emisa ithabanikeli, wafaka izisekelo endaweni yazo, wamisa amathala, wafaka imithando wasemisa izinsika. <verse eid="EXO 40:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="EXO 40:19"/>Wasesendlala ithente phezu kwethabanikeli wafaka isembeso phezu kwethente njengokulaywa kwakhe <char style="nd">nguThixo</char>.<verse eid="EXO 40:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="EXO 40:20"/>Wathatha izibhebhedu zobufakazi wazibeka emtshokotshweni wesivumelwano, wahloma imijabo kuwo wasefaka isihlalo somusa phezu kwawo. <verse eid="EXO 40:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="EXO 40:21"/>Wasengenisa umtshokotsho wobufakazi ethabanikeleni, waphanyeka ikhetheni lokusitha wawugubuzela, njengalokho okwakulaywe <char style="nd">nguThixo</char>.<verse eid="EXO 40:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="EXO 40:22"/>UMosi wasebeka itafula ethenteni lokuhlangana eceleni langenyakatho lethabanikeli ngaphandle kwekhetheni, <verse eid="EXO 40:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="EXO 40:23"/>wasebeka isinkwa phezu kwalo phambi <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char> njengokulaywa kwakhe <char style="nd">nguThixo</char>.<verse eid="EXO 40:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="EXO 40:24"/>Wabeka uluthi lwesibane ethenteni lokuhlangana lukhangele itafula eningizimu kwethabanikeli, <verse eid="EXO 40:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="EXO 40:25"/>wasemisa izibane phambi <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char>, njengokulaywa kwakhe <char style="nd">nguThixo</char>.<verse eid="EXO 40:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="EXO 40:26"/>UMosi wabeka i-alithari legolide ethenteni lokuhlangana phambi kwekhetheni, <verse eid="EXO 40:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="EXO 40:27"/>wasetshisela impepha phezu kwalo njengokulaywa kwakhe <char style="nd">nguThixo</char>.<verse eid="EXO 40:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="EXO 40:28"/>Waselengisa ikhetheni esangweni lethabanikeli. <verse eid="EXO 40:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="EXO 40:29"/>Wamisa i-alithari lomnikelo wokutshiswa phansi kwesango lethabanikeli lethente lokuhlangana, wanikela phezu kwalo iminikelo yokutshiswa leminikelo yezilimo njengokulaywa kwakhe <char style="nd">nguThixo</char>.<verse eid="EXO 40:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="EXO 40:30"/>Wasebeka umkolo phakathi laphakathi kwethente lokuhlangana le-alithari wasethela amanzi okugeza phakathi kwawo, <verse eid="EXO 40:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="EXO 40:31"/>ngakho uMosi lo-Aroni kanye lamadodana akhe bawusebenzisa ukugeza izandla zabo kanye lezinyawo. <verse eid="EXO 40:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="EXO 40:32"/>Babegeza ngasosonke isikhathi nxa bengena ethenteni lokuhlangana loba nxa besiya e-alithareni njengokulaywa kukaMosi <char style="nd">nguThixo</char>.<verse eid="EXO 40:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="EXO 40:33"/>Ngakho uMosi walungisa iguma elihonqolozele ithabanikeli le-alithari waselengisa ikhetheni esangweni leguma kwaba yikho ukuqeda kukaMosi umsebenzi.<verse eid="EXO 40:33"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Inkazimulo <char style="nd">KaThixo</char></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="EXO 40:34"/>Emva kwalokho iyezi lasibekela ithente lokuhlangana, kwathi inkazimulo <char style="nd">kaThixo</char> yagcwala ithabanikeli. <verse eid="EXO 40:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="EXO 40:35"/>UMosi kenelisanga ukungena ethenteni lokuhlangana ngenxa yeyezi elalimi phezu kwalo, inkazimulo <char style="nd">kaThixo</char> yagcwala ethabanikeleni.<verse eid="EXO 40:35"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="EXO 40:36"/>Kulolonke uhambo lwabako-Israyeli, kwakusithi iyezi lingaphakama lisuka phezu kwethabanikeli, labo baqhubeke; <verse eid="EXO 40:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="EXO 40:37"/>kodwa kuthi nxa iyezi lingaphakamanga, labo babengaqhubekeli phambili, kuze kube mhla liphakama. <verse eid="EXO 40:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="EXO 40:38"/>Ngokunjalo iyezi <char style="nd">likaThixo</char> lalisiba phezu kwethabanikeli emini, kuthi ebusuku kube lomlilo eyezini, bekubona bonke abako-Israyeli ekuhambeni kwabo konke.<verse eid="EXO 40:38"/></para>
  <chapter eid="EXO 40"/>
</usx>
